INSERT INTO `wb_page_content` (`id`, `org_id`, `page_id`, `row_number`, `title`, `widget_type`, `widget_html`, `media_json`, `created_on`, `updated_on`) VALUES (1,1,1,1,'Nine west gladiator wedge sandals',1,'<p>Nine West is a brand that has been synonymous with effortless styling in the field of footwear and accessories.  It produces upscale shoes, sandals and boots designed by some of the best designers in the business. The brand has a huge collection in wedge sandals and all the makes have been praised by fashion educated people around the world. Nine West shoes and sandals are known for being very durable, stylish and classy. The models are made with utmost diligence to ensure that they never go out of fashion.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Gladiator shoes seem to be the latest trend in the global market. From high end designers to top celebrities, everyone seems to be in love with these shoes. Wedge sandals with gladiator features are the newest rage in the market and almost every brand is coming up with ideas that combine both the features very distinctively. Nine West too has forayed in this genre and has come up with all new Arzytoo Wedge Sandal having the beauty of wedges and the styling of gladiators. The distinct design with highest detailing make this model one of the best buys from the brand.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Arzytoo sandals are made of pure leather with a manmade sole for extreme durability. The wedge heel measures 31/2 inches and the model also features very finely woven straps of leather. There are dual straps at the ankle with buckles for easy adjustments. There is synthetic detailing in the side ways for specific attention to glitz. The model comes in three very classy colors –black, brown and silver. The black model speaks volumes about branded detailing when paired up with formal attires. The silver model is more appropriate for parties with small dresses in light colors. The natural leather looks more appropriate with shorts or skirts. On the whole, this is a very fun and hip model that aims to create a neat look with all the good styling of gladiators.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The availability of all the models is hugely dependant on the stock of the company. Many times a particular model might not be available in the official website but may be in the stock of other online shopping platforms. one can check on multiple online portals for comparing the prices. One should ensure that the right size is available for sale. Gladiator wedge shoes are definitely one of the coolest shoes from Nine West.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(2,1,2,1,'Nine west nuncio shoes',1,'<p>Pump shoes are forever and can be worn in style for almost any occasion. The trend of pumps started somewhere in the 1940s when the elite and upper strata of the society started wearing them. With time, pumps have reached almost every global market. Branded pump shoes are ‘must have’ essentials in a closet of any women. What can be a better brand than Nine West that gives prime focus on detailed styling and comfort? The brand is one of the largest dealers of designer pump shoes and has a huge collection in sandals as well.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The most classic design in pump shoes from Nine West is Nuncio. The model has been designed for women specifically for the purpose of daily wear. Whether at college or at work, this model promises to never go out of fashion. The make is synthetic with leather with a manmade sole. The heels of Nuncio measures 3inches and the chic pointed toe gives the scope for a very clean and uncluttered look with any dress. The model is available in four colors and each look is equally poignant and elegant. The classy black is very office footwear designed for wearing with trousers or formal skirts. The green synthetic look of the model works best with skirts and small knee length dresses. The other two colors are in shades of brown with one having small scaly design and other with larger scales.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The best thing about Nuncio from Nine West is the comfort factor. Without any discomfort or pain in the ankle, this model can be worn for hours at a stretch. Whether worn with jeans or shorts, this model lets the user be always smooth at walking. Instead of those high heels that always give the user a feel of crippling at one time or the other, buying Nuncio is better deal for long term wearing. Originally priced at 70USD, Nine West has recently discounted the model. One can check on the online shopping website of the brand for more detailed pictures of the model. There are many online shopping houses where large discounts can be availed on clearance stock sales. The official website mentions all the colors and sizes of the models launched by the company which is quite useful while buying from unofficial websites. Nine West Nuncio shoes is pretty decent model and the money spent is worth the benefits and styling gained. </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(3,1,3,1,'Nine West Rocha Pump',1,'<p>Pumps list among the best styles in women’s shoes around the world. Buying branded pump shoes is like investing in a good classic that is bound to last for years to come. Pumps are simple yet sophisticated style statements and can be worn for almost every occasion. Nine West is one the best manufacturers of stylish pump shoes and every pump from the brand draws huge attention. The ace designers of the Nine West spend a lot of time and efforts in making some of the best pumps in the business. The Rocha pump is one such wardrobe classic footwear which is loved by women of every age.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Rocha pumps are one of the best buys in pumps from Nine West. This simple yet stylishly cut shoe can be worn with almost any outfit. The model is pointed at the toe and the upper is made of pure leather. The insole is made of synthetic and fabric for proving comfort while walking and dancing. The heels of Rocha measures approximately four inches with half inch of platform heel. The model has added arch support for long wearing. The manmade sole is highly durable and this model can be worn almost every day of the week. There are many colors available like Dark Purple Synthetic, Dark Green Fabric, Taupe Leather, Dark Blue Synthetic, Natural Reptile Synthetic, and Black Leather. While the colored models go best with specific outfits, the natural taupe and leather black are eternal classic makes for offices and parties alike.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>This model is one the few models from Nine West that has featured in Lucky magazine. Most fashion critics and users have given good score to this pump shoe in terms in style and comfort. In spite of the medium sized heel and simple cut, the model offers the maximum oomph quotient for every occasion.  Rocha has been priced modestly 80USD. The official website of Nine West offers two colors of the model-Taupe and Black. For all other models, customers need to refer to the nearest authorized dealers or check the online dealers. Most models from Nine West are available on many online shopping websites.  The price of Rocha pump shoe is often different on different online platforms.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>On the whole, the Rocha pump is one of the coolest pump makes from Nine West. Once bought, this model is surely to last for many seasons to come.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(4,1,4,1,'Nine West casilda boot',1,'<p>In the early times, boots were utility footwear. People, who had to work on rough and tough terrains, used boots as a protection for the legs.  In present times, boots mean fashion and more of it. Knee high boots can turn any woman into a diva and can fit with most dresses. Investing a little extra on the right pair of branded boots is worth the money spent. Nine West is one such brand that has steered cleared of all the competition to establish itself as one of the best footwear companies in the world. Boots from Nine West are designed by some of the best designers in the industry. Among the knee high boots from the brand, one that stands out is Casilda.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Calsilda is very fun and hip model with the fineness of a classic. Styled in the military style with laces in the front, this model is a decent buy in the price range of 150-250USD. The suede upper is extremely soft and looks stylish with all the detailing of the laces. The laces are enhanced with the metal grommets for giving a neater look. For those concerned about the fitting, Calsilda features a stylish long zip on the side for easy stepping in the boots. The rubber sole has been designed for maximum durability. The height of the shaft measures 16inches from the arch and the boot opening is about 14inches. The model has heels measuring less than an inch avoiding the chances of crippling. The fine stitches and the sleek posh design makes Nine West Calsilda shoes a must have wardrobe classic. This knee high boots is available in black, grey and brown. While the brown make looks more natural and rusty, the black make is more in demand. For those who like to be different, grey is the perfect offbeat choice and looks velvety at a glance. Fashion experts suggest wearing Casilda with miniskirts or short dresses in the summers. In the winters, the boots can be casually worn with cardigans or pullovers.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>This is one of the most sought after models from Nine West and is often out of stock on the official website. Customers can look for Casilda boots on online shopping plazas and sale units. This boots get full marks on the oomph and styling factor and is perfect for women who love to carry their attitude with them.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(5,1,5,1,'Nine West wedge sandals',1,'<p>Wedge sandals are evergreen fashion statements. These high sandals are welcome from the pencil heels that many find uncomfortable to wear. Nine West is brand that makes some of the most fashionable wedge sandals in the international market. With more than twenty models in different collections, this brand name itself spells style and class. Nine West has series of designer shoes and sandals that fit even the most smallest budgets with ease.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The first model from Nine West that deserves a mention is Elspie. This model has a rubber outsole and is made of pure leather. It features a wedge if 4inches and is available in two prints. The tiger print can be worn with specific dresses where as the grey model is perfect for everyday wear. Those who love wedge sandals in colors will love Gingerly series. With very girly colors like pink, violet, black and natural white, these sandals give a well finished look to the entire dressing. The simple bow detailing on the fingers along with heels of three inches, Gingerly is priced at 69USD. For extreme detailing to bows, the Gelpi series is a decent buy. It comes in classic white and berry pink colors with a heel of three inches.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>With extreme attention to the buckle, the HeartFul series is very innovative attempt from Nine West. The model has one buckle pointing at the fingers and comes in three very different colors. The divinely collection is another series of well designed wedge designed sandals from Nine West. It comes in three colors with two makes of pure leather in black and white. The little metallic detailing on the sides enhances the look of the wedges. Jocelyn is another popular make in wedge sandals that focuses on crisscrossing. This four inches wedge sandals come in blue and suede and is priced at 70USD. For party dresses, Larita is a very eyeball grabbing model. The colors in the series are gold metallic and pewter metallic, both designed for wearing with shimmery dresses. Nacia is another model that has featured in the Seventeen magazine and garnered very positive reviews from fashion critics. The designer has given ample detailing to the straps in the toe and instep area with buckle at the ankle. The four inches wedge and eight different colors make this model a clear favorite in a price of 90USD.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Knotting and detailing at the maximum, Barella is one of the best buys from the house of Nine West in wedge sandals. The model is made of pure leather in golden color and features a buckle closure at the toe. If instep detailing is needed, then Nine West offers the Violanda series in a price of 130USD. Coming in three very classic colors, this model is perfect for dresses that demand detailed shoes. Other models that need special mention are the knotted and weaved Koulax, the ultimate cut and designed Polly. All the models are available in all sizes and can be seen on the official portal of the brand.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(6,1,6,1,'Nine West Sitcom Boot',1,'<p>From being basic utility shoes to becoming evergreen fashion statements, boots have come a long way. Thanks to the time and efforts invested by the leading fashion houses in the world, boots have become signature ways to show style, oomph and attitude. Among the best boots manufacturers in the world, one name that has made its mark in many international markets is Nine West. The brand has a charisma and style that shows in every model it makes. Nine West has a huge collection in boots and one of the best models from the brand is Sitcom. The model is hugely popular with women who love well cut classy boots.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Sitcom boot from Nine West is a very decent product from the brand. It creates a very neat designer look for almost any occasion. The best feature in the model is a well cutout shaft that offers the best custom fit. The soft suede leather upper provides great comfort levels and a fine finish to the entire look of the boot. The outsole is made of rubber to give the best grip at every step. The height of the shaft is approximately 21inches from the arch and the heels measure one inch. The boot opening approximately measures 14inches. Unlike other high heeled boots that often have the fear of crippling; Sitcom is a very easy going model. It can be worn with skirts, cardigans, pullovers or even shorts with equal style. The model is available in black and grey and both the colors look equally hot.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Fashion experts suggest matching the handbag with the color of the Sitcom boot for an uncluttered look. Except for extreme summers, this model works perfectly for almost all seasons. The model is available for sale on the official website of Nine West. Since the demand for the model is quite high, Nine West website might often show that the model is out of stock. There are many other shopping avenues online where one can check the model and compare the prices. Originally priced at around 150USD, the model has been heavily discounted by the brand. The best competitive prices can be found by comparing the various online shopping platforms. Sitcom boot is a sleek, well finished model with maximum detailing to the stitching and cut. Women, who love boots with simpler looks, will love this trendy yet sober model from the house of Nine West.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(7,1,7,1,'Nine West Clearance Shoes',1,'<p>Everyone is fascinated at the idea of shopping branded shoes. While many people go for street shopping of dresses, shoes are something that everyone prefers to be branded. All good branded products have certain qualities that fetch them any high price quoted by the company. Good companies maintain a level of style, comfort and quality in every product to hold the current base of customers and at the same time, capture new markets and sections. Nine West is a renowned brand globally in the market of shoes, bags and accessories. The company leads in designing some very innovative shoe models, thereby creating new trends and styles. With all the efforts and time of designers put in together, the products are bound to cost high. Lovers of the brand wait for the chances where they can acquire the products at cheap rates.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Nine West Clearance Shoes are those shoe makes that are sold by the company at discount through their online portal or retail outlet. The models, which are otherwise very expensive, can be bought at very affordable rates. The Nine West clearance shoes are those models which are heavily discounted by the brand. The golden wooden platform sandal is currently one of the most discounted items on the block. While the model was priced at 110USD, the new price offered is 28USD. Every model that is available for discounts can be bought only within a stipulated period. Since the brand is one of the best in footwear industry globally, the offline and online stores gets more than hundreds hits every day. Customers need to pick up models in the nick of time to get the correct size.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The models featuring in Nine West Clearance shoes keep changing and only personal visits to the outlet or website can help the customer make a perfect choice. Buyers can rest assured that the products on the official site are genuine and have all the inherent qualities of Nine West. In case, Nine West products are purchased from other shopping platforms at discount, customers need to ensure that the products are authenticated and are purchased directly via the company.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Nine West clearance shoes give a fair chance to fashion lovers to buy high priced designer shoes in a decent budget. Staying stylish and upscale is just a few clicks away with these discounted shoes. Buying the best Nine West products was never this easier and simple. </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(8,1,8,1,'Nine west vintage America boots',1,'<p>There is no dearth of brands when it comes to boots but Nine West is brand that remains the first choice of many. Nine West started off initially as a footwear brand with an aim of providing of stylish and comfortable shoes. Presently the brand has expanded in many areas like shoes, bags accessories etc. The vintage America collection from Nine West is one of the popular collections from the brand. There are many earrings, shoes, bags and pendants in this range but boots are undoubtedly the most popular products in the collection.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>There are some very well fashionable boots in the Vintage America collection. The first one is Inthedirt which is a limited edition collection. The model is inspired by musician Karen Elson’s own definition of vintage styling. Laced up, this boots are flat with little touch of glitz and glamour on the back and body. This black model with zip on the side is must-have classic in the wardrobe. Midnight Sun is the second best model in the collection made of pure leather. The model has been designed for utmost detailing to laces. Midnight sun is a knee touching boots with shaft of fifteen inches and a circumference of fourteen inches. The boots have heels of height two and half inches. Designed for the highest level of styling and detailing, this model is priced at 270USD.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Fashionestas who love boots with a buckle will be surprised at the design of Nine West vintage America model named ‘Kedan’. This knee-high model comes with a buckle at the ankle giving it a very clean look. it features a heel of four inches with a shaft of 18inches and circumference of 15inches. It comes in two evergreen classic colors- black and brown and is made of pure leather for high performance. With the zip in the back, Kedan is relatively a very easy to maintain boot from the house of Nine West. Takotae is another model in the Vintage American collection designed for those who love smaller boots. More than styling, this model is more about utility. It features one inch heel and seven inch shaft and can be used for everyday wear. Providing excellent comfort to the feet, this model has side zip for easy wearing and is priced at 110USD.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>For more detailing to buckles, the all new Newberry from Nine West is a pretty decent buy. This model can be easily counted as one of the most fashionable boots from the brand. The entire boot has four buckles at equal distances and features heels of four inches. The shaft of these boots measure 19 inches with a circumference of 16 inches. The model is available in grey and dark taupe and is priced at 190USD. All the models of the Vintage America collection can be seen online on the official website. Exclusively designed with utmost importance to comfort and durability, Nine West boots are quality investments. Most models are available as per stock which can be checked with the brand.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(9,1,9,1,'Nine west trinity boot',1,'<p>Riding boots are dual purpose boots. They serve as the best utility shoes for those who travel and ride the tough routes and become style statements for those who know to carry attitude in style. Protective yet stylish, riding boots can last for many seasons and are known to be one of the most durable make of shoes. When bought from a branded company, these boots become jewels in the wardrobe and fashion lovers love to wear them time and again.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Nine West is known to create models in footwear that turn out to be trend setters. This brand that deals in shoes, accessories, bags on a global platform started off mainly in the footwear market. Currently, Nine West has some of the best designers in the fashion business who create the best models in shoes, sandals, wedges and boots. Among the many makes of boots from the company, Trinity is a model that stands out and demands attention.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>This model from the house of Nine West is a pure classic. This is a flat knee high riding boot made out of pure leather upper. The outsole is made of pure rubber for better traction and superb durability. The shaft of from the arch measures around 15inches and the circumference is 14inches. This boots are perfect for regular usage with very well balanced heels measuring one inch. While knee high boots with heels can be really dangerous for rough terrains, this one works perfectly for any topography. The leather used in the make is of extremely high quality and comes in solid black color. Trinity is designed to give a comfort feeling inside and a tough and rough feel outside. There are two buckles featuring on sides for a clean feel. The cut of this boot is very upscale with simple detailing near the ankle and minimal attention to the front.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Trinity is such a popular make from Nine West that it is often found to out of stock. The official website of Nine West can give better details in terms of availability in the company stock. Other online shopping platforms too deal in this model but customers must ensure that the products are authentic and comes from the company stock. The model was originally priced for 180USD but company later on discounted the model which led to faster sales. Customers should not think twice before buying this model if found in stock.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(10,1,10,1,'Nine West pump shoes',1,'<p>Pump shoes are loved by women around the world for the unmatched level of style and comfort. From a tiring day in the office to pool parties, pump shoes can be worn for almost any occasion. Pumps shoes are devoid of laces and buckles and cover the toe for protection and styling. From flat pumps to pumps with high heels, these shoes are evergreen style statements for almost any occasion. Nine West has twelve very different models in pump shoes and every model has received positive reviews from fashion critics and users alike.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The first model from the stable of Nine West is Dasa. This toe peeping model features heels of four inches with cross detailing at the front. The model comes in classic black color and looks perfect with any black short black dress or office attires. Flashbulb is another popular make from the brand coming in five very elegant colors. The design focuses on buckle and crisscrosses detailing and has heels measuring whopping 4.5 inches. Among all the colors, the blue satin make looks most stunning and spectacular. After featuring successfully in Teen Vogue, Noelia is high end designer shoes available for sale in official portal of Nine west. It comes in black color featuring 5inches heel and one inch platform heel at the front. Girls who love pointed pump shoes can check the OAKS model. This model is available in classic oak color and features a two inch heel. Designed for regular wear, this model can be teamed with many dresses. Another model with pointed toe along with high heels is Barbe. This three and half inches heel pump shoes can be worn by anyone with any dress without making any fashion blunder.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>In the range of heels with platform at the toe, Nadia is classic brown make with stacked heels measuring four inches. The Escher range is the most diverse range from Nine West. It features five different models with similar peep toe feature and four inch heel. The black colored model looks like transparent model made of netted material. There are other colors like Oak, Traupe, Croco, all having different looks and styling details. The Taketwo model from Nine West has featured in many magazines and is the best buy for those who seek ultimate levels of detailing. The model comes in black and white and has buckle detailing behind the ankle. Lexie is another model that deserves special mention in the series on pine shoes by Nine West. This is almond shaped model made of pure black leather and featuring heels of 4 inches. Simple and very detailed designing makes this a perfect party wear pump shoes. The all new Excite also is a fine model that has scaly detailing and comes from treasure house of Boutique 9. This perfect black shoe with 4 inches of heel with 3/4th inch of platform heel can make any lady look gorgeous at all occasions. For more knowledge and detailed pictures of Nine West pump shoes, customers can refer to the official website.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(11,1,11,1,'Nine West Maeble Ankle Boot',1,'<p>Ankle boots are pretty decent style statements and can be found for even the most modest budgets. When it comes to ankle boots, investing in the right brand is very important. Nine West is one such brand where customers put their faith without a doubt. This brand started off as a footwear manufacturing company selling some of the best designer shoes in the fashion world. The brand has a cult following around the globe currently and continues to create designs that get listed in many magazines and fashion listings. Maeble Ankle Boot from the company is hot favorite among fashionestas worldwide and definitely one of the best makes from the stable of Nine West.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Maeble Ankle Boot is a very casual design that aims at creating a simple uncluttered look. Funky and cool with the qualities of a classic, this model looks perfect with almost any attire. The leather upper features a smooth cut with toe designed for a rounded look. The complete look is further enhanced by rusty simple metallic embellishments on the back and sides. The outsole is made of thick rubber for great traction and durability. The side zipper allows easy stepping in and out in the smoothest way. This model can let the user be in complete ease even when travelling through the roughest routes. The shaft of Maeble ankle boot is around 7 inches which is very basic for any such make. The boot opening is 11inches and the model has heels that measure one inch. Nine West has ensured that the model works perfectly for styling and usage alike. Some of the colors come in suede as well like the dark green suede. Other colors include classic black, taupe and black in suede. Fashion gurus confess that black and brown makes are classics in any wardrobe and can be used for certain official occasions as well.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Like most other models of Nine West, this model too has been discounted since the first launch. Currently the model doesn’t feature in the official website of the brand and therefore needs to be purchased from other online shopping platforms. Customers can also contact the local dealer of the brand for ordering offline.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>On the whole, Maeble Ankle Boot from Nine West is definitely ‘the perfect buy’ of the season. Women, who love the endearing elegant look of ankle boots, will definitely adore this Nine West Boot.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(12,1,12,1,'Nine West Tierney Boots',1,'<p>Knee boots are very special in every woman’s wardrobe. These boots were initially used by people who always had to work in rough conditions. Knee boots provided protection from external damages like water, insects, mud etc. With time, fashion houses changed the concept by making these boots a fashion essential. Nine West is one such brand that has played a prime role in bringing knee high boots in fashion. With more than a dozen makes in the collection, the brand has ensured that these utility shoes become fashionable to the masses and classes alike. One of the best models that have come from the brand is Tierney.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Tierney is more of riding boot made in a classic cut. This model is made of pure leather with minimal detailing along the cuts. Being a riding boot, Tierney is a very durable model. The tough complete leather upper provides maximum protection on the outer side and is very soft in the inner side. In spite of being a tough make of shoes, this model is very easy to carry off. There is a half zip on the side for easy stepping in and stepping out. The cuts of the leather can be seen easily which makes the look even more appealing. Tierney is a low heel make featuring heels of one inch. The shaft of the model is around 15inches and the opening in the boot is around 12inches. This riding shoe can be worn efficiently with cardigans, pullovers or even miniskirts and jeans. The colors of the model are hugely dependant on the company stock. One color that gives natural leather feeling is brown.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Tierney is a very popular model from Nine West and therefore customers might or might not find it in company stock. The brand has an official website where one can buy the product online. In case a particular color is not available online, customers can check the retail outlets. Many online shopping outlets too have stocks of this model which can be bought at competitive prices.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>On the whole, this knee high shoe from Nine West is a perfect buy for those who seek style with the goodness of a classic. Designed for being stylish and chic, Tierney is a very performance oriented model that promises to be in fashion for years to come. Once the money invested, customers can rest assured that this make will last for many seasons.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(13,1,13,1,'Nine West Contico boot',1,'<p>Boots are ‘must have’ items in the wardrobe of every woman. In the ever changing and evolving world of fashion, there are only a few classics that can style up every season, and boots are definitely one of them. There are numerous brands that have experimented with boots and have come up with some really innovative designs for eternal use. Nine West is one such brand that has been a pioneer in redefining styles in boots. From simple boots to knee high heeled boots, the company has changed the way boots were previewed by fashion geeks. Contico boot from Nine West is a classic leather model that can be truly called a classic in every meaning of the world.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Contico has been specifically designed for women who love simple cuts without any lace detailing. This is like an organic knee high model that is devoid of any artificial embellishments. The leather or suede upper is highly comfortable and features simple cuts along the toe line. The outsole is made of rubber for extreme durability in the most rugged terrains. The simple ‘riveted buckle’ detail gives the model a very chic finish. The shaft height is approximately around seventeen inches with a boot opening of the same size. This is rather a very well heeled model featuring height of a little more than one inch. Contico comes with a promise that it will never let the user cripple, unlike high heeled models that lack in the comfort genre. There are three very dark shades available in the model. While the natural brown gives the ultimate leather feeling, the grey model is more about looking different. Best styled with jeans or skirt, this boot from Nine West is perfect for the upscale city woman and the perfect countryside girl alike.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Contico doesn’t feature in the online portal of Nine West and therefore customers have to contact the local dealer for the price and the model colors. There are many other online portals where the model is offered at different competitive prices. Customers can get lucky in getting special discounts in season or stock clearance sales. Contico has been named as one of the best knee high boots from the brand and is definitely a standard buy. This make from Nine West is clearly to stay for many seasons to come and defines the trendy yet evergreen look of modern women. </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(14,1,14,1,'Merrell refuge core',1,'<p>While choosing the hiking shoes it is very important to get the lightest boots that can manage the conditions and load which you expect out of them. Merrell Refuge Core offers excellent comfort, durability and traction on any kind of surface. These shoes are designed especially for summer and they help to keep the feet as cool and fresh as possible.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell Refugee Core shoes are soft but they have durable upper which is made from mesh fabric and nubuck rubber.  The upper also provide excellent breathability and helps to keep the interior environment fresh and dry.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Features of Merrell Refugee Core Shoes</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell Refugee Core shoes are comfortable and lightweight shoes. The midsole of the shoes have a shock absorbing layer of EVA cushion and a broad nylon plate under the arch. The stiff external molding look the heel in place and the underfoot air pad increases the support and cushion. Also these shoes have a rubber reinforcement on the on the cuff tie into the laces and enhance ankle stability.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>These shoes also have a Vibram sole low profile, runner like tread provide smooth trail striding and is gripped well on everything. Also these shoes have a Gore Tex technology which provides breathable and water proof comfort along with Agesis anti microbial solution which helps to resist odor.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The foot bed of these shoes is made up of Ortholite treated that helps to maximize the foot comfort. The foot bed also has an additional air cushioning at the heel which helps to deliver extra comfort and can stay on the feet for a long time. And because the outsole is made up of rubber which enables the traction irrespective of the surface type and helps to provide slip resistant and secure ride.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Thus Merrell Refugee Core shoes are light, comfortable and are available in various colors.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(15,1,15,1,'History of Merrell shoes',1,'<p>Merrell is Foot Wear Company which was established in 1981. It was founded by Clark Matis, John Schweitzer and a Randy Merrell. They were made to give high performance hiking shoes. These shoes were highly praised because of their high performance.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Evolution of Merrell Shoes</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The first pair was delivered into the market in 1983 and the first shipment was to the pair of east coast retailers. When the merrell shoes were first introduced to the market for the very first time they got exceptionally well response.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Within the first five years Randy J Merrell sold his share as he thought to return to the previous life i.e., as a maker of custom boots and in the same year the company sold 250,000th pairs. In 1987 Merrell was then purchased by Karhu which is a Finland based company. The company deals in manufacturing the sports equipments. And their first step was to reduce the cost and transfer the manufacturing systems to Asia. Under the management of Karhu, Merrell shoes got a chance to expand with full capacity and increase its sales and revenue.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>In 1997 Karhu sold Merrell to Wolverine World Wide which is a big name in the foot wear industry. The main advantage of the acquisition was the world wide increase in sales and only with the help of Wolverine it was possible to sell the shoes in 155 countries. Thus Wolverine helped Merrell in establishing a distinct name as there was a time when nobody knew about the Merrell.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>After its acquisition with Wolverine the sales of the company volume total of $23 million. Wolverine also introduced light weight footwear though these were not very successful but as a competition the team which was led by Clark Matis also came up with the same idea and introduced the same kind of shoes.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>In 2007 Merrell was again expanded and it started producing apparel and accessories and during the year 2010 Merrell products are being sold in 151 countries and the company has almost 116 stores around the world.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(16,1,16,1,'Merrell zinnia sandals',1,'<p>Merrell zinnia sandals are the lightweight, comfortable and durable sandals and can be your best friend in summers. These sandals are fun and functional as well as they are available in various colors.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell Zinnia sandals can be worn with skirts, jeans, trousers, Capri or with any other outfit. Because of their very comfortable interior these sandals can be worn all over the day without any discomfort.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Features of Zinnia Sandals</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Zinnia sandals provide your foot excellent comfort and keep the feet free from bacteria and odor. The upper part of the sandal is made up of nubuck leather which has the elastic which provide the secure fit. The elastic arch with toe delivers a simple and homely fit that stays on. It also has indulgent and antimicrobial foot bed with the durable cushion guarantee. The foot frame is made from EVA which is not only lightweight but also provides stability.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The mid sole of the sandals is made up from the Q-form EVA which helps to absorb the shocks and reduce the amounts of shocks which travel to the spine. Also the heel area of the sandals has the air cushion technology which also helps to reduce the fatigue. The outsole is made up rubber which is sticky and provide good grip on the wet and dry surface.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Also the cement construction of the sandals makes these sandals light weight and durable and the slip on construction also helps to walk fast and effortless on and off wearing. The lining of the sandals is made up from the pig skin which helps to draw the moisture away from the feet and keep them soft and healthy and is soft as well.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell Zinnia Sandals are available in various cute colors. They are very comfortable and stylish though they are little pricy but they have a fashion appeal. Thus these sandals have a wow factor with the substantial quality.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(17,1,17,1,'Merrell hiking shoes',1,'<p>Merrell hiking shoes are the popular choice among hikers and even among the newcomers in hiking. Merrell hiking shoes are meant for high mountain crossings and heavy loads. They are designed by keeping performance in the mind and they are faster and comfortable. These shoes are even popular among people with back and leg problems.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Most of the people often remark Merrell as the most comfortable shoes they have ever owned.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Hiking Shoes/Boots</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell has the large catalogue for the hiking boots and these shoes are the right choice as per your taste and budget. Merrell shoes are provided with Gore Tex technology that will protect the feet from water and from blisters. These shoes help to protect the feet from both warm and wet weather.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell boots also helps to keep the feet dry and gives them air to breathe. They also have antimicrobial shield that protect the feet from bacteria and fungi. They are good in both design as well as quality. Thus these shoes are the best hiking boots and they are perfectly fit, light weight and supportive and also they provide grip and help the feet to breathe.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell shoes are the comfortable shoes and by purchasing these boots you will not be disappointed. They help to keep the feet comfortable, dry and can be worn for long hours without any difficulty. Also these shoes have Vibram sole that offers good grip in various hiking conditions. The Vibram sole last for the longer time and provide more grip than standard rubber soles as more grip gives more confidence.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The only complain with these shoes are only with its lacing system which is very fragile and tricky. Other than that these boots are the perfect choice than any other boots and are the most sold hiking boots in the U.S. Merrell shoes are durable and can withstand almost anything and are the lightest and most comfortable shoes. </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(18,1,18,1,'Merrell sonic glove',1,'<p>Merrell sonic glove shoe is very much similar to merrell trail glove shoe. Therefore we can say that Merrell sonic glove shoe is trail glove shoe but it is constructed with soft- shell upper instead of open mesh. Thus the new upper gives the Sonic Glove more of a substantial feel and the closed upper material helps to keep out both the debris and moisture.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell has also modified the lining on the interior of the shoe in the region around the mid foot. As in the Trail Glove shoe they used nylon like material which caused blistering when worn without the socks whereas this material is absent in Merrell Sonic Glove Shoes.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Features of Sonic Glove Shoes</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Sonic Glove shoes are the ideal shoes to run barefoot. They have breathable, flexible soft shell upper molds on the foot by pulling the moisture out and keep them dry. Also the Vibram sole and the minimal cushioning underfoot give you close to ground protection and the traction for unlimited adventure. These shoes are available in different colors.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The upper lining of the shoes is made up of textile and the microfiber foot bed which is treated with Agesis anti microbial solution which helps to resist the odor. Also the Merrell Omni fit lacing system help to provide a precise glove like fit. They have about 1 mm forefoot shock absorption plate which maintains fore foot flexibility and protect the foot by distributing the pressure.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The performance of the Sonic Glove shoes is pretty much good but these shoes are little bit warmer than the trail glove shoes hence it is difficult to run in them on a hot day. Thus these shoes are ideal option to run barefoot style shoe in winter season. They perform even better in cold and wet conditions. They actually help to block the water entry completely which is the amazing feature of Merrell Sonic Shoes.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(19,1,19,1,'Merrell Moab Ventilator',1,'<p>Merrell Moab ventilator shoe is one of the greatest shoe and they cater to the fun adventures of the outdoors. They are the best shoes for the people who want to enjoy their time. Thus merrell Moab ventilator shoes can be considered right shoes as they also have a specialty in providing lightweight hiking and trial wear.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell Moab shoes have various advanced and unique features which makes them a perfect choice.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Features of Merrell Moab Ventilator</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell Moab Ventilator shoes are made up of durra leather/nylon ventilator mesh upper which provide the ample amount of breathability, flexibility as well as support and thus provide long lasting performance. They also have protective rubber toe bumpers which ensure durability and provide resistance.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell ventilator shoes are provided with full length compression molded EVA midsole which provide cushioning and support for all day wear. Also the air cushion heel pockets provide extra shock absorption under heels and stabilize the foot strike. These shoes also provide full bumper protection around the toe and around the heel as well and the TC5 rubber present in the shoes compound for grip and durability. Like other merrell shoes Merrell Moab ventilator shoes are also treated with the Agesis antimicrobial solution which maintains the foot comfort.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The Vibram multi sport outsole with Trek and super Trek rubber delivers the reliable traction on both wet and dry surfaces. They also have removable foot beds which are anatomically shaped and add cushioning for improved comfort. Merrell Moab ventilator also have the nylon mesh lining which not only absorb moisture but also disperse excess moisture and provide more comfortable feel in hot conditions.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Therefore Merrell Moab shoes are considered to be the summer essential as they have excellent qualities in each pair and also they make sure that they provide quality and comfort which you deserve. They are not only preferred by the casual hiker but also casual walker. Also these shoes are extremely comfortable.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(20,1,20,1,'merrell xcr shoes',1,'<p>Merrell XCR shoes are the trail shoes that are lightweight and are designed mainly to provide athletic performance with waterproof construction. They are easy trail hiking shoes through sun and the shower.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>These shoes are great looking multipurpose shoes which are extremely comfortable at all range of temperatures. Also these shoes can be worn at any range of temperature which will help to keep away the feet from becoming too hot or cold.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Features of Merrell XCR shoes</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell XCR shoes provide high level of breathability and also provide the water proof protection to the feet. These shoes not only provide breathability and flexibility but also offer support for long lasting performance. The Mesh padded tongues also protect against the lace pressure without inhibiting breathability. They are also provided with removable anatomic foot beds that add cushioning and provide extra comfort.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The Vibram multisport outsoles help to deliver the reliable traction on both dry and wet surfaces. These shoes also offer great comfort and stability on uneven trials and pavements. The midsole of the shoes are made up of compression-molded EVA and injection molded nylon arch with pronounced heel cups that helps to cushion and centre the feet.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell XCR shoes have the Air cushion midsole and anatomical foot bed which