te as these shoes provide enough protection with providing the ground feel and prevent from the injury. Also the tread works very well in large range of terrain from hard packed dirt to sand.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell trail glove shoes because of their light weight and flexibility make the shoes minimal fatiguing. Thus these shoes have characteristics which make the shoes more desirable. They have some characteristics which are ideal for the barefoot runners. These shoes can be used on the difficult terrain and whether conditions. They work excessively well both in snow and mud. Therefore the trail glove shoes are ideal for barefoot running and are available in different colors.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(22,1,22,1,'Merrell shoes for women',1,'<p>The Merrell shoes are available in the market for both men and women. They are popular because of their styles. Merrell shoes are available in both casual as well as athletic style.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell shoes addresses all kinds of needs and are meant for all kind of activities and environment i.e., natural as well as urban.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Women Merrell Shoes</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell shoes for women are made especially for women and they just adore the shoes. They are designed in such a way that they can stand whatever is put through them. They are durable and fantastic to look. Merrell provides fantastic range of lady wear shoes.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell shoes provide light weight walking and hiking shoes for women. They are light weight and robust. Merrell shoes have designed the women shoes by keeping in mind the feminine colors and slim design. They are the most attractive shoes in the market.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell women shoes are one of the bestselling brands not only because of their light weight and design but also because of the fact that they offer comfortable shoes. They offer comfort and protect the feet from any painful blisters. The shoes also help to wrap the foot in such a way that they help to feel more secure and restrictive.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Women Merrell shoes are different from the shoes manufactured by other manufacturers because of they take the size of the average foot and try to make the same available in smaller size for the women. But actually the women feet are narrower and these shoes do not fit them properly and cannot hold the feet properly thus cause the blisters. Thus Merrell shoes while manufacturing the shoes keep these things in mind thus making them different from other shoes manufacturers.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell shoes provide Gore Tex shoes for women as they are waterproof and help to keep the feet dry. Thus Merrell shoes are excellent in walking and are available in wide variety of colors and styles. </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(23,1,23,1,'Merrell glove shoes',1,'<p>Merrell glove shoe are the minimalist trial shoes which stimulates the barefoot style of running. These shoes can be worn without socks and are the best for those who are looking for ultra minimal shoes.\nThe Merrell gloves shoes are bit conservative in terms of looks and their appearance is bit subdued but attractive and these shoes do not likely tend to turn off the heads despite of the fact that they are barefoot style of shoes.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Features of Merrell Glove Shoes</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell shoes are the high quality shoes but the Merrell glove shoes are the shoes which tend to fit in your budget. These shoes are made very well and are highly durable. These shoes are free from any manufacturing defects. The toe box of these shoes is very wide thus they help to provide enough room during the run. The shoe is also suitable for the sockless running.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The heel and the forefoot of the shoes are bit rounded from the inner to the outer margin and this makes the shoe a bit unstable underfoot when you are standing still on them. Also these shoes are the zero drop shoes. The performance of the Merrell glove shoes is also good. They are also very comfortable to run on snow and prevents from slipping. The traction present in these shoes is also very good and is zero drop shoes as they are quite easy to maintain thus these shoes are typical running shoes.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell glove shoes are very comfortable on the road and these shoes are thus the excellent choice. These shoes fit more consistently and it feels like as if they have locked down the feet better and the midsole and Vibram outsole provide more support. Also these shoes are designed in such a way that they can be worn without socks and have a smooth rubber inside which prevent blistering. Therefore these shoes provide confidence, support and protection on the rocky area thus these shoes help to enjoy to the fullest.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(24,1,24,1,'What to wear with black merrell shoes',1,'<p>Merrell shoes are available in different colors, designs and patterns and these shoes are very popular among the people of all age groups. They are popular because of their style, comfort, quality and appearance. These shoes are available in various colors like black, grey and also in the combination of various colors.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Black Merrell shoes looks trendy, cool and stylish. These shoes are the must have in the wardrobe. And there are various styles and range of Black Merrell like Knee high shoes, glove shoes, and various other sports and casual wear shoes.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>What to wear</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Black Merrell can be worn with denim jeans, trouser, shorts, skirts and Capri. With the Black Merrell you can choose blue or black jeans with a t-shirt. A combination of black white shoes needs no praises. Also these shoes go well with anything and everything.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Women can also tend to wear the black merrell shoes with skinny jeans and a t-shirt. One can also play with colors and wear it with fabulous color contrast as they look great with color matching. Women also use some accessories like necklace, bangles and earrings as they look great as a combination. They help to provide maximum comfort and ease.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Black Merrell shoes can be worn with black or dark blue jeans with t-shirt or shirt of your choice. T-shirt can be of any kind like graphic, v-neck, round neck or any other kind. These shoes can be worn with any kind of dresses like classic, traditional or authentic.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell shoes can also be worn throughout the day as these shoes are very comfortable and quality shoes. They look cool and also provide a great fit. Thus these shoes can be worn on any occasion with any kind of dresses. They are not only meant for office wear but also can be used for the casual wear. </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(25,1,25,1,'How to clean merrell shoes',1,'<p>Merrell shoes are worn not only by the outdoor enthusiasts or comfort seekers but also by the people who are fashion forward consumers. Thus these shoes require very good care of the footwear to free it from stains, smells and other mishaps that occur to the shoes through daily wear.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Cleaning of the Merrell shoes regularly will help to ensure the longevity, durability and appearance of the shoes over the years.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>How to clean Merrell Shoes</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>It is very important to remove the dirt and debris of the shoe by brushing it regularly and by brushing away any material on the surface of the shoe or boot. Also it is very important that for any stains and blemishes wash the shoes with a mild soap and warm water.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>There are several cleaners and detergents which are available in the market and can be used to clean the Merrell. Also try an all purpose shoe cleaner to clean the spots on suede, leather, rubber, canvas, vinyl or anything else. It is very important to clean the shoes with bar and brush.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>In order to dry the shoes the shoes can be placed in a well ventilated area which is away from direct source of heat. Also remember to remove the laces and insole if the Merrell have and open the shoe as much as you can for optimum drying.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>To keep the shoes stain free proper conditioning of the footwear in recommended. Depending on the material of the shoe use appropriate material to keep the shoes in a good shape and apply a water and stain repellent spray to the shoe in a good shape.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>It is also very important to keep in mind while drying hiking boots or leather footwear that not to keep them near fire or other heat sources for quick drying as it can crack leather. And also string the Merrell shoes in damp locations is not recommended.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(26,1,26,1,'Knee high merrell boots',1,'<p>Knee high boots are the boots which are worn below the knee cap. Women love to wear the boots with pants like men and these boots can be even worn with short skirt with the stockings. These boots are available in unique colors and styles. Women’s love to buy these knee cap boots.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Knee high boots can be made up from leather, synthetic rubber, vinyl or the combination of materials which are made up from polyvinyl carbonate family. These boots can be given plain look with the help of water or they can be made ultra glossy for the party wear look.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Features Of Knee High boots</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>These boots are designed with various fastening devices. They can be easily zipped, buckled, laced or can be easily worn over the stockings. They are also available with heels and it can be a platform heel, flat heels or boots with chunky heels etc.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Knee high boots can be worn not only at work but also they can be worn after work. And these are also meant for people who love outdoor activities as these boots provide double protection. Also these boots are versatile and can be worn all over the year.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>They also help the feet to stay dry at times when it is raining outside as there are waterproof knee high boots which are also available. These boots are not only waterproof but also they are sexy and classy also they are durable and reliable as well. These boots looks great with winter jacket and are soft and plush as well.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Knee high boots may look tough from outside but they will help to protect the feet to the fullest and also keep it dry.  They are very comfortable but are bit hard to get and are but pricy but have good quality. Also these boots look great with jeans as well as skirt.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(27,1,27,1,'Merrell intercept Gore Tex',1,'<p>Merrell intercept gore-tex shoes have Merrell air cushion midsole to cushion your feet at every step. These shoes are very ideal for moderate or warmer conditions and the Gore tex provide extended comfort to the shoes and keep the feet dry and protected with guaranteed waterproofness and enhanced breathability. \nMerrell intercept Gore-tex shoes are also provided with an injection molded arch shank along with the in board compression molded EVA foot frame to provide added support. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Features of Merrell Gore-Tex shoes</h3> \n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell intercept gore-tex shoes are provided with cutting edge technology along with the modern styling coverage for durable and all condition performance. Also they have Gore-Tex waterproof breathable lining bonds to the synthetic leather upper to play defense against moisture inside out. \nThe anatomical foot bed and the air cushion midsole score point for lightness and comfort. These shoes have much more athletic touch in them and also these shoes fits more like a running shoes. The shoes are much cooler and this is because of the numerous vents which are present in the shoes and helps in running down the side of the shoe.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Also the vents of the shoes are protected by the Gore-Tex bootie that is sandwiched between the internal constructions of the shoe and it also helps to keep the moisture out and allows the shoe to breathe. The Merrell intercept shoes have more cushioning and they are very comfortable and they have an aggressive sole lug design that shed mud and clumpy dirt a lot.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Therefore Merrell Gore-Tex shoes provide breathable and waterproof fabric. They are most rated because of their style and quality. These shoes also provide magnificent style and quality and because of their performance they are considered to be the best selling Merrell price. These shoes can be used with the casual outfit and can be worn while running, hiking, walking and even tracking as these shoes offer ultimate comfort and keep the feet protected.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(28,1,28,1,'Merrell flip flops',1,'<p>Merrell flip flops are the sandals that are provided with a piece of material separating the big toe and the second toe and then the attached to the sole on the sides of the foot to secure the shoes. Also the flip flops are made up of rubber or rubber type material.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>These sandals are available in different colors and styles and also are considered to be the most comfortable sandals. They are highly recommended for those who are looking out for a casual sandal that is stylish as well as super comfortable.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Features of Merrell flip flops</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell flip flop sandals are easily removable padded back strap with the slide form and one can easily close it with hook/loop straps. The sidewalls of the sandals are very well ventilated and also provide full support along with the length of the whole foot. They are provided with 3D design to seat the foot with comfort and are anti microbial footed as well.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>These sandals also come with nylon flex plate protection and air cushion midsole. The antimicrobial foot bed provides the feet with the quality ventilation and thus they are the great option. They come with antimicrobial support that makes the footwear endurable for the hot weather. The top side of the flip flops has a synthetic leather strap which displays attention while grabbing the stitched detail and the bottom of the shoe has air cushion which helps to absorb shock and adds stability.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell flip flops are not only fun and stylish but also comfortable. Merrell flip flop sandals embody the free spirit of fashion and easy living. Also these sandals are available for the people of any age group. Therefore it can be concluded that the Merrell flip flops possess both technology and styling which adds both comfort and styling to your day. The minimalist design also conceals the dedicated patterned microfiber and wrapped foot bed that provide soft touch and is treated with Agesis anti microbial solution.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(29,1,29,1,'Merrell Encore Ballet',1,'<p>Merrell Encore Ballet is the beautiful casual shoes provided by Merrell. These shoes are made up of Nubuck leather and mesh upper with contrast stitching and rounded toe for fun and sporty appeal. Also these shoes have slip on construction with padded heel along with hook and loop strap across the toe to provide easy and secure fit.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Ballet shoes have mesh lining which is treated with Agesis antimicrobial solution to resist the odor and keep the feet fresh. Also the Q form EVA foot frame and nylon arch shank and air cushion midsole to absorb shock and to reduce the fatigue.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Features of Merrell Encore Ballet</h3> \n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>These shoes are so magnificent that you will not be able to stop dancing once you wear the shoes. Also these shoes not only look stunning and adorable but also they provide extreme level of comfort. They are not only light weight but also have excellent built quality which helps to wear them for a long time.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>As the upper of the shoe is made up of mesh and nubuck leather and the combination of both provide durability and breathability which help to keep the feet in complete comfort zone. Also the upper of the shoe has a prominent stitch detailing on the top that help to enhance the look and the round toe design provide good room for toe.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>These shoes are provided with the slip on design that helps to wear them quickly. The heel is provided with additional padded to prevent the shoe against ankle discomfort. Also the lining of the shoe made up of mesh which not only provide breathability but also helps to keep it fresh. The foot frame of the shoe is made up of Q-form EVA and the material is designed especially for women by keeping in mind the comfort of women and also to keep women’s protected all the time.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Thus Merrell Encore Ballet provides support for better walking and prevents the shock from travel to legs and spine.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(30,1,30,1,'Merrell Nursing shoes',1,'<p>As hospitals are run by the feet of the nurses and nurses put on the shoes for long hours on the feet thus Merrell nursing shoes are the best option to wear. These shoes help them to keep up during the day and are comfortable, durable and also offer degree of protection.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell nursing shoes work as hard as you do. They have full waterproof full grain leather uppers and Merrell encore sticky rubber sole for grip and traction even on the wet surfaces. Also these shoes are available in various colors, style, designs and patterns.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Features of Merrell Nursing shoes</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell nursing shoes have sticky rubber sole which provide grip and traction even on the wet surfaces. They also provide comfort as they have air cushion midsole present in them. They are provided with Dri-Lex Shubuck lining anatomically molded foot bed with antimicrobial foot lining.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell medical shoes are provided with water resistant pigskin leather upper, heavy nylex moisture management lining and elastic bands which help for easy on and off, Merrell Nursing shoes are also equipped with Q-form alignment system which helps to provide whole day comfort and support.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell nursing shoes are very lightweight and flexible. They also look amazing and can be easily worn all over the day at work. The quality of these shoes beats any other sneakers brands and can be worn like sneakers. They are made up of high quality leather that breathes and also allows moisture to escape unlike plastic. Also the outsole of the shoes give flexibility and shock absorption and allows you to stand up in extreme hot and cold and protect your feet, back and legs when you have to stand for a long time.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Thus Merrell Nursing shoes are designed specifically by keeping nurses in mind. These shoes are not only comfortable, durable, provide perfect fit but also they look fashionable as well as trendy and stylish.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(31,1,31,1,'merrell vibram shoes',1,'<p>Merrell is a leading brand in outdoor footwear and apparel. It is known because of its comfort, versatility and Vibram. Merrell is also a world leader in advance performance sole design and is well known for its five fingers barefoot concept. It is a minimalist, lightweight versatile and efficient footwear.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell Vibram shoes help to create a natural stride by moving you away from the