ievement in women wear.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell Q-form shoes are light and durable with a stylish feminine touch. These shoes have style as well as performance like outdoor shoes. Thus these shoes have quality which makes it a perfect investment.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Features</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell Q form shoes are equipped with the ground breaking technology with the sequenced cushioning with supportive midsole to give it a technology which is tailored to women and the way they move. Because as per the research it has already been proved that women have different stride when compared to men and it evolves running and walking. The midsole of the shoes are made up of Q form technology which is designed to keep their delicate feet super comfortable.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Women’s Q- angle is more prominent due to the fact that they have wider pelvis and lower centre of gravity. And due to the pronounced Q-angle the initial strike of the heel tends to be concentrated outside the foot. Thus as a result it causes additional stress is caused on the ligament which provide great discomfort to the individual.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell has come up with this Q-form technology which has proven to be a successful technology. With the proper support and by redirecting the gait of the women it can remove discomfort, minimize over correction and even reduce wear and tear on the shoe by providing an even wear factor. The Q-form is molded midsole with the three separate degree of firmness. When it is combined with patented air cushion the system directs a women stride with more fluid and a balanced process which results in extended comfort and stability.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Merrell Q-form shoes are designed especially for women and are lightweight, breathable and provide a flexible support.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(34,1,34,1,'Merrell chameleon 3 stretch',1,'<p>Merrell Chameleon 3 stretch shoes are a great s