ring of New Balance shoes is to check their official portal which contains many small tips and information about keeping the shoes in good condition.  </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Suede shoes are sort of these shoes which do have some trendy look. They tend to attract more dirt while being fussy themselves rather than clear shoes. These shoes typically need more attention since they cannot be wetted at all. Brushing off of the stains with a toothbrush might be useful. Regular brushing may also help keep the coating and effectiveness of the shoes. Hard stains might need significant stain removers available in the market. Even the company itself gives away suede cleaning solutions.<br />\nSoles of the shoes are also tremendously prestigious to be kept clean. Old toothbrushes, that have worn, out a bit and get aggressive, can be the perfect tool choice for cleaning shoe soles. A little bit of grease and cleaning solution will be binding while you are cleaning soles of a shoe. New Balance has recently introduced cleansing products for us and, therefore, we do not require going searching about in the market. The Oxyclean paste is a remarkably compelling product and scrubbing the soles of shoes with this paste will do a tremendous job. Simple cleansers too can work in case cleansing products of the company is not available nearby.  </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Leather shoes are highly sensitive. Therefore they need some convincing care at a regular interval. Shoe polish is the best choice for leather shoes. Shoe polishes recommend a reasonable deal of use in cleaning leather shoes. Mild damage and dirt marks are regularly cleaned rather leave hidden, once the shoes are polished. But, this implies that customers need to find out a complete color matching perfectly with the color of the shoe, or maybe something close to that. One of the biggest points, to keep in mind while polishing leather shoes is that, the shoes must not be in a damp or wet environment. With these simple techniques, caring for new balance shoes becomes a fairly easy task.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(47,1,47,1,'New balance golf shoes',1,'<p>A golf player needs certain paraphernalia to set the perfect mood in a golf course. Most importantly, the player must feel comfortable with his wear for the correct strokes. The golfer needs to slip in the prefect comfortable couple of shoes on the field. New balance is a shoe corporation that excels in the production of one of the finest golf footwear in the global market. Founded in the primary 1900’s, this company kicked off in the market for arch support mechanisms; with the advancement of the world, the firm have emerged as the leading athlete wear manufacturer.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>This brand of shoes is released in the market with a particular identification number. In the recent past they have come up to the market of golf wears. Shoes of the golfing range are available in two series’; the former 1250 one as well as the latter and brand new 1275 one. These shoes are contrived from full grain leather. The sole of the golf shoes from New Balance are made of solid rubber. The available colors of these shoes are white and black; at times they are given a corporate look of a combo of black as well as white. The golf shoes are sophisticated, classy, apart from being sturdy as well as robust.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The golf shoes are obtainable both for men as well as women. It should be kept in mind to buy the right pair of shoes for a golfer. The right pair means, the one in which the golfer fits well. This is urgent as the golfer need to walk around for taking the flawless shots, and one needs to be very much comfortable during the proceedings of a match. New Balance manufactures shoes of all varieties of widths as well as lengths unlike a lot of other companies; so for those who want to opt for good golf shoes with proper fittings along with the impeccable comforts, can come forward to fetc