tion and therefore the name of the brand is very important. New Balance has come up with range of shoes that have been designed with the best technologies for the budding feet. In the infant category, there are 23 models priced within a small budget of 40 USD. KV686PKI is the standard model that features ‘ABZORB® cushioning’ for mid sole support and has a ‘rubber cup’ outsole for outdoor durability. KV993PKI and KV993NVI are similar models with ‘hook and loop’ closure for complete fitting without laces. Most models come in different colors for girls and boys. While pinks are common for girls, boys have choices in grey, blues and oranges. KG632SBI is perfect model for kids who always to love to play. Standard features include ‘Rubber Cup Outsole’, mesh upper, ‘IMEVA (injection-molded EVA foam) midsole’ and ‘Hook and Loop closure’. In the running shoe category for kids, New Balance model number KJ688BOI is a runaway hit. Designed for comfort for day long activities, this simple model is high on style and quality. Other good models from New Balance come from model variations of KJ993 with standard features.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>While browsing for Pre-School category, customers must have a look at the model numbers because same model come in different colors for girls and boys. All the models are priced below 60USD and have standard feature of New Balance shoes. The first model with good rating is KV993NVP. It has a mesh upper which makes the model very breathable. It has a rubber cup outsole with ‘hook and loop closure’ for better fitting and durability. ‘ABZORB® cushioning’ is a sharp feature of the brand that helps in ultimate shock absorption and is included in most models of pre-school shoes. KV993 is also a popular model available in many colors. It has special highlights like sizing for all ages with ‘N-ergy®’ for providing highest levels of advanced shock absorption. The midsole consist of ‘IMEVA (injection-molded EVA foam)’ for firm cushioning. KV687 and KV688 are also genuine models of the brand in this category.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>There is also a grade school category where one can find vibrant colors and makes similar to the advanced models of adult shoes. Priced much lower than similar brands, New Balance kids shoes for grade category have maintained the highest levels of quality and standards. KV687 and KV688 are standard numbers having large variations in colors and designs. From the simple pinks with whites and blacks for girls to grey and black shades for boys, New Balance has vast collection at disposal for every type of customer. The official website of the brand can suffice the customer with all the queries and searches around the brand.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(58,1,57,1,'New Balance walking shoes',1,'<p>Walking is probably the best exercise for all ages and keeping this simple fact in mind, New Balance has designed extensive range of walking shoes for men and women. The company, established in the twentieth century, has turned out to be one of the leading sellers of walking shoes on the globe. New Balance walking shoes come in different categories like ‘motion control’, ‘stability’, ‘cushioning’ and is further categorized for fitness, toning and countryside walking.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>In the women’s category, there are many options that start in the modest prices of 50USD. In the ‘motion control’ category, the most valued product by users is New Balance 811. This model has been designed for women who love the feeling of being barefooted while walking. With the standardized ROLLBAR® along with Medial &amp; Lateral TPU Posts for ultimate motion control, this model comes in many colors. New Balance 850 is another model in ‘true balance’ category that comes in very girly color combinations like pink &amp; white and pink &amp;black. For giving a firm grip and ensuring ultimate levels of outsole durability, this model uses registered Ndurance® rubber compound along with ABZORB® cushioning for shock absorption. Women who like to find shoes with the blend of class, style and comfort, Aravon Farren can be a perfect buy. It has ‘Full Ground Contact Outsole’ for highest levels of comfort. Other good models in the motion control category include New Balance 927 and New Balance 846. These are very light weight walking shoes priced within 150 USD.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>New Balance walking shoes range for men is much more diverse and vast. Most shoes are priced within 150USD, thus catering to most customers in the global market without any compromises on quality and comfort. There are three sections in men’s range namely country, fitness and toning. In the fitness section, customers have options of buying models that are designed for cushioning, motion controlling. Some of the popular models in motion control section of New Balance walking shoes include New balance 927, New balance 812. All the models in this section feature the ROLLBAR® which gives the highest level of motion control and ABZORB® SBS foam for excellent chock absorbing. In the light weighted shoes, customers have New Balance 10 as the perfect buy within 100USD. These models have been designed with highest levels of research for barefoot feeling and can be worn comfortably without socks. In the cushioning section, New Balance 512 is basic standard buy with features like ABZORB® cushioning for shock absorption, outsole designed with slip resistant, IMEVA midsole for firm support. In the toning models of shoes, there is ‘true balance model 850’ which has emerged as one of the popular buys. ABZORB® cushioning with a solid rubber outsole makes it one of the most comfortable shoes from the stable of New Balance.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>New Balance walking shoes can be purchased from the wide network of dealers or online through their official site. For better discounts, customers can look into retailer’s site and find authentic dealers.    </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(59,1,58,1,'New Balance shoes for women',1,'<p>New Balance is a brand that has been synonymous with quality, durability and comfort. It offers numerous models in men’s, women’s and kid’s category for sport or non-sport needs. New Balance shoes for women have over 150 models in various categories, all designed with latest technologies and infused with some excellent trademark features. There are categories like lifestyle, outdoor, running, waking, toning, training and there are numerous designed specifically for every purpose. In the lifestyle category, there are twelve exclusive models in the price range of 50-100USD. Simple models include WL773WST (which features ‘EVA (Ethyl Vinyl Acetate) foam midsole’ for extra cushioning), WL474WS (lightweight model with a retro look, S410SSC (for simple straight fit with high comfort levels), WL773SR (the racing comp of New Balance minus the spikes), WL773SP (same racing comp with excellent upper and outsole for ultimate styling and comfort).</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>New Balance outdoor shoes for women have twelve models priced higher that the lifestyle category. Outdoor models are further categorized as trail, country walking, multi-sport and light hiking. In the trail category, there are five models each priced in and around 100USD. Some models are WT20 (features ‘ACTEVA* midsole* for higher levels of flexibility and cushioning), WT10 Minimus Trail (Similar to WT20 with durable <em>Vibram outsole</em> and <em>minimalist upper</em>), WT560 (designed especially for women who love to style with trail shoes off the trail as well). In the country walking category, there are three models - WW977, WO1520 and WO650. WW977 is known for being the best waterproof shoe from the stable of New Balance. Designed for the outdoor enthusiast women, this model features GORE-TEX® fabric known for durability. WO650 has mesh upper for a supportive fit and comfort cushioning and is priced moderately for budget constrained customers. There are similar models in light hiking and multi-sport category as well.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>New Balance shoes for women offers 26 different models in running shoes. Further subdivided in categories like training, off road, racing comps, track and field, running shoes from this brand can be trusted blindly for quality and comfort. Some of the priced models in training category include WR1012 (designed for professional runners featuring ‘ACTEVA* Midsole*, <em>N-ergy®</em> for shock absorption) and WR993 (featuring ABZORB® DTS and ABZORB® SBS). In the training shoes category, WX1011 is good model having features like <em>ACTEVA</em> LITE premium lightweight midsole*, <em>SURE LACE</em> secure shoe laces* and <em>N-ergy®</em>. There are 29 exclusive models in women<em>s walking shoes category from New Balance. Most models can be found in other categories like running as well. WX1210 is a good model in the walking shoes category including features like LockDown Liner</em>, ABZORB® DTS, ACTEVA*, ABZORB® SBS and ABZORB®. On the whole, New Balance shoes for women meet the diverse sports and walking needs of customers in terms of features in a very flexible price band. The best place to shop for New Balance shoes is to browse on the web on the online official portal. There are also authentic dealers of the brand who sell the products in many global markets and shipping costs may be applicable as per location.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(60,1,59,1,'How to lace new balance shoes',1,'<p>New Balance manufacturers are one of the leading giants in shoe designing and marketing, in the United States. They claim to be among the top four productions in the United States and the top five in the whole world. They are famous for their shoes manufacturing and specialize in sports shoes. They say that they are the only company that is still continuing manufacturing their goods in the United States. Their prime product being shoes for athletes, they are doing a marvelous deal of business at the moment. They have a wide range of varieties, and most of all their collection is not limited to a genre. They manufacture for men, women and youngsters, as well. Covering a wide range of sports like football, baseball, yoga, running, walking and etc, they are a complete package solution for any athlete. But, in order that we get the best experience of these marvelous shoes, we must lace them well enough to get the perfect feel and comfort.  </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>First, we need to throw the laces straight, right up to the toe end. The laces will reach the shoe eyelets. Tuck them through the eyelets and then get them straight by pulling them together. Keep straightening the laces until they come up to be of the equal sizes. Next, cross the shoe laces, in the form of an X. After this, pull the laces up, as if to get them, tightened. Now try the next eyelet. Run the lace through the next eyelet again. We need to make sure that the laces are all of equal length and that they are tightly knit to the eyelets. Now, cross the outer part of the laces and then re tie it to form an X again. Make sure to form a knot and tie it hard. Continue, repeating the above steps, and pushing the laces in, and out of the eyelets. Finally, we reach the tongue of the shoe and complete our process of enclosing the whole shoe with the knots. The final eyelet is still free from the X knot. This eyelet can also have a knot depending on your personal choice of fittings. You can select to have a tight fit around your ankle or a loose one. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>For those who prefer to have tight one, they can make the final X knot in the last eyelet. Tie the knot on the top position; this will help you get a tighter fit. Finally, we must tie the full knot to get our shoe tightly fitted to our feet. If we have a pain in our feet or some toe problem, then we must follow a slightly different mechanism for the wearing process. The knots that we were making will be skipped at regular intervals. For example, if we start off with the bottom most eyelets, then the next X knot will be in the third and fourth eyelet. The next two knots will be in the sixth and seventh eyelet. This loose knotting process will give us a loose fit. Tying the laces of New Balance shoes in style is not that of a hard task.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(61,1,60,1,'what to wear with black new balance shoes',1,'<p>Black has been a classy color since ages and men have always preferred black. Be it the ethnic glamour or a corporate mood, black serves the best in every purpose. In older days, women used to fantasize pretty colors like reds and all; but with modernization and involvement of women in the corporate world, tastes have changed. Ladies seem to prefer black even more and black have turned out to be the diva color both for men as well as women. Black brings out a sophistical hue and makes style transpire. Even in movies, it can be seen that the glam icons, attired in black. This color never gets outdated. Similarly black shoes can be worn with a variety of outfits almost in every occasion.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>A black tuxedo, teamed with a nicely knotted tie along with a pair of New Balance black shoe is the perfect dress for almost every occasion. It can be easily worn on a business event. It is not necessary to wait for an occasion to feel a pair of black New Balance; regular wears are available which looks perfect apart from the office wears, i.e. a nice shirt and a trouser. The black New Balance shoes look awesome when teamed with trendy casuals; this can be the flawless outfit for a high-school party or probably a graduation treat.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>New Black shoes are attainable at a variety of price ranges; it is therefore suggested that a couple of pairs are bought so that one can have office wears separated from the occasion wears. A black New Balance is good to couple with tees and denims to make the perfect attire for a night out at a club. These black shoes are the best for hangouts as scratches as well as imperfections are best hidden in blacks. These black leathers are the best pertaining to regular use as they remain stylish and look cool on every outfit.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Women can team denims with funky and trendy T-shirts to match the clubbing environment. Girls are often to team leather trousers and jackets with black shoes. Black gives the ultimate touch of style even to a fading outfit. If this is the style sense then opting for a nice pair of new balance black is the best option. These shoes makes a person look elegant as well as smart owing to the confidence that is attained through the comfort in the dress.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>These shoes can be teamed with a decent tuxedo and can be worn on funerals. These black shoes are available at a number of stores at various prices. Style experts have come forward on the internet to share their views as well as ideas about the dresses that goes well with the black New Balance ones. The official website of new balance is associated with various styling brand who can give enhanced suggestions on what to wear with a New Balance black. One should also try to mix and match and do some experimentation with the outfits and a black New Balance to get on the heights of styling and fashion.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(62,1,61,1,'born flip flops for men',1,'<p>Flip flops as well as sandals are the most comfortable footwear. A good casual look can be sported with a classic yet fashionable pair of flip flop brings out a glamorous look in a casual one. It is therefore suggested to purchase flip flops from reputed brands. Born shoes are one among the top rated firms that sew exclusively durable, yet comfortable, nevertheless cool and funky spontaneous footwear. This footwear firm has received a world-class excellence appreciation from all its custo