sual looks turns out to be elegant with a crown Monroe one. The Windsor class of Born men’s flip-flops is a stylish one with an ethnic combo. The Nero shade, Thong sandal can be a world-class experience for the brand fetish people. The Men’s sandals from Born are an absolutely stylish one. These green leather flip-flops highlights, a chic look out of a modest outfit. The Trail NIB range of the Born house can be another worthy choice for men.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The brown Surf flip-flops are the best ones for a seaside walk. This Opanka crafted, Thong Flip-Flop is an outstanding Men’s footwear with the embellishment of the DRYZ® panel. This breathable sandal along with the shank of plastic ensures enhanced support along with superb traction anywhere and everywhere. The 6M leather Flip-Flops from Born is a simple but unique collection of this marque.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(63,1,62,1,'born cornflower sandal',1,'<p>Sandals are a necessity in this season Global warming. It may sound strange, but it’s a fact that comfortable sandals are something that every woman seeks; but style and trendy is equally significant. Born is that particular brand that has taken keen care to satisfy every single necessity, from trend to quality, from panache to sturdiness. The sandals are cage-style ones; the upper portion shaped with full-grain leather and lower adjustable straps makes this Opanka arts, a fabulous creation. The last thing that can add completeness to a head-to-toe look is a nice, stylish pair of Born Sandal.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The Cornflower Sandals from the Born House have a dash of feminine knack. The Cornflower Sandals are completely chic owing to the flower detailing on the uppers. This footwear looks good with any outfit; just the choice of right hue is needed. These human crafted shoes draw the ultimate diva appeal due to its strappy vamp along with the floral embellishment. These Cornflower shoes come in a huge variety o