are accessible in three basic bold colors; black, red and natural brown. The Foam midsoles are an important feature of these shoes. The man-made outsole along with the hand-stitching causes the shoes to be flexible as well as sturdy.  Model W12172 stands for the Born Cornflower shoe, of the sophisticated, off-white hue.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(64,1,63,1,'born clearance shoes for women',1,'<p>Born shoes have been the leading enterprise of leather footwear for men as well as women since the 1995. This firm is globally appreciated for its excellent quality, trailblazing design, dexterity. Women are generally fetish about stylish yet comfortable footwear, and born shoes are just the thing. This corporation crafts all its shoes in the famous European skill- “Opanka”; hand-sewing is the basic thing of this art. The upper portion is hand-sewed; sock lining along with double-needle stiches at the outsole is the basic science behind each born shoe. This brand has exclusively fashioned, a variety of range for women. These shoes pinch the pocket a bit and so clearance sales are the best time to fetch one.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The classical Sage boots from Born shoes is a “must have” of the wardrobe of every trendy girl. Available in black as well as brown, this Opanka hewed boot is made of soft and tender leather. The petite faux badges, details these zipped boots to give it a chic yet corporate look. The boots of Tembi Ankle model are the best put on for a forest camping or a late night party. Made of Tomro leathers, the Mary Beth clogs are among the casual wear stock of this outstanding brand. These shoes are designed intricately with crossed straps of hand-tooled leathers. The Nance High Heel Pumps for women are the best combination of tradition and modernization. The tassels on the full-grain leather uppers along with the padded foot bed make this high heel model, a complete comfy shoe. A.O.C Angelica sandals, Ari Mary Janes, Davina M