e leather wrapped heel give a healthy feeling of support mixed with style.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(67,1,66,1,'born shoes for kids',1,'<p>Shopping for the kid’s shoes is an important thing and needs to be carefully chosen. Kids have delicate skin, so every type of material may not suit them, leading to the appearance of rashes. It is important to go for reputed brand that trade good quality leather, while shopping for footwear for children. Born Shoes is a trusted firm over a number of years, owing to the premium quality of materials combined with style. So nothing can be better than a Born outlet while fetching kid’s footwear. Shoes for youths as well as Newborns are widely available at the Born factory.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>For newborns, this exclusive firm has brought forth a delicate collection. There is a good collection for the youngsters. The Toby Cuero Model of Born Kid’ shoes are an Opanka craft. The features of this shoe include its robust full-grain leather body along with the polyurethane sole. This shoe is preferred owing to its high-lasting comforts. Susy-Mary-jane is another staple choice for the kid’s shoes. “DRYZ Intellitemp” internal lining is an important characteristic that implies towards a padded sock. This shoe guarantees moisture-wicking facility. This collection includes the shoes of the same design on different colors like- black, brown.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The Chacha Sandals are another class of the Born kid’s shoes. The floral decal on these easy put-on sandals is fashioned from the full-grain leather. The outsole is made of rubber that conforms to the lightweight as well as the durability of the product. These sandals are available in Pink, White, Dark Brown hues. Bailie Boots from the born house are a perfect one for the kids, in the winter season. These boots sports an earthy look and has also got a back, filigree panel. This hand-stitched boots have a cork plus urethane outsole. The shoe of 