ltimate in style and fashion. These flats go best with a skinny jeans and a fitted cardigan. It has full grain leather, with fabric and leather lining and a light rubber outer sole. The shoe has the traditional Opanka hand construction and features a heel height of about half an inch.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The Adele Marrone, W81620, is another nice piece of art. This shoe is also made from full grain finish and a leather outsole. The outer sole is extremely light made from rubber and the shoe is provided with a steel shank. These shoes are available in a variety of colors like black, reddish brown, tomato red. The Adele Red, W51933, is also a sleek design and a good choice. These shoes are also appropriate as footwear for a stylish jeans finish. These shoes are made from folded leather designs and fabric linings. This model also uses the Opanka technology and a steel shank support. The extra cushioning is provided by the external lightweight rubber linings.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The Born Adele Lavender is an exquisite pair of shoes to put on. It has a suede finish or a full grain finish option to opt for. The shoe provides the combination of a fun and sophisticated look. The leather lining and the fabric covered foot bed helps to keep our feet free from moisture all day long. The steel shank facility is also embedded to provide support to the middle region of the foot and also some lateral constancy. The Adele Moro, W61933, is yet another exotic addition to the Adele collection. This shoe is made from sheer Opanka handwork and luxurious leather designs. The light weight leather finish at the upper wall and the rubber outer sole helps us gain more control over our feet. The leather frill lining provides a charismatic look to the shoe.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The Adele Cielo, W42191, expresses our romance through our feet. This lightweight shoe comes in variety of vibrant colors and can be your choice of footwear for almost any kind of attire in your wardrob