ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6680104619/\" title=\"reef sandy flip flops by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7021/6680104619_fa8bb511e3.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" alt=\"reef sandy flip flops\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Reef sandy flip flops are one of the most popular models from the company and have a large share in the entire sales of the brand.Sandy <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/\">flip flops from Reef</a> have a rubber sole for extreme durability and fall in the textile based make of sandals. </p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/xvJf0Dsr9eI\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br></p>\n\n<p>The heel measures around one inch and the rest of the platform measures around 3/4th of an inch. EVA sole from the brand is known for providing arch support and exceptional cushioning. The <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/reef-fanning-flip-flops\">classic look and design</a> are the first two things that customers notice in the model. These sandals can be worn anywhere, thanks to the firm and comfortable making and extremely basic <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/reef-vision-mens-sandals\">stylish design of Reef</a>. </p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/pF0SrIXrYUk\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br></p>\n\n<p>The straps are made of polyester woven in utmost style with ultra fine embroidered designs. A sanded texture features below the foot-bed for greater traction and density.  Whether one is walking on the sandy beaches or taking a walk along the street markets, Reef sandy flip flops are the most comfortable sandals to be in.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Most customers in the market are interested to know the places where they can get discounted prices for Reef products. Reef products are not cheap, but investing in a good pair of sandals that can last many summers is not that of a bad thought. Online shopping is the best way to get discounts on branded products. There are many authorized online dealers of the brand who often give discounts on clearance sales or weekends to accelerate sales. Reef also has an official website where one can check the models and their respective highlights. Comparing on online platforms is remarkably easy which makes shopping even easier. All Reef products come with the logo of the brand embedded at many places. This is the easiest way to check the authenticity while shopping online.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>For those who give comfort the prime importance while buying flip flops, Reef is the perfect brand for them. A company started by two highly creative Argentine brothers in the 80s has emerged as one of the largest producers of sandals on the globe. A strong base of loyal customers and excellent innovative creative products separate this brand from others in the same business.     </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(73,1,72,1,'Reef mulligan golf flip flop',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* reef new */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"9468098303\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6680103881/\" title=\"reef mulligan golf flip flops by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7160/6680103881_e74078018c.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"450\" alt=\"reef mulligan golf flip flops\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Reef mulligan golf flip flops are one of the most sophisticated and comfortable models from the house of Reef. Flip Flops are the most comfortable way to stay stylish, and therefore, it is best suggested that one should invest in a branded pair. Reef mulligan golf flip flops are grassy <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/reef-thongs-for-women\">models from the brand</a> providing the highest levels of comfort to wearer. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/U-9va21veTA\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The vibrant green color <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/reef-leather-smoothy-sandal\">comes in leather</a> upper that has a golf ball embossed near the heel. The golf ball is made of extremely soft rubber for soft cushioning to the heels. The foot bed is made of synthetic turf for superior comfort while walking. ‘Reef-flex triple density EVA construction’ is simply the <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/reef-vision-mens-sandals\">best from the brand</a>. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/T93_ueJW2mI\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The anatomic arch support in the make also gives the construction of the model a cutting edge. Tee and ball marker are included in these models. On the style factor, Reef mulligan golf flip flops score the best marks due to its high quality finish. The logo of the label is printed on the straps and the embossed golf ball for brand authentication. Avid golf lovers and stylish folks will like these ultimate golf shoes for sure.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Buying Reef mulligan golf flip flops is an easy task online. Reef is a gigantic company, and therefore, there are many authentic dealers of the brand who sell the models via the internet. One can check the official website for knowing the product details and features. Many dealers might give alluring discounts online and customers have the option of comparing the prices right at their home. With the brand reputation of Reef and the evergreen sleek look of the model, spending some extra dollars doesn’t matter. For the real comfortable feeling of walking on the golf grass, invest in mulligan flip flops of Reef without any second thought.</p>\n\n<p>Reef has emerged as one of the leading global brands in sandals and flip-flops in the past decade. The company was initiated in 1980s in California and primarily focused on the production of beach footwear. Presently, Reef serves in many countries with some of the best innovative models of sandals.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(74,1,73,1,'Reef flip flops with bottle opener',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* reef new */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"9468098303\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6680105233/\" title=\"Reef_Fanning_Bottle_Opener by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7168/6680105233_b9b01ab7ab.jpg\" width=\"440\" height=\"440\" alt=\"Reef_Fanning_Bottle_Opener\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Reef is a brand that is known for innovations and quality. With introduction of flip flops featuring a bottle opener, the brand name of Reef increased by several times. The brand that started producing sandals for beach goers, currently has more than a few experimental models in the market like <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/\">sandals with flasks</a>, bottle openers etc. </p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/w-oqsyPItEU\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The bottle opener in the flip flops or sandals means many things to many people. For some, it is a <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/reef-ginger-flip-flops\">distinctive fashion statement</a> while others might find the opener useful in many places.There are some distinct features in the models of Reef that ensure durability and comfort apart from the opener feature.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/bIwnpbcjVig\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>A contoured and arch supported food bed provides space for cushioning. There is airbag support (full 360 degrees) in the heel that makes walking in the sandals an enjoyable task. The outsole is made of rubber for maximum durability. The synthetic ‘Nubuck’ upper has been designed with an intention of giving comfortable feel to feet. The church key bottle opener in the design is elegant, stylish and sleek. Whether it’s the beach or any casual party, Reef flip flops with sandals look remarkably upscale and serve more than just sandals. From girly colors for women to pure basic colors for men, these flip flops come in seven different combinations.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Buying Reef flip flop sandals with bottle opener is a extremely easy task with online portals. The brand has its own official website where models have been mentioned with features and price. There are many other authenticated websites where customers can special discounts on special sales. Since these models come with the trademark logo of Reef, distinguishing the brand become very easy from imposters. Looking at the features and highlights, sandals with bottle openers can be called as one of the most exciting experiments from Reef. These models have now reached many international markets and most reviews from users are thoroughly positive. Except for snow covered terrains, Reef flip flops with shoe openers work perfectly for all seasons and all reasons. On the whole, these models are perfect summer beach buys in a modest price tag.     </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(75,1,74,1,'Reef thongs for women',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* reef new */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"9468098303\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6680103289/\" title=\"reef thongs by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7147/6680103289_fe61e94d12.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"331\" alt=\"reef thongs\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Reef has a huge collection of apparels, sandals and flip flops for women in many styles. When it comes to thongs, Reef has introduced more than a few models in the women’s category. All models have received excellent reviews in all tests and have been praised by all users.</p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/TAoXXkPr50Q\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The first model in Reef thongs for women is ‘Butter Thong’. <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/reef-flip-flops-with-bottle-opener\">Highly popular with girls</a>, this model scores full marks for being the most feminine thong. Made specifically for everyday wear, butter thong from Reef has a very remarkable flattering square body. The model has a truly stylish Nubuck strap of silky texture. The middle height wedge gives this thong a perfect style boost up. The model is available in basic colors like black and brown. </p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/MAwQmCNxokg\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The seaside thong from Reef is another popular model of the brand. Made with ‘Reef-Flex triple density EVA construction, Reef’s seaside thong makes beach fun even more happening. The features  include ‘EVA outsole’ which is extremely durable. EVA foot bed is contoured for a perfect feel in the water. The strap of the model is synthetic which is further highlighted with polyester made lining. Women with budgetary constraints can check the sandy throng that is priced around 25USD. It has strap that is double layered and wide woven. The EVA foot bed provides the feet with exceptional cushioning and comfort. The wedge shape of the model gives it a truly natural feeling.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Braideau Thong is one of the best buys in the women’s category. Fashionable and classy are the best words for this incredible braided thong. It has a sponge outsole made of rubber that gives extremely flexibility to the wearer. It features ‘Reef-flex triple density EVA construction’ with the very classic ‘anatomical arch support’. The area around the toe post is lined with very soft suede. The metallic logo of the brand along with the braided upper gives a ultra fashionable look to this thong from Reef. There are many other models which customers can check on the official website. The prices of these thongs may differ in many online portals and making a refined search about a model may fetch some very alluring discounts for customers. Reef thongs for women last for years and need a minimum of maintenance on daily basis. Combined with all the features, Reef thongs are worth the money.   </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>When customers look for Reef sandals, they probably already have the idea about the durability and quality of the brand. Unlike other brands that take several decades to make an impact in the market, Reef has managed to become of the best sandal producers in the world in less than three decades.     </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(76,1,75,1,'Reef ginger flip flops',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* reef new */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"9468098303\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6680103603/\" title=\"reef ginger flip flops by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7155/6680103603_398eb04bac.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"266\" alt=\"reef ginger flip flops\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>When it comes to simplicity with unparallel levels of comfort, Reef ginger <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/\">flip flops come as a perfect buy</a>. Reef is one of the largest producers of sandals and Flip Flops in the Unites States and also exports products to many other countries.</p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/ut4Go8Bw5qY\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br>\nGinger flip flops from Reef is products of excellence. Being <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/reef-leather-smoothy-sandal\">one of the most sought after range</a> from the label, this model has found immense likeability with the youngsters and middle aged alike. The first feature that is noticeable in the model is the strap. The strap is ultra soft, woven out of polyester. The famous ‘Reef-flex triple density EVA construction’ is a prime highlight which with anatomical arch support gives the <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/reef-sandy-flip-flops\">most comfortable feeling to the feet</a>. </p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/AX83yrTxaF8\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The product is extremely easy to wash, maintain and can be worn to almost any casual occasion. On the styling aspect, the model has received full marks from the users for being a lightweight flip flop in standard colors. While there are many colors introduced by the company, the product looks great in combination of aqua blue and brown. With little care, this flip flops can last for man than a few summers.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>While Reef itself maintains its line of dealers along with a full-fledged official portal, it is very easy to find other deals of the brand as well. Some special discounts are always available on certain sites but customers need to be sure if the ginger flip flops that they are buying are authentic. Reef ensures that the logo of the company is placed at the right places which not just creates branding but also is a mark of authentication. On the whole, Reef ginger flip flops are value for money products. Considering the long durability and the product features, buying the product at the cost quoted by the brand is not that of an expensive deal.</p>\n\n<p>In a span of three decades, this brand has become a pioneer in creating valuable designs in sandals. Innovation with quality seems to be the motivation of the brand and it continues to excel in making new products that break the market jinx.     </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(77,1,76,1,'Reef mick fanning sandals',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* reef new */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"9468098303\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6680104361/\" title=\"reef mick fanning sandals by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7165/6680104361_cf9ea36f29.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" alt=\"reef mick fanning sandals\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Reef holds the name in the market of flip flops for being one of the most innovative brands. The company started by two brothers in the 1980s is currently a global leader in sandals. Among the many <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/reef-thongs-for-women\">models launched by the label, Reef</a> mick fanning sandals is one model that has garnered positive reviews from most niches.Style and comfort at an unbeatable price, fanning sandals are always in demand. </p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/W5TD5kmNIjo\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Reef mick fanning sandals are one of the best buys from the brand. It is <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/reef-leather-smoothy-sandal\">available in both leather</a> and non-leather models in a modest price. The non leather make features synthetic ‘Nubuck’ upper with contoured ‘CMEVA foot bed’. The model has an airbag (in full 360 degrees) in the heel enclosed in polyurethane. It features the <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/reef-flip-flops-with-bottle-opener\">classic bottle opener from Reef</a> in the outsole near the bottom.</p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/NvPnqji8fyQ\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The herringbone outsole is known for high durability and traction. The complete model is extremely water friendly and can be dried very easily. Thanks to the airbag in the heel, one can wear these fanning sandals for long hours at a stretch. On the style factor, these sandals score quite respectable ratings. The colors are very basic, and overall the opener gives the sandals an innovative look. The non marking and non slippery sole is another prominent feature to watch out in these sandals. With the opener in the feet, making room for a surprise party on the beach is a thrilling experience.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Customers often want to know if they can get discounts on Reef mick fanning sandals. Firstly, Reef is known to provide sandals that are durable, comfortable and stylish. Hence, the prices quoted by the brand are quite reasonable. One pair of fanning sandals can last for more than three summers and require almost no maintenance. There are a few online shopping platforms where one can locate discounts on Reef products. The logo of the label is something that can verify the authenticity of the products. The label has its own official portal that features the models, also talks about the features and highlights in a more elaborative manner. There are separate shopping categories for guys and girls for easy sorting of products.      </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(78,1,77,1,'Reef leather smoothy sandal',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* reef new */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"9468098303\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6680105641/\" title=\"reef leather smoothy by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7004/6680105641_7021ec18d5.jpg\" width=\"344\" height=\"500\" alt=\"reef leather smoothy\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Reef leather smoothy sandal has been made with the highest level of research, just to make <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/reef-fanning-flip-flops\">every walk a pleasant experience</a>. The model provides the highest level of support to the feet with Reef-Flex density and superb EVA design supported with anatomical arch. The foot bed has been designed with reef polyester lining for superior detailing. </p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/kbQUbXrY5pM\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br></p>\n\n<p>The strap of the <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/reef-leather-smoothy-sandal\">sandal is made of pure leather</a>. The outsole is highly durable, non marking and abrasion resistant. Walking for a long time isn’t a problem with this supremely comfortable model of sandals on the feet as the grip is firm and tight. The design has been incorporated in a way so that sores and pains in the feet are prevented. Unlike other leather <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/reef-mulligan-golf-flip-flop \">models in the market</a>, this one is a very light model. </p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/ZhufV6fkei4\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Being simple yet truly classic, smoothy sandals create a look that is loved by youngsters and old aged alike. This is an authentic make of sandals from Reef that can last many seasons.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>On the whole, Reef leather smooth sandals are best buys from the brand for outdoor activities. The performance of the model lives up to the name of being real ‘smoothy’. The model can be checked for colors and features on the official portal of the brand. Online purchasing is the best way to save money on buying Reef products. Clear product details and easy comparison on multiple websites can make shopping for smoothy sandal a real easy task. The comfort of leather with a firm outsole is all that is required to hit the beach in style.</p>\n\n<p>Lovers of beach will never deny the importance of the right beach sandals. Taking part in the wide array of beach activities and walking along the coast line needs sandals that can stand the sands and water in a tough manner. These sandals come from Reef, one of the best sandal makers on the globe. Reef started as a very small company in the 80s, then run by two Argentine brothers. The company ventured into clothing and apparel lines with an equal amount of applause after finding enormous success with foot wears for beach goers.     </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(79,1,78,1,'Reef fanning flip flops',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* reef new */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"9468098303\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6680104179/\" title=\"reef-fanning-sandal by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7155/6680104179_19f4468e70.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" alt=\"reef-fanning-sandal\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>If brand name matters, then Reef is probably one of the best names in the market of flip flops.  Reef <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/reef-mick-fanning-sandals\">fanning flip flops</a> was introduced in both men and women categories, and the product has received smashing reviews from masses and classes alike.</p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/NvPnqji8fyQ\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br></p>\n\n<p>Nothing can be more relaxing than hitting the beach with a pair of comfortable sandals. Reef fanning <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/reef-mulligan-golf-flip-flop\">flip flops</a> just give the same comfort to customers with a <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/reef-flip-flops-with-bottle-opener\">distinctive bottle opener</a>. These models are made of rubber, plastic, leather along with a stylish metal opener attached. Fanning flip flops from reef are extremely durable, thanks to the enduring outsole made of rubber. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/W5TD5kmNIjo\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The upper is made up of synthetic ‘PU Nubuck’ with texture lining for a supreme comfortable feel. The mid sole part is molded with compression with ‘custom airbag’.  Styling with class is another striking feature of the brand which shoes in the fanning flip flops. The church key for opening soda and beer bottles features in the lower part of the sandals. With those little details to styling and the placement of the ‘Reef&#146; logo at the right places, these sandals from the brand are a clear hit. For the colors, one can visit the official website where shopping categories has been differentiated for guys and girls.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Easy to maintain and wash, Reef fanning flip flops last for years and can bear almost every season with ease. The price quoted by the company is above 50USD in most markets. Many might find the price high but considering the comfort and durability of the brand, these sandals are simply best investments. On an overall rating by customers of the brand, fanning flip flops from this reputable brand remain the best purchase for all terrains in a extremely modest price. There are many online dealers who give discounts on the products of Reef on special occasions. Customers can also check with individual shopping platforms for better price searches.</p>\n\n<p>Reef started as a brand in the 80s and originally focused on beach footwear. But with time, the brand has spread over a large range like clothing and apparels and has also moved to many international markets. Reef today remains the topic choice for many customers for sandals.     </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(80,1,79,1,'Reef vision mens sandals',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* reef new */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"9468098303\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6680104931/\" title=\"Reef Vision sandal by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7011/6680104931_7133336036.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"340\" alt=\"Reef Vision sandal\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Reef visions men’s sandals come with all the qualities of the brand infused in the right places. Comfortable in all conditions, <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/reef-mick-fanning-sandals\">these sandals have a soft textile lining</a> that gives a very fine finish and keeps the feet soft. These models have ‘nubuck upper’ along with a molded ‘EVA footbed’ in contoured compression for the best support in all areas. </p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/OZRtpWvjhiM\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br></p>\n\n<p>The foot-bed features a very lightweight cartridge with tunnel vision for the best level of comfort. The rubber outsole provides a very comfortable grip and has ‘debossed Reef tread’ on the entire area. The logo of Reef is embossed on many areas of the sandals for the real feeling of the brand. Except for snow, Reef vision men’s <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/reef-sandy-flip-flops\">sandals works perfectly for almost any terrain</a>. In three very basic colors, vision sandals are one of the best models from the brand. Being sport was never this easy.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/6gk5tiWk9Vs\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>While many might find the cost of Reef sandals quite high than similar brands, there are others who are ready to pay the quoted price for acquiring a piece of pure comfort. The brand has worldwide network of dealers for catering customers in global markets. There is also an official website of Reef where customers can shop the sandals and apparels online. Most models are priced in a bandwidth of 25 to 50USD. Special discounts can be availed in many online shopping platforms. No matter whatever is the season, Reef offers a range of sandals that can take the terrain and weather in the best manner.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Sandals are all about comfort and investing in a good brand like Reef is a very well thought decision. Reef is a brand that has been very synonymous with quality and comfort. Started by two brothers from Argentina in the 80s in California, Reef today stands as one of the most popular brands of flip-flops and sandals around the world. In the initial stages, the brand concentrated more on the needs of beachgoers and surfers. But presently, they have started producing sandals for all outdoor activities and have also opened up unique line of fashionable dresses and apparels.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(81,1,80,1,'Reef sandals with flask',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* reef new */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"9468098303\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6680103017/\" title=\"reef sandals with flask 2 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7171/6680103017_11c8b6e84c.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"299\" alt=\"reef sandals with flask 2\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Reef is a massive brand in sandals, and it infuses every design with quality, durability and the latest technologies. Reef took around 30 years to reach in a position where it can be called as one of the perfect <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/reef-flip-flops-with-bottle-opener\">sandal brands</a> in the world.  </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/ztA-I-YsBdM\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The branded started when two Argentine brothers came up with the idea of making <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/reef-mick-fanning-sandals\">flip flops for beachgoers and surfers</a>.After getting success in their initial attempts, Reef started making innovative products like sandals with flasks and stylish flip flops, without any compromises on the quality. <a href=\"http://www.reefsandals.biz/reef-mulligan-golf-flip-flop\">Reef sandals</a> are also known as Reef Dram sandals because there is an inbuilt flask in the sole. The idea became so popular that presently the model is in constant demand from many countries.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/jaRdGPe2ys8\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>There are some very common inherent qualities of Reef in the container shoes introduced by them. Comfortable, elegant and sophisticated, this model promises a lot of fun while wearing them. The upper of the model is made of synthetic ‘Nubuck’ upper and is water friendly. With anatomical arch support, the ‘contoured compression molded EVA foot bed’ works wonders in the comfort genre. There is a ‘polyurethane encapsulated canteen’ infused in the heel of the model with a firm screw cap. There is a very fine ‘shaker icon’ on the Reef rubber sole which is particularly appealing feature to watch out. Reef sandals with flask can hold 3 ounces of liquid and are priced around 50USD. The model has been immensely popular with college goers as they find it the easiest way to carry liquid with them a truly exciting fun task.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>One can shop for Reef sandals with flask online via the official portal. It is quite possible that some models might not feature on the website, and one might need to check other shopping platforms for the same. These sandals have been made with the best of technology and are embedded with the logos of Reef for quick identification. With the standard price, sandals with flask are perfect buys for every season. While many might not know about the carrier under the shoes, others might like appreciating the sleek choice. Overall, these are decent products from the house of Reef.           </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(82,1,81,1,'How to lace vans with 4 holes is an interesting read',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6171911031/\" title=\"lace vans with 4 holes 1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6176/6171911031_0140374b50.jpg\" width=\"333\" height=\"500\" alt=\"lace vans with 4 holes 1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You should understand that four holes are there in lace shoes. First take second lace and insert it through the right hand top and keep it aside. Take the first lace and insert it through the left hand hole on top and keep it aside.Check whether the two <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-lace-vans-straight-across\">laces </a> are of equal length.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/z0RpVsFZyEk\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Then take the second lace and insert it through inside the Vans shoe and take it outside through third hole in the right hand side of Vans shoe and keep it aside. Take the first lace and insert it through the shoe and take it through the second hole on the right hand side of <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net\">Vans shoes</a> and keep it aside. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Then you should drag the lace across and insert it through the second hole on the left hand side and you should insert in top and pull it downwards. Take the second lace and drag it across the third hole and insert it through third hole on left hand side of shoe through top and drag it down. Check whether the two laces are of equal size now.Do adjustments if the two laces are not equal in size.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"425\" height=\"349\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/Q27wNa9VdEU\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Insertion of lace in fourth hole is tricky and you should do it carefully. Insert the first lace through inside fourth hole on left hand side of Vans shoes and drag it outside.</b> Insert the second lace through right hand side of shoe through inside and drag it outside. Then drag the first lace to right hand side of fourth hole and insert it through top .Drag the second lace to left hand side of fourth hole and insert it through top. Drags both laces downwards and tie it together after inserting your leg. <b>This type of lace tying is bar lace method for 4 holes Vans shoes.</b>                      </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(83,1,82,1,'How to lace vans straight across',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6172440530/\" title=\"lace vans straight across 1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6171/6172440530_514bb5d636.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" alt=\"lace vans straight across 1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Vans shoes are the most common shoes which are worn by skateboarders as they have better grip on skateboard deck. Though there are varieties of ways to lace and wear <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net\">van sneakers</a>. but the shoes are most commonly laced straight with a hidden knot which prevents untied shoe from creating an issue on skateboard.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/PJOYix5OTlE\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Instructions to Lace Vans Straight Across</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Place the toe of the shoe pointed towards the body. Insert the <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-lace-vans-with-4-holes\">shoe lace</a> downward into the bottom pair of the eyelet or the one which the closer towards the toe of the shoe. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Make sure to pull the string so that there is an even length of the shoe string on each side.Then feed the right end of the shoestring into the second eyelet on the right hand side. After that pull the shoe lace across and down to the matching eyelet which is on the left hand side. Skip the third eyelet from the bottom and pull the shoe lace to the fourth eyelet in the same way.</p>\n\n<p></br>\n</br>\n<iframe width=\"420\" height=\"315\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/9uYgWHSmfhs\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><b>Now pull the lace across and down into the matching into the forth eyelet on the right hand side and then to the sixth eyelet and skip the forth eyelet. </b>Then start from the bottom and feed the shoelace on the left hand through the third eyelet hole on the left. Pull the shoestring across the matching eyelet on the right hand side and feed it down into the eyelet.Feed the string up through the fifth hole and then pull it across to the fifth eyelet on the left hand side. At last insert it down into the fifth eyelet and then feed it up into the sixth eyelet. <b>Also remember not to skip the holes.</b></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Vans shoes are most commonly worn by teens and adults and should not lace them in a normal way.  <b>Straight lacing also eliminates diagonal strings</b> and it makes the shoes look neater and also helps to take the pressure off of the top of foot.                         </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(84,1,83,1,'How to Clean Vans Shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6171810167/\" title=\"clean vans 2 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6169/6171810167_39750e854d.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"434\" alt=\"clean vans 2\"></a></p>\n\n<p><br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Use wet sponge to rub the <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net\">vans</a>. and remove any dirt and after that apply Mr Clean Magic Erasers or you can use wet tissues.</li>\n<li>The easiest option is to wash them in washing machine.Use the gentle washing option.Avoid dryer to protect rubber parts of our shoes.</li>\n<li>Avoid washing any clothes with <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/history-of-vans-shoes\">Vans</a> as sometimes color from clothes mixes with Vans.</li>\n<li>Try toothpaste or white shoe polish to remove yellowness from the white parts of the Vans.</li>\n<li>Avoid bleach during washing as they add yellowness.</li>\n\n</br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/SZB7iz2t_2g\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n</br>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a>\n\n\n\n</br>\n\n<li>Always air dry your shoes.</li>\n<li>Buy Mark Remover to remove an mud stains.</li>\n<li>Always <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-lace-vans-straight-across\">remove laces</a> before washing shoes.</li>\n\n</br>\n\n</br>\n<li>Spray some detergent over the marks.Sprinkle a little water over mark.Use brush or nails to scrub the marks.You have to repeat the process for stubborn marks.After that wash them well.</li>\n<li> <b>Use some towels while washing shoes in washing machine and place some hard plastic inside vans while drying it off </b></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br>\n</br></p>\n\n<p>Since the Vans shoes are worn with all types of fabrics being the best suited footwear, they are highly exposed to getting ragged over a period, similar to any other type of footwear.<b> Eventually, it is important to clean the Vans shoes and keep them appear as good.</b>It is quite important to learn the things not to do while cleaning the vans shoes rather than knowing how to clean the vans shoes.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The first and foremost aspect to be considered is these shoes should not be cleaned like typical footwear. It is trickier to clean the Vans shoes than a normal canvas shoe. Different types of Vans shoes are required to be cleaned in a different way.<b>For cleaning white Vans, use mild detergent powder to mix with the water and dip a brush in the water. Brush out the dirt from the canvas until it is cleaned. </b>Don’t dip the Vans into the detergent water. Once they dirt is removed, rinse the shoes with clean water and squeeze the water by covering the shoes with towel. Dry the shoes and <b>ensure that you don’t wear a wet or damp Vans Shoes, which not only spoils the durability but also affect the feet.</b></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Suede Vans can be cleaned by rubbing the shoes with the sponge dipped on some suede cleanser. </b>Suede cleansers are available in most of the footwear shops as well as online. Ensure to dry out the shoes naturally under sun.White Vans are more likely to turn into yellowish, when they are washed in a washing machine. So, it makes better sense to prefer hand wash these types of shoes, even though it might be a time consuming. Do not try to dry the Vans using a laundry dryer, because it might damage the fabric. Similarly, <b>ensure to avoid any harsh detergent or soap water, as the colour of the Vans gets faded away quickly.  </b>                   </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(85,1,84,1,'What to wear with white vans shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6163667916/\" title=\"white-vans-1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6176/6163667916_9e58485424.jpg\" width=\"294\" height=\"500\" alt=\"white-vans-1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Some Suggestions to match clothes with white vans</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>Wear High waist denim short with pink t-shirts.</li>\n<li>Wear Cardigan (black and white strips),<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-blue-vans-shoes\">aqua blue</a> shirt and denim shorts with white vans.</li>\n<li>Light colored bloused with black Pleat Shorts looks cool.</li>\n<li>Try Dark skinny jeans with blue t-shirts.Add a leather belt.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\">Gray</a> v-neck tee with black hotpants is a hot choice.</li>\n<li>Stripe cardigan(black and white) or white strap tank top with black mini skirt(leather crinkled is better) is a great choice.</li>\n\n</br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/SAIaxf-lgS0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n</br>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a>\n\n</br>\n\n\n</br>\n\n<li>White shirt,royal blue jeans and black leather jacket is another great choice.</li>\n<li>Try Floral halter dress or Floral pleat skirt with black top.</li>\n<li>Try Funky sweater with short and watch.Try to match the colors.</li>\n<li>Try Baggy t-shirt,denim short(buttons) and gray knee high socks.</li>\n<li>Blue loose crop tee or silk tank is good for casual look.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-black-vans-shoes\">Try Light blue</a> shirt or silk-chiffon dress or silk blouse with pockets or white tabo tank or a colorful shirt.You can also check striped T-shirt,gray </li>\n</br>\n\n<li>sweater,dark colored cardigan.</li>\n<li>White boatneck sweater,denim short and striped over the knee socks look great on white vans shoes.</li>\n<li>Dark colored corest top or pullover with light colored shorts looks cool on white vans</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Have you yet thought what shall go with the latest white pair of shoes you lately bought? One simple way to match up white pair of shoes  is to make certain that there is pale in your outfits.</b> So, if you are sporting a white and black striped top with a dark colour pencil skirt, you can match up a pleasant pair of black flats with your outlook without looking too “coordinated.” Another rule you may pursue is to sport a black belt with black pair of shoes. Match darker colours with the lighter colours to accentuate the black colours in your shoes and belt. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>If you are a female ,you can consider sporting a pair of black tights, brisk skirt and a nice coloured top with waxen party shoes.</b> The black in your apparels will make the white shoes stick out for a simple retro appearance.                         </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(86,1,85,1,'Vans knee high shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6172439984/\" title=\"vans knee high shoe 1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6176/6172439984_565f189b9b.jpg\" width=\"336\" height=\"500\" alt=\"vans knee high shoe 1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Vans is one of <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net\">popular footwear brands</a> loved by people across the globe. Vans shoes are more popular among sports people, where it is considered one of the important elements of sport accessories. Earlier, the company engaged in producing and <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-customize-vans-shoes\">selling Vans extended limited versions of shoes</a>. When it comes to fashion and style, no one wish to portray themselves with ruined products. The rapid growth, fame, demand and popularity of the Vans shoes due to its reliability, durability and cost efficiency motivated the producers to design and introduce more and more models.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/O3U6huG3I7s\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Usage of Vans shoes are not limited to any specific age group or gender, as it is designed for men, women and kids of all ages. Similar to Vans shoes, <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/vans-knee-high-socks\">knee high</a> shoes also have a global recognition with a long history. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br>\nThe manufacturers of Vans shoes decided to blend the preference for knee high shoes with their exclusive products, introduced Vans Knee high shoes. Vans Knee high shoes are considered the style statement. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>As the Vans shoes are greatly used by skateboarders, different types of Vans knee high shoes are designed specifically to use with skateboarding. A wide range of Vans knee high shoes are available in the market. Exclusive designs and models are available separately for men, women and even kids. Skateboarders prefer using Vans Knee high shoes. The knee high boots blends well with Vans bindings and act as an all-in-one or multipurpose mountain boot. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>In addition to being considered the sports boot, Vans women’s knee high shoes have reached a different arena, where they are used in ramps and fashion shows. Women prefer wearing Vans knee high shoes with mini frocks and high cut dresses. It is considered one of the sexiest footwear in the fashion world and women are constantly trying out the Vans knee high shoes with different outfits, creating a unique style statement every day. Further, Vans Women’s Knee high shoes are suit well with micro shorts or micro skirts.                       </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(87,1,86,1,'Vans clearance shoes for men',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6171910899/\" title=\"vans clearence 1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6179/6171910899_ec9fcfebe5.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"500\" alt=\"vans clearence 1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Vans offer a great collection of the clearance shoes. Though there are many <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/vans-skate-shoes-for-girls\"> brands available in the market</a> but vans clearance shoes are comfortable, unique and durable. These shoes are one on which one can rely on and will not break easily.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/do4bwxu-L2k\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Vans shoes are so comfortable that your feet will not ache and you will not feel any pain riding on the skateboard. As Vans is one of the oldest companies they have sufficient time to prepare <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-shorts\">comfortable shoes</a> and they pay special attention to sole which helps to relieve impact and create the shoes which keeps the feet away from hurting.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>These shoes are for the fashion and they are popular among the youth. The youth always keep in mind the type of shoes they want to go for. Vans offer shoes of different styles and kinds.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Vans clearance shoes for men comes in different styles  like classic slip-ons, era, skate shoes and sport shoes. </b> Vans shoes keep the choice type and interest of consumers in mind.Clearance shoes are comfortable, durable and high quality shoes at a price which is not heavy on their pocket.                       </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(88,1,87,1,'How to wear vans with skinny jeans',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6163665858/\" title=\"vans-skinny-jeans-1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6164/6163665858_73a35e0981.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" alt=\"vans-skinny-jeans-1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Both Girls and guys look stunning in vans and skinny jeans.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Below are some suggestions on wearing skinny jeans with vans</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>Tuck your skinny jeans in shoes if you are wearing hi-top vans.</li>\n\n<li>One good choice is <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-purple-vans-shoes\">purple vans</a> with black skinny jeans.</li>\n\n<li><b>Wear ankle socks with slip ons to avoid showing off your ankles.</b></li>\n\n<li>Avoid wearing vans and jeans of the same color.</li>\n\n<li>Baggy skinny jeans are better than tight ones if you dont have slender legs.</li>\n\n<li>Slip on is best choice with skinny jeans.Another good choice is checkered vans.</li>\n\n<li>Guys can try flannel shirts or t-shirts with skinny jeans.</li>\n\n<li>Sparkle dusted jeans with dark colored vans will make you stand out in the crowd.</li>\n\n<li><b>Red Cardigan with checkered vans and black skinny jeans looks stunning.</b></li>\n\n<li>Black shirt,red jeans and white vans for a casual look.</li>\n\n<li>Try <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\">dark grey vans</a> with light grey shirts and skinny jeans.</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/YYUm4o1aDmY\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-white-vans-shoes\">Wearing vans</a>  is considered a great style statement. In today’s era ,skinny jeans are fitting into fashion style easily.The style and glamour quotient of skinny jeans and vans have even attracted  the public who are not very fond of wearing skinny jeans . These jeans appear more striking when they are paired with just right color and style shoes.  <b>Vans and skinny jeans is great for skaters, artists, musicians and people who are fond of becoming a fashion setter. </b></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br>\n <b>Jam pearl</b> is one of the immense popular cornerstone groups of the ever prominent grime movement. Since their initial album, 10, was launched in the year 1991, they have demonstrated to have the melodic staying authority only asserted by rock and roll myths. <b>The Vans x Jam Pearl Dk4-Vi alliance is being at large with plenty of pride as these performers are also enthusiastic skate and surf buffs</b>, and a long time Vans clique.                    </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(89,1,88,1,'Vans shoe size chart',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6172170714/\" title=\"vans shoes size chart 1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6175/6172170714_4af96640ee.jpg\" width=\"478\" height=\"500\" alt=\"vans shoes size chart 1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/hello-kitty-van-shoes\">Vans shoe</a> sizes generall run large and they also stretch out a little.So always subtract half to your size while ordering vans,if you are shifting from Nike ,adidas,jordans,etc.For example if you wear Jordan or adidas of 8.5 size ,then order vans of size 8 online.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net\">Vans</a> follow the same sizing convention across all its brands like slip ons,era,etc.</li>\n<li>There is a difference of 1.5 between women sizes and men sizes.A women in need of size 10 can order Men size 8.5.</li>\n<li>Vans size is written just below the Tongue.</li>\n\n</br>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/YzDRrzieJHQ\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n\n</br>\n\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a>\n\n</br>\n\n\n\n<li>Vans are available in half sizes.</li>\n<li>Its always better to go to a store and try shoes before buying.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/vans-shoes-for-kids\">Vans</a> is good for people with wide feet.</li>\n\n\n</br>\n\n<li>If your shoes is loose,try to wear it with thick socks.</li>\n<li><b>If your shoe is little bit tight, stretch it with ice or shoe strecher or liquid spray.</b></li>\n<li>If the ordered Vans shoe does not fit you properly,you can always return it.<b>Vans refunds money in 2 weeks.</b>Unfortunately they do not have any exchange policy.</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Measure the size</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>To determine the size of the shoe use a ruler or tape to measure the foot. </b>To ensure that you are taking accurate readings when measuring always flatten your foot by shifting your foot forward.<b> If the measurement is in between the two sizes then always move to the larger size.</b> Always do not forget to <b>measure both the feet</b> i.e., left and right foot as the sizes may be different try to fit to the larger of the two.Find the closest measurement in inches that is equal to and greater than the length of the foot. <b>Remember to put on a pair of socks before taking the measurement</b> of the shoe as a pair of socks adds a little extra room for the measurement.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The shoe sizes are not measured with the same unit around the world. Also it is very important to convert the shoe size used in one country or region to the shoe size used in another country. It is very easy to get the shoe size at home.<b>Vans are available in different sizes like small, medium, large and extra large</b>, it just depends on the kind of the shoe you are looking for.                       </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(90,1,89,1,'How to wear Vans with shorts',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6163665008/\" title=\"vans-shorts-1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6176/6163665008_fb9cc58b71.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"411\" alt=\"vans-shorts-1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>In hot weather,shorts look stylish and are very comfortable.Below are some suggestions to <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-black-vans-shoes\">wear your vans</a> with shorts :</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>White v neck t-shirt with khaki shorts</li>\n<li>You can roll your jeans if you dont like to wear shorts.</li>\n<li>You can wear your vans either without socks or with <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/vans-knee-high-socks\">no show socks</a>.Both looks cool.</li>\n<li>Quarter socks looks best with vans slip ons.</li>\n<li>Girls can try black vans with black ankle socks.</li>\n\n</br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/7C-W51u1fwQ\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n</br>\n\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a>\n\n</br>\n\n\n</br>\n\n<li>Wear checkerboard Vans with black shorts and ankle socks.</li>\n<li>Girls look cute in black soffee shorts and pink vans.</li>\n<li>Another good combination is <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\">grey colored vans</a> and shorts with purple shirt.</li>\n\n</br>\n\n<li>Another combination to try is gold vans,khaki shorts and orange polo t shirt.</li>\n<li>Try black sweater with holster shorts and blue vans.</li>\n<li>Baseball and knee high shorts look best with vans.</li>\n<li><b>Vans slip on and low tops go best with shorts.</b></li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<b>Vans shoes have been transformed into a fashion icon from being an exclusive sports and skateboarding footwear. </b>The popularity and usage of Vans shoes by people of all age group moved the manufacturers to produce the Vans shoes in different styles and models to cater and suit the needs of all types of customers. Vans shoes are highly comfortable and appear casual. Beauty of the Vans is enhanced by the lace and the lacing style. Eventually, there is a hesitation in wearing the Vans with Skinny Jeans. Vans shoes are ideal choice of footwear with shorts. But there are lot of questions revolving round the mind how to wear Vans shoes with shorts? What is the appropriate design or model of the shoes that perfectly match with shorts?, etc.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Vans with shorts and a T-shirt offer an elegant look, being a casual wear. <b>The colour of the Vans influences the appearance and should match with the model or colour of the shorts. </b>Similarly, black Vans suits well with all colours any kind of shorts like denim shorts. Vans shoes can be worn with shorts in any shades of blue. They are perfect with blue, grey, brown, white and black coloured shorts, where the shorts should match the T-shirt. However, black Vans is the perfect match for Jean shorts. Blue Vans suits with light shaded shorts and jean shorts.  As stated earlier, Vans shoes are preferred by people of all ages and genders. Wearing Vans are considered the fashion statement and hence, it is certainly loved by women. <b>Generally, girls tend to prefer soft coloured vans like pink. Further, most of them prefer to wear mini or micro shorts </b>.Vans shoes look good on cuffed shorts and skinny jean shorts. <b>Wearing Vans shoes with short shorts or athletic or sport shorts enhances the look and makes the wearer to look cool.</b>                    </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(91,1,90,1,'vans slip ons for women',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6166734092/\" title=\"vans slip on 1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6177/6166734092_aa403a50fb.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"377\" alt=\"vans slip on 1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Vans slip on is great for travel in plane or train.Its very easy to wear and take them off.</li>\n<li>Its one of the most popular <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/vans-skate-shoes-for-girls\">shoe for skateboarding</a>.</li>\n<li>Please avoid it if you have big feet.</li>\n<li>You deodorizer if you sweat a lot and prefer to wear slip ons without socks.</li>\n<li>Ronnie radke weared skull slip ons in his music video.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-lace-vans-straight-across\">Checkerboard Slip on</a> was launched in 1979.</li>\n<li>Slip ons gained pouplarity in 1982 when actor sean penn used it in movie <b>Fast Times at Ridgemont High.</b></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/zCN8zpGSAnU\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Dressing options with vans slip on</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n\n<li>Black cashmere sweater,white t shirt and blue skinn jeans looks great with slip ons.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-black-vans-shoes\">Black</a> and white striped jersey tank,black sleeve sweater and denim shorts looks cool.</li>\n\n</br>\n<li>White polo top with grey wrapped short.</li>\n<li>White half sleeve,yellow jacket and black skirt.</li>\n<li>White tanktop,leather waistcoat with straps with ripped mini skirt looks amazing with slip ons.</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Vans slip- on for Women does match the contemporary style and would give authentic style to wearers. Wearers would have the difficulty in finding the right words that would describe shoes quality and the comfort it offers to wearers. <b>High quality innovation is what you get the moment you land on this product.</b></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The shoes come in various formats like the <b>sneaker format, the skate format, core classic format, and casual format</b> and so on. You can go for the classic look by purchasing the traditional white and black combination and checkered style would take your looks to another level. You can go for colorful all blacks Vans slip- on as that would give a classic outlook. Some of the other colors that shoe comes in are <b>pure white, navy blue, pink, charcoal and neon pink.</b></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>The shoe durability is impressive and would last with you for a long period. </b>The shoe would take comfort zone of wearers to another level and would pass any shock absorption tests. The shoes have better breathing capacity, increasing the comfort level of wearers. The sole attachments of these shoes are of high quality and they pass all rough tests that you can give to it.The comfort level of getting in and out of this shoe is high but chances are also high that you would hate getting out of these shoes. <b>You should buy sizes that fit your legs better and have a pleasure in walking in this real treat.</b>                     </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(92,1,91,1,'What to wear with red vans shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6165712835/\" title=\"red vans 1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6160/6165712835_43fab371d2.jpg\" width=\"333\" height=\"500\" alt=\"red vans 1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<h3>Some of the dressing tips and suggestions for Red Vans shoes </h3></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Long layering yellow tanks,<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-blue-vans-shoes\">navy blue</a> denim shorts and red suspenders match well with red vans</li>\n<li>Red-white t-shirt with dark stretch jeans is a good choice</li>\n<li>Mickey mouse tank ,dark dolphin shorts and white jacket looks cool.You can also add a yellow watch</li>\n<li>White short sleeve tee ,black skinny jeans and <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/vans-knee-high-socks\">black socks</a> with polka dots goes well with red shoes.</li>\n\n</br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/liWPflq_0Zs\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br>\n\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a>\n\n</br>\n</br>\n\n<li>M personal favorite is Black-white striped t shirt ,red white tank and open cargian of dark color</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-pink-vans-shoes\">Pink</a> hoodie with dark bottoms looks good</li>\n</br>\n</br>\n\n<li>White sweatshirt,plaid t shirt (red black strips) over roll up shorts.</li>\n<li>Floral top or grey cardigan with dark skinny jeans looks well</li>\n<li>Red zip back vest with black skirt is another good choice</li>\n<li>Try Dark wash skinny jeans with multi stripe tie hem top or a check tie front shirt</li>\n<li>Try white Roll Sleeve Flecked Tee with Cobalt cigarette tapered trousers and silver belt</li>\n<li>Try mid rise leather skinny jeans with red colored flannel shirt</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>What to wear with red van shoes is not a perplexing question for fashion lovers. <b>The real answer is that you can wear anything that would help you stand out in a crowd.</b> You should think of the occasion for which you are wearing shoes and creative ideas will flow.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>If you are planning to go for a wedding occasion wearing red shoes, it is better you highlight yourselves wearing check stripped top and plain bottom colored dress. </b>You should highlight the color of these shoes as red is vibrant and energy filling for onlookers. Silver color dress contrasts red colored shoes and blue color dress also goes well with these shoes. You should look at using multiple shades of pink, white and orange. Women can go for skirts that have the white or cream color . Black colored tops would help you to give contrasting color .<b>If you plan to wear a hat, it is better that you come with white colored hat and you can have pink colored shade on it.</b></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Men can wear t-shirt that has patterns as it  matches well with red colored shoes.</b> A printed pant that uses blue color goes a long way in highlighting red color. What to wear with red van shoes is not a problem, if you plan to go forward with Jeans. Any color Jeans would look cool with red color.What to wear with red van  shoes is your choice ultimately and you should use your beauty sense to find the right answer. <b>There are colors that bring red to prominence, and you should try to use them if you want to highlight red.</b>                       </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(93,1,92,1,'What to wear with grey vans shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6163133007/\" title=\"grey vans 1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6154/6163133007_17a362ae8b.jpg\" width=\"333\" height=\"500\" alt=\"grey vans 1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<h3>Some Suggestions to match clothes with Grey vans</h3></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>Wear plaid or checkered shirt(red and white) with white skinny jeans.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-black-vans-shoes\">Black</a> tee or tank,Strip Shirts,Red round or v-neck t-shirt looks always good with white vans.</b></li>\n<li>Wear Cropped Top with strips and black shorts.</li>\n<li>My personal favorite is <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-blue-vans-shoes\">Blue</a> cardigan and white skinny jeans.</li>\n<li>Floral Crochets Top(pink) with black skinny jeans is another great choice.</li>\n\n</br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/CNfV_ri87us\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n</br>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a>\n\n</br>\n\n</br>\n\n<li>White pullover with red leggings is a good choice for parties.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-red-vans-shoes\">Red</a> tank with navy blue shorts looks absolutely cool.</li>\n</br>\n</br>\n\n<li>Try Printed tank with bermuda shorts (black or white).Add Pink handbag and black hat.</li>\n<li>Wear Faded crop jeans(dark color) with any dark colored top.</li>\n<li>Try Grey cotton tank,red colored draped cardigan and low rise skinny jeans of light color.</li>\n<li>Wear it with Floral skirt with black band and chalk colored trim tank with laces.</li>\n<li>Wear it with Purple long sleeve tee and dark colored jeans.You can wear a white sweater over tee.</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Grey Vans not only looks cool and trendy but also stylish.They also look hot and they are one of must have items in the wardrobe. <b>There are stylish ranges of grey vans shoes like Vans Era , Classic vans slip on .Grey is a unisex color and can be worn by both men and women.</b></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Grey Vans shoes are available in different styles and patterns. They are the part of the skate culture</b> and their style is beyond compare. Not only grey vans slip on shoes but also grey era, grey skate shoes or any other kind of grey vans shoes looks great on anyone.One can wear the grey shoes with everything .They go well with skinny jeans, regular jeans and shorts  and even with sun dresses and skirts.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Always try to wear something comfortable and casual .Wear dark denim jeans or skinny jeans with a graphic t-shirt, white v neck short sleeve t-shirt or even cardigan . </b>Grey vans looks great with black jeans as grey looks cool with black. Also one can wear the cool accessories to create more stylish, cool and trendy look.Grey Vans makes a great combination with white and black . They also give the classic, traditional authentic and a cool look. Thus Grey Vans is such a collection that everyone would like to have and add it to his or her collection as it can go well with any color and also give you right style.                        </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(94,1,93,1,'what to wear with purple vans shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6163134739/\" title=\"purple-vans-1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6174/6163134739_5f348bc8aa.jpg\" width=\"470\" height=\"470\" alt=\"purple-vans-1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br>\nPurple vans shoes looks cute and bold.It helps you to get noticed.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Please try these clothing suggestions with your purple vans</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>Try to create a layered look at top by wearing your shirt or t-shirt under jacket or cardigan.</li>\n<li>Ripped skinny jeans with purple-yellow-white t-shirt is great for party look.</li>\n<li>White sleeveless top with pink laces and dark colored skinny jeans gives you a perfect casual look.</li>\n<li>You can wear Floral top,Cotton shirt with white and purple checks,Flannel shirt with colored strips,White and <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-purple-vans-shoes\">purple top</a> with deep scoop neck,Aqua cashmere cardigan,Long sleeve cardigan with multicolored strips,Gray or black blazer with any skirt or jeans.</li>\n\n</br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/1ZrUaqQkv3U\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n</br>\n\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a>\n\n</br>\n</br>\n\n<li><a  href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/orange-vans-shoes-for-kids \">Orange</a> scarf,purple top and skirt (preferrably orange black checks) goes well with purple vans.</li>\n<li>Purple scraf on v-neck t-shirt plus low rise navy blue skinny jeans looks good with purple vans shoes.</li>\n<li>Black skinny jeans with purple t-shirt or blouse is another good choice.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-white-vans-shoes\">White</a> skinny jeans with black t-shirt with some designs looks cool.</li>\n</br>\n\n\n<li>Girls love to wear Purple cardigan with matching scarf and white skinny jeans over their purple vans.</li>\n<li>Wear Gray hoodie,t-shirt and dark jeans .</li>\n<li>Buy matching handbags,belt(metal color or purple),woolen cap,necklace and hair clips.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>You should know whether you are wearing dark-colored purple or light-colored purple as they match with different kind of dresses. </b>This is one color that gives classy look to wearers.But you should get careful with the outfits that you wear with these shoes as an outfits that do not highlight the purple color would not look good.Mens should wear gray colored or khaki colored pants that would highlight the purple color of shoes.<b>You should wear only light-colored Jeans with purple shoes. You can go for dark-colored tops that would highlight the purple .</b>You can also try white colored t-shirt that has shades of purple in it. Dark-colored purple t-shirt looks great if you are wearing light-colored purple shoes.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Women should go for light-colored skirts like cream or light yellow. White skirts that have purple shades </b>in it would also look good with these shoes.  A plain white colored top is an excellent choice with these shoes.You should wear accessories like watch,bracelet  and jewels that do not directly matches with the purple color of your shoes. <b>Always make sure that purple is not on higher side in your accessories.</b>You can try multi colored bangles and white colored earrings.What to wear with purple Vans shoes is a topic that deserves your fully fledged attention and you should understand the classy nature of this color.Always try to come out with outfits that matches well with purple .                         </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(95,1,94,1,'Yellow vans shoes for women',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6165713297/\" title=\"yellow vans -1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6155/6165713297_28fc568bb4.jpg\" width=\"333\" height=\"500\" alt=\"yellow vans -1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Some of the dressing tip for  yellow Vans shoes </h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Wear White cotton tank with floral denim hot pants.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-white-vans-shoes\">Wear White</a> cashmere tank with floral skirt</li>\n<li>Wear Gray tee with denim shorts</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/yellow-vans-shoes-for-women\">Try Yellow colored</a> loose top with polka dotted skirt.</li>\n<li>Try White t shirt,ice jacket and black skirt with yellow vans shoe.A matching yellow handbag will compliment the look.</li>\n\n</br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/gIAr4C2sGNM\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n</br>\n\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a>\n\n</br>\n\n\n</br>\n\n<li>Try White frayed bloused with yellow twill shorts.</li>\n<li>Wear Charcoal colored tank with white skirt.Add a buttermilk cape cardigan for layered look.</li>\n<li>Yellow leather tank with navy blue skinny jeans.Add a leather jacket.</li>\n<li>White and yellow stripe t shirt with denim short looks amazing with yellow vans.A sunglass adds to the look.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-pink-vans-shoes\">Pink</a> sleeveless blouse with grey skirt matches well with yellow vans.A navy blue jacket adds to the look.</li>\n</br>\n</br>\n\n<li>White trench coat,grey top and red skirt goes well with yellow vans.</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Yellow van shoes for women are another ideal product from this respectable brand.</b> It meets the classy style of women and would meet their fashion demands also. It comes in grey yellow and other shades of yellow. <b>Yellow is a color that bolsters the creative mind and would send artistic signals to viewers.</b> Yellow color shoes alter your appearance and would present you as a confident savvy girl. Yellow white and  yellow black are two of most popular color options.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Yellow van shoes makes an ideal wear for women when they wear skirts and trousers that contrasts the shoe. </b> Always go for matching dress and bag to highlight the shoes. You should not make any efforts to keep the shoes in background . <b>This color is ideal for tourism and travel to parks. These shoes would also support the executive office dress and would help act confidently.</b>Always wear clean shoes as any dirt or patch would bring yellow color to forefront. You should remove stains and dirt from the shoes.Yellow vans shoes for women are a lovely treat from a brand that knows how to make shoes. <b>You can wear this for parties and for serious occasion like in office also.</b> You would find these shoes affordable and will soon find that they add style to your wear. You should not miss these  lovely yellow pair of Vans shoes.                        </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(96,1,95,1,'Vans boat shoes for men',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6165530096/\" title=\"vans-boat-1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6179/6165530096_2a795243fd.jpg\" width=\"333\" height=\"500\" alt=\"vans-boat-1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br>\nDel Barco boat shoes from vans are available between 55 to 65 USD on <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/\">Vans website</a>.Girls adore the guys who wear boat shoes as it is cool,stylish and always in style.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/XSnR-J4_yPQ\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>Guy can go for chukka del barco if they like <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/vans-clearance-shoes-for-men\">hi-tops style.</a> It looks good with cargo jeans or skinny jeans</li> .\n\n</br>\n\n<li>If you want to wear shorts with your boat shoes,i will suggest you to take a look at C&P Zapato Del Barco as it is low-top and looks cool with shorts.</li>\n<li>Another good choice  is Patchwork Plaid Zapato Del Barco if you want to look different.Its one of the coolest designs ever from Vans.</li>\n<li>Girls should avoid boat shoes as it makes their feet look large.</li>\n<li>You should take a look at Sperry top spider for boat shoes.Vans boats are limited in design and sizes while Sperry gives you plent of options.</li>\n<li>Buy a boat shoe of brown color as brown matches with almost anything.</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Boat shoes are the best to have in summer or spring season.</b> They provide both style and comfort with an outdoor adventurous look. Vans boat shoes are manufactured to provide extreme sports and active lifestyle products.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Boat shoes are worn to give the sporty look rather than casual look.</b> They come in different colors and textures and are available with or without laces. Boat shoes require minimal maintenance. They are classic and the most prominent style on the street.Boat shoes are the fashionable foot wear that falls <b>in between formal dress shoes and casual wear shoes.</b> They provide relaxed look and a unique style. <b>These shoes can be worn with or without socks</b> but people prefer to wear them without socks.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Boat shoes can be worn with both sporty and casual clothes.</b> Vans boat shoes provide extreme comfort and style and are perfect for the casual look. They also provide assured quality as they are meant mainly for slippery boating.These low profile shoes can withstand the rough conditions and <b>require a low amount of maintenance</b>. Quality oil on the leather of the shoes should be applied regularly to protect its shine. Also the inner sole should be removed and sprayed with the cleaners.Though these shoes are not cheap but their quality exceeds the expectations. <b>They are available in various colors like black, blue and white.</b> The boat shoes not only give style but also classy look. Thus these shoes add style to the wardrobe.Vans Boat shoes are aimed at the younger generation and thus it is very popular among youth and looks great.                       </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(97,1,96,1,'What to wear with black vans shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6163132759/\" title=\"vans-black-1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6170/6163132759_303b214a58.jpg\" width=\"321\" height=\"500\" alt=\"vans-black-1\"></a>\n</br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Black vans looks nice with almost any of your outfit.Its cool and stylish.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Below are some suggestions to wear black vans with different dresses.</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>Girls can try <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-pink-vans-shoes\">Cute pink</a> top and rolled up jeans with their Black Vans slip ons.</li>\n\n<li>You can use silver sharpie to decorate black vans.</li>\n\n<li>Wear dark denim or grey jeans with black vans.Avoid black and <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-blue-vans-shoes\">navy blue colors</a>.</li>\n\n</br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/63dVDE8_CDA\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br>\n\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a>\n\n</br>\n</br>\n\n<li>Try boot cut jeans with blouse for dashing look.</li>\n\n<li>Leather jacket over white cardigan and pink skirt is another good choice.</li>\n\n<li>Wear khakhi with ankle socks.</li>\n\n<li>Try <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/vans-knee-high-socks\"> knee high socks</a> with skirt or shorts for party look.You need beautiful legs to carry it off.</li>\n\n</br>\n\n<li>Tight top(avoid black and navy blue) with skinny jeans gives you a casual look.Tops with light color will look better.</li>\n\n<li>You can go for V-neck or cardigan instead of tops.Make sure that its not too tight.</li>\n\n<li>Wear matching bangles,purse and earrings.</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Among the range of colours and models, black vans shoes are quite unique and preferred by more. <b>Black vans shoes  tend to be more stylish as well as  professional looking footwear.</b> It perfectly matches with all dresses irrespective of the age and gender. Girls look fabulous in black vans shoes.Since black is an eternal color ,it suits well with all kinds of outfits and accessories, the question of what to wear with black vans shoes becomes immaterial. However, wearing perfect clothing enriches the personality . </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>For men, black vans shoes are the right choice of footwear to wear with shorts and jeans.</b> It looks great with blue jeans and a T-shirt. Further, it also goes well with sports costume. When black vans shoes are worn with shorts and T-shirts, wearing black or white knee high socks enhance the personality.When it comes to women, a wide option of outfits is available to wear with black vans shoes. Similar to men, blacks vans shoes suits with knee high socks in women. <b>Black vans can be worn with yoga pants or shorts, harem pants, skinny jeans, skinny pants, jean shorts, skinny cargo, miniskirts, etc.</b> For a stylish look, black vans shoes perfectly match with blue jean shorts or white shorts with striped or plain t-shirts. White shorts and Polo T-shirts with black and white stripes offer an amazing look with black vans.                         </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(98,1,97,1,'Vans knee high socks',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6168960109/\" title=\"vans knee high socks 1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6167/6168960109_0c3b3a59d2.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" alt=\"vans knee high socks 1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Dresses that matches well with Vans Knee high Socks</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Grey V neck cardigan and sparkle dress goes well with knee high socks</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-black-vans-shoes\">Wear Black</a> printed t shirt,black line skirt and grey or white sweater</li>\n<li>White stripe shirt with dark denim skirt looks cool</li>\n<li>Printed cotton tank and hot pants is a great choice with knee high socks</li>\n<li>Wear Lace prom skirt with checks and red sweatshirt</li>\n<li>Wear Khaki Mini skirt with pockets and grey t shirts</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/yellow-vans-shoes-for-women\">Try Yellow</a> collared top with black miniskirt</li>\n<li>Pink colored tuck blouse with leather shorts looks cool with vans knee high socks</li>\n<li>Dark blue bubble hem dress is a great choice.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/rCPMLwz7T3E\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<H3>Knee high socks available on vans website</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>Women\'s Classic Knee High Socks   </li>\n<li> Women\'s Nylon <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/vans-knee-high-shoes\">Knee High</a> Socks  </li>\n\n</br>\n\n<li> Women\'s Triathalon Knee High Socks  </li>\n<li>Women\'s Light on your Feet Knee High Socks   </li>\n<li> Mistletoe Knee High Socks  </li>\n<li> Women\'s One, Two Step Knee High Socks  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br>\n</br></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<b>Knee high socks initially rose in popularity in 1970\'s.</b>The style back then was to dress in any solid black or white color of knee high socks.With time the color and styles have improved and this has a important part of women wardrobe and dresses.<b>For job, you can select to sport an artistically ornate pair of knee high strikes with a diffident kitten and skirt heels. </b>On a  night out with pals, you can wear black dress, a pair of tall heels, and a corresponding pair of lacy knee high socks.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Vans offers these socks in wool,mixtures of polyamides, spandex, cotton (silk is an innate polyamide and nylon is an artificial one), metallics and Eastman (man-made yarn with stretchy properties that preserves its form after stretching).These socks are available in plenty of designs and patterns.<b>Vans knee high socks have also been a significant part of aerobics instruction uniforms.</b></p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(99,1,98,1,'History of Vans Shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6166197041/\" title=\"vans history 1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6164/6166197041_8219714702.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" alt=\"vans history 1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<h3>Important landmarks in history of Vans shoes</h3></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net\">Paul van doren</a> started the vans shoe company in 1966 along with his brother steve and serge D\'Eila.</li>\n<li>It grew in popularity becuase of 1982 sleeper hit <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/history-of-vans-shoes\">fast times at ridgemont high</a>.</li>\n<li>Its first target market was sailors but accidently its popularity grew among surfers and skateboarders.</li>\n<li>Steve caballero was first signature shoe of Vans released in 1989.</li>\n\n</br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/dfvF70iBG5w\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n</br>\n\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a>\n\n</br>\n<li>Vans slip on was introduced in 1979.</li>\n<li>Vans era (blue and red) was launched specifically for skateboarders.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-customize-vans-shoes\">Vans custom shoe</a> was launched in 2004.They allow people to design their own unique shoes.</li>\n<li>In 1998 vans skate park was built in California.</li>\n\n</br>\n\n\n</br>\n\n\n<li>In 1998 it was acquired by McCown De.Currently its a part of VF corporation.</li>\n<li>Geoff Rowley is best selling signature shoe from Vans.</li>\n<li>The current vans product line stands at 173 compared to original 3 it started with.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Vans Shoes are the highly renowned brand and are considered the preferred footwear among the sports people and skate boarders. History of the Vans shoes can be traced back before 50 years.The United States is the mother land of the Vans shoes and Paul Van Doren is the father of the Vans Shoes Company.<b> Earlier, Vans shoes were not available for direct sale from the manufacturer. </b>The founder was interested in selling the shoes directly to the people to avoid the middleman for marketing the products, with the intention of offering quality footwear at affordable prices with a good profit. The founder launched the official business of Vans shoes being offered directly to the customers from the manufacturers in the year 1966. He started the business with three partners, his brother Jim Van Doren, and two friends Serge D Elia and Gordy Lee.<b> The first Vans Shoe store was opened in Anaheim, California.</b></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The Van Doren Rubber Company came into existence on March 15, 1966, where the exclusive vans shoes are directly sold to the customers. On the official day of launching the business, it was announced to offer three different models of Vans Shoes for sale. Unfortunately, they were able to display only one model of the Vans shoes and managed to display the rest of the models by displaying the empty boxes.<b>Twelve customers purchased the Vans deck shoes from the shop on the very first day of opening.</b> The company has gained greater popularity and outstanding growth, as the father of the company was quite efficient and smart to understand the clients and learn their requirements and dislikes in the product.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>The company has huge growth in 1970s, where they were asked to manufacture shoes with woollen linings and rubber canvas for the Federal Government.</b> The company produced the woollen and rubber canvas shoes for the department of Defence as well for the Air Force.Subsequent to the day of launching the business, the manufacturers were able to stock different types of Vans shoes in range of styles. Now Vans shoes are available in a plethora of designs and styles, which is quite impossible to list out and the prominent and <b>popular models include as classic shoes, Vans band shoes, Limited edition shoes, Vegan friendly shoes, Stake shoes, etc. </b>                </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(100,1,99,1,'Vans shoes for kids',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6172439682/\" title=\"vans shoe for kids 1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6164/6172439682_8d602c8265.jpg\" width=\"333\" height=\"500\" alt=\"vans shoe for kids 1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Vans Shoes is an American based Footwear Company. The <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/history-of-vans-shoes\">first store of Vans</a> was opened somewhere in 1960’s and since then the company has been a worldwide popular and became a dominant player in footwear and action sports market. The company manufactures sport shoes,skate board shoes, snowboard shoes and various other shoe types.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/U8opyfdTeq8\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The company mainly focuses on youth market and they also sell accessories and apparels catering to needs of the youth market. Vans shoes offers the most <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-customize-vans-shoes\">diverse range of shoes</a> for kids and there are more than hundreds of stores available both online and offline from where one can buy the shoes.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Features of vans kids shoes</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Van shoes are of high quality shoes and are very popular  because of their style and comfort.</b> Another factor which makes them even more popular is the durability. Though these shoes are available at a price which is quite high and while buying it may be a burden on the pocket, but one can easily rely on the quality.\n<b>Also these shoes are available in various designs and colors which make them even more popular among the kids.</b> Parents or kids can also customize these shoes and order them as per their own choice for their kids. Vans also <b>offers the newest design and editions</b> which is another factor which kids like about the shoes.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Vans shoes are available in wide variety of sizes ranging from toddlers to kids</b>  and cater to the needs of both male and female. There are various designs, colors and patterns which are available in the market which tends to attract the kids. <b>Designs like cartoons, polka dots, checker boards and pictures of bugs make it a perfect option available for kids.</b></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>No wonder because of these facts one can deny about the popularity and craze of these shoes among the kids. They have great quality and can easily fit properly and are available at the right price thus making them most popular among parents and kids as parents don’t have to hunt for the right shoes for the kids.\n<b>No matter style whatever style and variety one wants for their little ones Vans has made it available for them.  </b>                    </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(101,1,100,1,'how to spot fake vans',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6167281346/\" title=\"vans-logo by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6178/6167281346_32f4759bda.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" alt=\"vans-logo\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Check the Logo</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>All the Vans shoe has a logo of VANS written in capital letters.The \"V\" will look like Square root symbol..You will also be able to see capital \"R\" inside a circle just next to the logo.Please check the logo (as shown in the image at the top) before <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net\">buying vans</a>.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Check the Sole for Star of David</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Just near the ball of the foot,you will see a <b>pattern of interlocking six sided stars</b>.Just as shown in below image.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6166745587/\" title=\"vans-star-of-david by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6170/6166745587_9d369d4b38.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"510\" alt=\"vans-star-of-david\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Check the stiching</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>All the stiching done on the shoe should be strong and even.Try to pick stich using the nails,if it does not comes out than the it is <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-customize-vans-shoes\">original vans</a>.If two line of stiching are running together,then they must be identical and distance between them must remain the same.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Check quality of rubber toe</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Vans shoes have the best rubber toes and the <b>bend easily as they are designed for extreme sports</b>.So try to bend to bend the shoes near toes.It will not bend easily in case of fake vans.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Check the price</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Vans shoes are generally priced between <b>40 to 70 US dollars</b>.So if a guy is selling Vans for 10 USD ,it will be a fake.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Match the Design</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Take the printout of Vans Model that you are buying from the Vans website.</b>Match every pattern and color before buying from any store.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Buy Vans from Reputed Places Only</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Always buy Vans from official Vans website or from reputed places like <b>Journeys,Target,Zappos</b>,etc.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Contact vans Customer service</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Take the photo of shoe from your mobile and send it to Vans customer care and wait for their answer.The email address is <b>vanscustserv@vfc.com or you can try their toll free number 1-800-826-7800.</b></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Again have a look at the price that you are paying. <b>If you are paying fewer amounts than the normal supposed amount, chances are high that you have a fake one and you would end as loser. </b>Sometimes you may get a chance to get hold of stolen Vans shoes at half of the original price. It is better to stay away from those kinds of trashes.<b>You can always compare with your friends who use original Van shoes and can take their feedbacks to know more about the product you are going to buy.</b> Go straight inside Vans show room and buy yourselves and family Vans shoes. You can guarantee yourselves with the real quality stuff and can stop worrying about fake ones.                   </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(102,1,101,1,'How to customize vans shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6168960441/\" title=\"vans custom shoes 1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6170/6168960441_d511063ee4.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"276\" alt=\"vans custom shoes 1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Vans offers everyone the choice to create custom shoes of his own choice on their website from 2004.These <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/vans-clearance-shoes-for-men\">custom shoes</a> will help you to look different in the crowd.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/iiIGmQdwSAE\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Instructions to customize Vans Shoes</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>In order to customize shoes go to the official website of Vans Shoes i.e., <b>shop.vans.com.</b> </li>\n<li>Then click on the option <b>Custom Shoes</b> which is given on the left hand side of the page to start customization. </li>\n<li>On the next page there are pictures of various styles of <a href=http://www.thevansshoes.net/vans-clearance-shoes-for-men\">Vans shoes like old skool,slip-on,Era and 106</a>.Choose a shoe style which you want to customize.</b> Click on the appropriate picture of the shoe to continue.</li>\n<li>Now you have to select <b>\"gender\" and \"size\"</b> and Click on Next to continue.</li>\n<li>On the nest screen,you will see a large number of shoes displayed as strip.Choose and click on the image that appeals to you.Keep in mind,these displayed shoes are just like templates and it is to give you an idea about how the custom shoe will look like. </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Vans divides its shoes in eight areas(Vamp,quarter,heel counter,vamp binding,foxing,foxing stripe,elastic gore,collar lining).These areas will be shown on the right hand side.You can select any of 8 mentioned areas and customize the color of that section by choosing one of many displayed colors.</li>\n<li>You can view your work from three different angles (top,back and side).These options are displayed just below the shoe.</li>\n<li>You can take the printout of your design by clicking on <b>\"Print\"</B> button at the bottom.</li>\n<li>You can click <b>share</b> button at bottom to email or sms you the link of your design.</li>\n<li>You can save some of your recent designs in <b>scratchpad</b> by clicking on \"+\" button at bottom.</li>\n<li>There is also a <b>chat</b> button at the bottom.Vans now offers the chat option while designing so that you can take inputs from our friends while designing.</li>\n<li>Click on <b>add to cart</b> ,Once you are satisfied with your design.</li>\n<li>You have to login with your Vans Id now to login to Vans website and place your order.</li>\n<li>The shoes are available within 5-7 weeks once you place an order. </li>\n<li><b>Please create a account on Vans website before creating the design.</b></li>\n<li>Now <b>106 Vulcanised Vans</b> are available for customization.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Thus it is very easy to customize and order the unique vans shoes of your own choice. The only thing which is required is to have an internet connection and account on vans website to avail the opportunity to order the unique shoes anywhere you want. <b>So if you want to wear the unique shoes which are designed by you then vans is the best option available.</b></p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(103,1,102,1,'How to repair vans shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6172170566/\" title=\"repair vans shoe 1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6161/6172170566_2a2c69857c.jpg\" width=\"451\" height=\"500\" alt=\"repair vans shoe 1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Soles of my Vans have become loose</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Buy a tube of <b>shoe gloo</b> and Clean the area where you have to apply the glue.Apply the medium amount of gloo on <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net\">vans shoes</a> and apply pressure on gloo from both sides  for 3 minutes.After that wipe the excess glue and wait for 1 day.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/pjg379TX0h4\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>There is ripping on top of my Vans</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Just clean the shoe and dry it properly.After that apply Stormsure adhesive (water proof) around the edges of ripped area.Place a patch (with something written on it) carefull over the hole and apply pressure from both ends on your <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net\">vans sneakers</a>.Wipe the excess glue and wait for 24 hours.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Heel of my Vans shoe is worn out or there is a hole in my sole</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Appy the process same as above.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>I feel pain in ankles while wearing Vans</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You need better <b>arch support.</b>Place some gel soles inside the shoe.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>White rubber area of Vans have turned yellow.What to do?</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Apply toothpaste ove the white rubber area.After that apply 10 to 15 strokes of toothbrush and rinse it with water.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>If the problem happens within 2 weeks of buying,return the shoes and ask for refund.</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>In case of more serious damages,please take our shoe to a professioal shoe repair shop</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Even though the shoes are highly durable, they are subject to wear and tear. Don’t panic if your favourite Vans shoes has a tear or any damages, they can be fixed very easily.Since Vans Shoes are quite different from typical footwear, it is recommended to contact the seller to fix the damages, where in most cases, sellers extend warranty on replacement parts.<b>Ripping in the Vans shoes is the most common problem experienced by many users of Vans shoes, who have been using it for a longer period. Fixing the ripping is quite easy. Any mild or minimal tear in the fabric can be fixed by applying a small quantity of glue. </b>However, prior fixing the ripping with glue, ensure to remove the lace and clean the shoes to remove the dirt. Sometimes, glue might not be sufficient enough to repair the damages, where <b>waterproof adhesives can be used.</b></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Fading is yet another common problem required to be repaired by the user,</b> where the Vans shoes are more likely to fade away due to improper cleaning method and using harsh detergents. The best thing about Vans shoes is that they can be customized to conceal the damages, which can be easily done through dyeing.<b>Dyeing the Vans shoes is an effective repairing option of the faded shoes.</b>Either it is an old Vans shoe or a faded Vans shoe; it can be revitalized by applying fabric dye in a darker shade of the shoe. <b>Lacing the Vans shoes is an art and it conceals most of the damages of the Vans shoes.</b>                       </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(104,1,103,1,'What to wear with blue vans shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6163667536/\" title=\"blue vans 1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6177/6163667536_8bdcc2c62f.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"448\" alt=\"blue vans 1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Blue vans goes with almost any type of clothes and be assured that you will get a lot of compliments.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Some of the suggestions to match your clothes with blue vans</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-white-vans-shoes\">White</a> and blue check shirt with faded low rise jeans.</li>\n<li>Gray biker jacket,blue sleeve shirt with mid rise legging style jeans.</li>\n<li>Silk chiffon tops with khaki shorts.</li>\n<li>Jersey tank with open vest and a <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-blue-vans-shoes\">navy blue</a> denim shorts.</li>\n\n</br>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/5NCpiKJIyHQ\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n</br>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a>\n\n</br>\n\n</br>\n\n<li>Light colored tunic shirt ,cardigan,lace cami,sweater with some nice stickers,floral dress with scoop neckline and light colored cami looks best with any variant of blue vans.</li>\n<li>Try matching bracelets,necklaces and sunglasses to add to your look.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-black-vans-shoes\">Black Boot</a> cut jeans and white blouse.Add blue bracelet and golden.You can opt for a layered shirt instead of a blouse.</li>\n\n</br>\n\n\n<li>Light colored t shirts looks best with blue vans.Add a dark colored hat to your clothing.</li>\n<li>Try white or gray v-neck t-shirt with red cardigan.</li>\n<li>Faded or light colored jeans looks best with blue vans shoes.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Blue vans are in fashion and has great effect on the appearance of the person. They are the perfect summer shoe.</b>More and more people will notice a pair of vans blue shoes. Blue and white makes an excellent color combination. The cotton shoelace, foam insole and rubber outsole makes this shoe extremely comfortable to wear.With blue vans you can wear blue denim jeans and a v neck t-shirt . Women can wear vans with skinny jeans and a plaid shirt. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>They look great with matching clothes. The blue vans shoe goes well with skinny jeans and t-shirt.</b> They also look good with blue or black skinny jeans or with a black or white t-shirt. They also look great with denim shorts. Capri’s and other stuff also make a great combination with these shoes.One can also wear vans with shorts but  try to match the colors. A navy blue short with white sleeveless top and utility jacket looks great with navy blue vans with a white sole . Accessorize it with long necklace and bangles as it looks great.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(105,1,104,1,'Hello kitty vans shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6166408479/\" title=\"vans hello kitty 2 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6155/6166408479_435de009da.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"304\" alt=\"vans hello kitty 2\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br>\nThis shoe line is a tribute to Sanrio pop icon Hello kitty.It is available as <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net\">classics</a> and slip ons for both kids and adults.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>What to wear with Hello Kitty Vans shoes</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Cute pink or green t shirts with white roll up shorts is amazing combination with hello kitty.</li>\n<li>Cut off bermuda shorts with <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-blue-vans-shoes\">light blue</a> oversized t shirts is another great choice.Diamond earrings will add to the beauty.</li>\n\n</br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/FFM8deD3cig\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a>\n\n\n\n\n</br>\n\n\n<li>Black blazer,pink vest top and skinny jeans(navy blue).</li>\n<li>Try Floral top and pink trousers is good for night outs and party.</li>\n<li>Try <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-pink-vans-shoes\">Pink</a> sweater,with jeans skirt and pink earrings.</li>\n<li>Pink skirt with black and white stripe t shirt always looks great with hello kitty vans shoes.</li>\n<li>My personal favorite is White roll up top,maroon shorts with blue necklace.</li>\n<li>Pink earrings,necklace ,watch and bracelet will always add to the beauty of hello kitty shoes.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br>\n</br></p>\n\n<p>Hello kitty van shoes will increase your thinking power. Yes!  You would reach a point of exhaustion  to choose one pair as all pairs has stunning designs and colors. You would try resisting temptation to buy more than one pair hello kitty van shoes.The key advantages of these shoes are that it comes in all sizes and forms and cater to the needs of family. <b>You can see varying colors like pink and designs splashed across the body of shoes.</b> The other key advantages of these shoes are that these shoes are that boys and girls will like it as designs do meet their taste and interest.<b> Cute designs splashed across these shoes would help you to become the toast of your neighborhoods as everyone would flock around you</b>, praising about your hello kitty van shoes. <b>Slip-on shoes</b> are also available with this brand and would meet the demands of young kids.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You can face the wrath of your family members as you would always walk inside the house with this shoe and would feel pain to keep aside without wearing it. You need not look anywhere else for casual wear and the key attributes of these shoes are the versatility it offers and moreover it is stylish also. You can use these shoes for travel and work purpose also. <b>The product durability is good and it comes in right sizes and right width catering to the needs of consumers. You can use these shoes as beach wear as the cushion comfort is great and would support your legs in beaches and it is lightweight also.</b>Hello kitty van shoes will help you look better and would improve your confidence level and would make you center of attraction in a crowd. You will just wear it with everything, and you would hate stepping out without these shoes.                      </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(106,1,105,1,'Vans watermelon shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6164995295/\" title=\"vans-watermelon-1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6170/6164995295_263b1e9f78.jpg\" width=\"332\" height=\"500\" alt=\"vans-watermelon-1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Vans watermelon shoes are available for toddlers and girls.They are available in two styles : <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/vans-slip-ons-for-women\">authentic and slip ons</a>.These shoes are priced between 25 to 32 USD.The canvas is of red color with black dots and Vans Logo on the side.It has a comfortable fitting (both lengthwise and widthwise) and looks cool on both <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/orange-vans-shoes-for-kids\">kids and girls</a>.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/wJngUfdIpl4\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Wear it with short silver skirt and tight red t-shirt.Add silver bracelet and necklace to our clothing.You will look stunning.Another good choice is denim white shorts with Black shirt.Add gold bracelet and earring.A silver or red handbag will add to your beauty.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/vans-watermelon-shoes\">Audrey Kitching</a> modeled for these watermelon shoes prior to their release.</li>\n</br>\n\n<li>You can buy these shoes from Vans,Journes,zappos,amazon,ebay,alloy,etc.</li>\n<li>Unfortunately you can not custom design watermelon shoes on vans website.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>One of the most popular and most attractive models of vans shoes designed exclusively for toddlers and women is Vans Watermelon Shoes. <b>These shoes are more popularly referred as fruits collection among the women. </b>Vans watermelon shoes are always highly demanded. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Watermelons look attractive in the combination of red, green and white with tiny black seeds. </b>Vans watermelon shoes are produced in the same pattern and colour offering a cool look. These shoes are characterized by a typical colourful watermelon pattern with green base, white fabric liner, red body with exciting patterns of black dots. The fabric features a bold look and offer delight to the eyes and the colourful design and patterns offer delight to the feet. Vans watermelon shoes are widely used by several celebrities because of the cool look and comfort. These shoes are not only used as a style statement, but also used by skateboarders. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Vans watermelon shoes are available in different sized for kids and women. <b>Vans shoes produced in two different models : watermelon shoes with lacing and watermelon shoes in boot model.</b> The attractiveness as well as the availability of vans watermelon shoes in different sizes (including bigger size for women) tempted men.Vans watermelon shoes are best suited with skirts and three fourth jeans. Any outfit in red or black colours suits well with these shoes. For Toddlers, almost all outfits look great and cute with vans watermelon shoes. Vans watermelon shoes are the ideal choice of gift for birthday parties.                       </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(107,1,106,1,'Advertise on Vans Website',1,'<p>This is very popular website for the lovers of Vans Shoes.The daily traffic varies between 150 to 250 unique visitors.On an average five thousand (5000) unique visitors will see your ad every month.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>These ad SLOTS are great oppurtunity for anyone who wants to sale Vans shoes online.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Payment will be through paypal . Contact email : sanjeevnjha@gmail.com.Please mention \"vans ads\" as email subject.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><strong>Available Ad Slots</strong> </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><em>1)Banner (ad slot 1</em>)</p>\n\n<p>Rate/per month = 65 USD per month</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><em>2)Right below the menu(ad slot 2</em>)</p>\n\n<p>Rate/per month = 35 USD per month</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><em>3)In place of adsense ads (ad slot 3</em>)</p>\n\n<p>Rate/per month = 150 USD per month</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>20 Percent discount will be given to buyers who will buy ads for 6 months.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>For better understanding of ad positions please see below images.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><strong>Note</strong> :</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You have to provide your own images for stores.    </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(108,1,107,1,'Wear Vans Shoes for style and comfort',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6163131211/\" title=\"vans home 1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6151/6163131211_1fdab8c475.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"361\" alt=\"vans home 1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Vans produced the sleeper hit dogtown and z boys in 2002.</li>\n<li>Vans produces surfing magazine airshow(SMAS) in 1999.</li>\n<li>Vans Era (red and blue) was the professionall designed shoe for skateboarders.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/vans-slip-ons-for-women\">Vans slip on</a> was introduced in 1979.It soon grew in popularity because of comfort and designs.It gain further boost because of Sean Penn</li>\n<li>Steve Caballero was first signature <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/vans-skate-shoes-for-girls\">skateboarding shoe from Vans</a>.</li>\n<li>Geoff Rowley is the best selling signature shoe of Vans till date.</li>\n\n</br>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/Bo98QUzE2gs\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n</br>\n\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n\n</br>\n\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n\n</br>\n\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a>\n\n</br>\n\n<li>Vans was bought by VF corp in 2004 for 396 million dollars.</li>\n<li>Vans started its online sale in 2004 and its a great success.</li>\n<li>The price of first <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/history-of-vans-shoes\">vans shoe</a> for men was 4.99 USD.</li>\n<li>Vans product line stands at 173 now compared to 3 when it started.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Vans is one of the most popular brand of shoes ever made.Its popularity cuts through generations and genders.<b>Vans started their line in 1970\'s with the launch of \"authentics\" shoes.</b>In 1970\'s ,its popularity grew among Skateboarders because of great styles,color choices,low price and better biomechanics.<b>Vans slip ons gained popularity in 1980\'s because of the movies Fast Times at Ridgemont High.</b></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You can buy vans shoes from stores of Journeys,vans,Target or Foot locker.You can also order it online from Vans website or from Ebay or Amazon.I personally prefer to buy from stores because i like exact fitting.\nVans was the first company to create skateoarding shoes.<b>Vans launched steve caballero signature skateboarding shoes in 1989.Later on it partnered with Johnny Layton ,Geoff Rowley ,etc to launch its other signature shoes.</b>Till date,vans remains the number one choice for skateboarders and other atheletes across the world.It also creates shoes for other extreme sports like BMX bikes and skateboarding.</p>\n\n<p></br> </p>\n\n<p><b>Vans was started by Paul Van Doren in 1966.</b>It soon grew in popularity as they were very durable because they created better and thicker soles.Vans has always managed to  meet public expectations and changing tastes with times.They are always trendy because they launch shoes in new colors and designs for men ,women and kids.<b>Vans even gives you option to create custom shoes on their website from 2004.</b>It gives you an oppurtunity to create and unique vans shoes that everyone will be jealous of ! </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(109,1,108,1,'Vans boots for women',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6172440140/\" title=\"vans boots for women 2 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6154/6172440140_99fc3db382.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" alt=\"vans boots for women 2\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br>\nVans boots make any women look stylish and help her stand out in the crowd.It is one of the best addition to <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/\">Vans collection of shoes</a>.The popularity of these boots is comparing well with skating and snowboarding shoes because these boots are trendy and comes in different styles .Vans boots are beyond comparison.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/XkM1rAHLkGg\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Vans boots are very simple in design but are highly efficient and comfortable wear. They boots are comfortable and high in durability.Boa lacing looks good on <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-blue-vans-shoes\">Vans boots</a>.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Vans Fargo Boots are stylish upper pattern shoes with the great arch support or feet.These boots show the remarkable performance on the slopes because of excellent grip. They also provide supportive fit which increases the support and have extraordinary features that promises excellent ride on any travel and tours.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br>\nVans Hi Standard Snowboard shoes is excellent for hiking and have air holes for fighting any kind of bad smell. These shoes provide a day long comfortable ride on the mountains. Vans Kira Boot is a different type of boot and It is adjustable at each end.Vans boots are the dynamic selection at the affordable price. These boots are excellent in design simplicity.<b> Slim shapes, high quality materials, performance-built Bio mechanics  technology, and vulcanized rubber waffle outsoles</b> come together in a near-perfect but understated package that allows for limitless improvisation.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Fine leather inning, genuine leather tongue and solid soles with power grip have made these boots the preferred choice for all those who want comfort when they walk and play. </b>Trusted for years now for its durability, Vans footwear have brought smiles to all those who have ever used these once at least.Vans Shoes are great for footwear fans who keep up to date fashion. These boots are very comfortable to wear because the boot covers are made of fabric.The black color option with white logo combination is full of stylish accent.                       </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(110,1,109,1,'Orange Vans shoes for kids',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6166248094/\" title=\"orange vans 1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6166/6166248094_f949b8bcdd.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" alt=\"orange vans 1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<h3>Some of the dressing tips and suggestions for orange Vans shoes </h3></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>Wear White sleeveless t shirt with black polka dots and plain white bow skirt</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/yellow-vans-shoes-for-women\">Wear Yellow colored</a> scoop long tank with white denim short</b></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-black-vans-shoes\">Try Black</a> skinny jeans with purple cropped t shirt</li>\n<li>Try Black roll sleeve printed t shirt with white biker jeans .Add stud belt,yellow earring,silver bracelet and pink handbag.</li>\n\n</br>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/Q1KKPqECDLY\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n</br>\n\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a>\n\n</br>\n\n</br>\n\n\n<li>Bright floral crop t shirts and denim jeans looks good with orange vans shoes</li>\n<li>Purple,yellow and black printed t shirts with denim shorts or black mini skirt <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/orange-vans-shoes-for-kids\">looks cool with orange vans</a> </li>\n</br>\n\n<li>Polka and strips on the top compliments the orange vans shoes.</li>\n<li>Try to match earring,watch,handbag,necklace and bracelet colors with the orange color.</li>\n<li>A jacket,sweatshirt and cargian will add to the look over shirt or t shirt.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Orange Vans shoes for kids are a lovely proposition.</b> Have creativity with your child and walk with them to beach when sun sets and show them how matching the nature color is with the color of shoe that they wears. <b>Sun orange is a color that attracts young minds and would encourage them to wear shoes.</b>  The designs that come with this color would make these shoes stand out and would meet their fashionable needs.There are occasions when parents would worry about their children not wearing well for occasion and these shoes would discard those worries. The shoes come in various sizes and widths .Orange Vans shoes come in various selection models and the range is amazing as always. <b>There are slip-on model for these shoes and they are affordable also.</b> The product durability is amazing and comfort level of these shoes is also on a high.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Irrespective of the color, the shoes are of high quality and would endure the rough ride outdoors.<b> Kids love the attraction they get from others and orange is an ideal color to catch attention of onlookers.</b> Orange when mixed with black would give a sensational feeling to wearers and there is every chance that people will flock around your kids. <b>Orange van shoes for kids will bring an enthusiasm to your children to walk outside, to go out to school, to go out to park, and they would soak all the attention they get from others.</b> Affordability coupled with quality makes these shoes stand out along with cool designs and cool colors. It is not only children that get attracted to these types of shoes but it also attracts adults.                       </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(111,1,110,1,'vans skate shoes for girls',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6169527434/\" title=\"vans skate shoe 2 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6161/6169527434_0214235778.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" alt=\"vans skate shoe 2\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Vans skate shoes have very high quality thick rubber sole and hence they last very long time even with a shoe killing sports like skating.They dont rip even with your regular flip tricks and ollies while skating.They give you very good grip on our skateboard.You can  <a href=\" http://www.thevansshoes.net/hello-kitty-van-shoes \"> wear these shoes  </a> even if you dont skate because they are durable and comfortable.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/f8BRjazrvpE\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>What womens can wear with Vans skate shoes</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-black-vans-shoes\">Wear Black colored</a> long sleeve T shirt with silver splatter denim shorts with Pink colored skate shoes </li>\n</br>\n<li>Try floral tank,denim hot pants with purple skate shoes</li>\n<li>Pink plaid shirt and black skirt looks cool with dark grey vans skate shoes</li>\n<li>Pink cut out shoulder tee and jeans short is a great combination with black skate shoes</li>\n<li>Wear black off shoulder top and knee length jeans with vans skate shoes of white color. </li>\n<li>Try to match color of earring,watch,handbag,necklace,bracelet,etc with the color of our shoe. </li>\n<li> Loose and baggy pink crop t shirt with white or black denim shorts or skirts looks cool with any dark colored skate shoe </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Vans skate shoes for girls are new rage in ever- changing society. </b>The designs of the shoes are cute and would satisfy all. Boys and men had dominated skateboard for long period. Women and girls have started entering the skateboard arena in recent times .There have been demand to meet the changing needs of women and girls. <b>These shoes do come in traditional black color with laces .</b> The shoes are not meant only for skating purpose but also meet the changing fashion style statement of girls. The new style of shoe means that girls can wear it at any occasion .</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>The shock absorbing feature of this shoe is intact and would help the skater when she jumps off the board. </b>The wrapping of shoe is done to give extra support to girl skaters .<b>The stitching on girl’s shoes is slightly different from boys to give shoes a feminine look.</b> Girl’s shoes also have double stitching like boys shoes to give longer shelf life. Girl’s shoes do overcome the strict completion offered by boy’s shoes.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>The skating shoes for girls meet the increased pressure of skating and lasts longer than expected. </b>The shoe durability is of high quality and is also skater friendly. You can buy discounted Van skate shoes from your favorite store.Van skate shoes for girls would surpass customer expectations. <b>The advantage of these shoes is that it is not only meant for sporting arena but also for daily use. </b>Join the ever- increasing list of satisfied customers and get committed to high quality.                     </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(112,1,111,1,'What to wear with pink vans shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6163134565/\" title=\"pink-vans-1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6176/6163134565_9fda016aff.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"500\" alt=\"pink-vans-1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br>\nPink vans looks good on every girl and kids.Girls absolutely love Pink vans as it makes them look even cuter.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Some Suggestions to match clothes with pink vans</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>Wear it with white broderie playsuit and black crop tank (crew neck) on top.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-white-vans-shoes\">Try White</a> t-shirt or blouse with pink cotton shorts.Add golden chain and gray handbags.</li>\n<li>Try White shirt with black skinny jeans.Add a shining metal belt.</li>\n<li>Wear black skirt with red top.</li>\n<li>Wear it with <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-black-vans-shoes\">Black vans</a> romper and hanging silver necklace.</li>\n\n</br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/z8w64SkkMmM\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a>\n\n</br>\n\n</br>\n\n<li>Black vest,faded denim shorts and sunglasses is another good combination.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-pink-vans-shoes\">Pink</a> sweatshirt with black leggings(preferrably silver stripes) looks good on all occasions.</li>\n</br>\n\n</br>\n\n<li>Try boot cut jeans with navy blue top.</li>\n<li>Wear cardigan,blazer or jacket over t-shirt or top to create layered feeling at the top.</li>\n<li>Black and silver laces looks best with pink shoes.</li>\n<li>Try to match belt,hat,necklace and or earrings with your pink vans shoes.</li>\n<li>Wear White and black striped shirt with black skinny jeans.Wear socks to avoid showing ankles.Tuck jeans in case it is long.</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Pink Vans shoes have become a hot talk in the fashion world . They are very popular among the younger generation and are very easy to find at an affordable price. Pink is a feminine color</b> and has always been the defining color for females. Most retailers around the world use this color for advertising their products as it has always been a popular color in females. Pink color is always considered as delicate and eye catching. It is known for its softness and uniqueness.Vans offers a great variety of pink shoes  for the men. For women, vans have high top shoes, pink sneakers and skate shoes. <b>These shoes have unique design with the mixture of various colors like pink, blue, white, yellow and aqua blue</b> which make them look gorgeous. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>These shoes are versatile and they will look stunning with any casual outfit. </b>They will look cool with dark jeans, skinny jeans or short shorts and you can wear a t-shirt or any other top on it. Skinny jeans with graphic t-shirt  and pink accessories will give a hot look.Pink shoes with white checks are quite popular among the youth as they are perfect to mix and match.Pink has always been a hot color and the pink vans shoes are a part of today’s fashion. <b>Pink van shoes have been more in demand among girls and kids.</b> They look more comfortable, stylish and unique on female sex.                        </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(113,1,112,1,'how to stretch vans shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* vans shoe square */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"4618508294\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 250;\ngoogle_ad_height = 250;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6165144629/\" title=\"stretch-vans-shoes by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6164/6165144629_3d8bb7ec76.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"500\" alt=\"stretch-vans-shoes\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>The best solution is to wear shoe for one week and give it time to expand and adjust as per your feet.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net\">Shoe</a> stretcher  expands the shoes both lengthwise and widthwise.Always buy a two way shoe stretcher for this purpose.Leave stretcher inside the shoe for 24 hours to get the perfect fitting.</li>\n<li>Place water balloon inside the shoe and place it inside the freezer for 12 hours.Once the water inside balloon turns into ice,the surfeace area of balloon will increase and expand our shoes.Make sure that there is no leakage of water as it will damage our shoes.</li>\n\n</br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/qf5mJ7aR2t8\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br>\n\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-spot-fake-vans\"> How to spot fake vans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/how-to-wear-vans-with-skinny-jeans\"> How to wear vans with skinny jeans</a>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/what-to-wear-with-grey-vans-shoes\"> What to wear with grey vans shoes</a>\n\n</br>\n\n<li>Wear shoe and blast hot air from hair dryer on problem areas.This solution is very useful for fixing specific problem areas inside the shoe.Make sure that you are wearing a <a href=\"http://www.thevansshoes.net/vans-knee-high-socks\">thick sock</a> and wearing shoes while blasting hot air.</li>\n\n</br>\n\n</br>\n<li>Use alcohol to stretch leather shoes.</li>\n<li>You can also take it to a shoe repair shop.There will be many such places in your location,you just need to search online.</li>\n<li>These methods are good only for stretching shoes a little.If you are down by one size,please go and buy new pair of shoes.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>How to stretch Vans shoes is a tricky question. Wearers may face blisters and pain after wearing shoes for one hour and they would like to get their shoes stretched a bit so that pain would recede in later wears.Stretching shoes would increase the comfort level of users and make shoe wearing a blissful experience.Buy shoe stretchers from shops near you and try to stretch your shoes.<b>Shoe stretcher spray will work if you are applying it on a leather shoe .</b>You should spray it on the area that you would like to stretch. After spraying you should insert the shoe stretcher and walk around in shoe. If that does not work, try the following methods.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>The first method is to try wearing more than one sock at a time and put Vans shoes.</b> It may stretch the shoes though there is no guarantee that it would really stretch the shoes. You can make someone else who is having a bigger leg to wear them and stretch the shoes. The chances are high that you can stretch your shoes as you wear them more as canvas can stretch after long wear. You can stuff inside your shoes with newspapers and try walking around inside your house with your shoes. The more you walk, the more it can stretch. <b>Washing your shoes more than once and getting it air dry would do wonders in stretching your authentic shoes. </b> Do not try drying them in any other methods as that can shrink your shoes.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(114,1,113,1,'About Us',1,'<p>We provide all the information on converse knee high shoes.We tell you about the types of converses,how to lace your converse,etc.We also tell you how to match converse with your dress.We try to give unbiased reviews on converse shoes.Please visit this website to know everything about shoes.Please provide your suggestions to improve the website.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(115,1,114,2,'Pink knee high converse will help you express feminine side of yours',1,'<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6175317218/\" title=\"pink converse by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6176/6175317218_7d9c6ec383.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" alt=\"pink converse\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Pink helps you to discover your <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/classic-yellow-converse-chuck-taylors-for-women-and-kids\">girlie side</a>.Pink is color of love,tenderness and caringness.\nBright pink colors reflect youthfulness inside you.It is color of romance.It spices up anything that you are wearing.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/Pks98EVRj-4\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/john-varvatos-converse-slip-on-shoes\">John varvatos converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">Kurt Cobain converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-ox-shoes-are-trendy-yet-variant-and-comfortable\">Converse Ox shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<h3>Do\'s with pink converse</h3></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li> It goes well with neutral shades like white, cream, chocolate,blue  </li>\n<li> Wear bright pink with grass green  </li>\n<li> Wear it with blue jeans and black top for trendy look  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Don\'t with Pink converse boots</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Avoid baby blue with pink </li>\n<li> Avoid bright pink with black  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(116,1,115,2,'History of converse shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6174790247/\" title=\"converse-history by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6153/6174790247_2b9a9dd8e9.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"466\" alt=\"converse-history\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse High-Tops are an American institution. The <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info\">best selling basketball shoes of all time</a>, Converse High-Tops have been owned by sixty percent of Americans at some point in their lives.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/w_zyqUivDJE\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/john-varvatos-converse-slip-on-shoes\">John varvatos converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">Kurt Cobain converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-ox-shoes-are-trendy-yet-variant-and-comfortable\">Converse Ox shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Established all the way back in 1908, the <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/knee-high-converse-shoes\">Converse Rubber Corporation</a> started out by making galoshes and all rubber boots for seasonal laborers. The company soon decided to produce shoes year round, and started focusing on athletic footwear as these are sold all year round. The rest, as they say, is history.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"420\" height=\"315\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/k8de8bxhSl0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>The Origin of the Converse High-Top </h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The sport of basketball was, at the time, in its ascendancy. More and more people were taking up this new and intriguing sport, a fact not lost on the management at the Converse Rubber Corporation.<b> After many attempts and revisions, the legendary Converse All Stars basketball shoe was produced in 1917.</b> It wasn\'t an instant hit as initial sales were slow. Original All Stars models came in a natural brown leather finish and black trim with the familiar all black canvas shoes coming out sometime in the 1920\'s.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Sales reached an all time high when Converse decided to <b>use the name of one-time basketball star Charles \"Chuck\" H. Taylor on their shoes.</b> The Converse High-Tops became the first mass produced American basketball shoe with an athlete’s endorsement. The popularity of such a move was undeniable, and Taylor\'s name started to appear on the side emblem of the All Stars basketball shoes. Converse had the market in an iron grip until the 1970s, when competing shoe makers gained dominance in the basketball footwear arena.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Although losing its market share in sportswear, Converse High-Tops were by now an all-American symbol. <b>The sneakers found newfound fame among rock musicians, artists and fashionistas thanks to its distinctive colors, style and comfort.</b> The fact that Converse High-Tops were cheaper than the high priced performance shoes from Nike also played a role in their widespread appeal. The company took advantage of this new found fame as a fashion symbol, and began producing their iconic Chuck Taylor All Stars in hundreds of variation that incorporated unusual prints, colors, patterns and styles.</p>\n\n<p><br></p>\n\n<p>The momentum did not last, however, and the <b>company experienced hard times throughout the 80s and 90s, eventually filing for bankruptcy in 2001.</b> The new owners maintained the iconic brand, but moved manufacturing operations to Asia in an attempt to save money. Eventually the new owners were bought out by Nike, Converse\'s one time rival.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>It is astounding to think that more than <b>800 million pairs of Converse High-Tops have been sold around the world.</b> While other sneaker brands wax and wane in popularity, the Converse brand has always remained fashionable in good times and bad. A shoe in continuous production for over 75 years, Converse \"Chuck Taylors\" has not changed design since 1949, a testament to the sneaker\'s timeless appeal.   </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(117,1,116,2,'Three Popular Lacing Styles for Converse Shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6174791095/\" title=\"converse lacing 1 by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6166/6174791095_e5718c607e.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"339\" alt=\"converse lacing 1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br>\nKeeping up its image as the <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-in-movies\">sneaker for fashionistas, Converse shoes</a> today come in many styles and colors, although their iconic Chuck Taylor All Stars remains their best selling model. Throughout the years Converse fans have developed different ways of lacing their beloved shoes to give it a distinct appearance. Here are three popular ways of lacing your <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/dr-seuss-converse-shoes-for-kids-and-adults\">Converse sneakers</a>:</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/8Y8MhQoYRq0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/john-varvatos-converse-slip-on-shoes\">John varvatos converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">Kurt Cobain converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-ox-shoes-are-trendy-yet-variant-and-comfortable\">Converse Ox shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br>\nAn all American classic, Converse shoes burst onto the scene all the way back in the 1900s and remains to this day one of the country\'s most popular sneakers.<a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/knee-high-converse-shoes\">Converse sneakers have a timeless appeal</a> that has kept them in the public consciousness for all these decades. Sometime in the 70s the Converse sneakers made the jump from strictly athletic shoes to fashion statement. The sneakers became extremely popular with <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-in-movies\">musicians, artists, kinds, teenagers and women</a>.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ol>\n<li><b>The Classic Cross-Lace.</b> Start by inserting the lace through the bottom two holes of the shoe (the end closest to the toe) and pull the laces. Pull the right lace through the nearest hole on the left side and do the opposite for the left lace. Continue lacing the shoes in this pattern by pulling both laces through opposite holes. If you\'ve done this properly the shoe will be completely laced with a classic \'x\' pattern. This type of lacing is favored by the purists, who like their Converse sneakers done up the way their parents and grandparents did.</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/A53xy88md-g\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ol>\n<li><p><b>The Loose Laced Look.</b> As with the cross-lace, start by pulling the lace though the bottom two holes of the shoe nearest the toe. Start lacing upwards the same way you would a cross lace. Stop three fourths of the ways up - you’re done! Try to walk around in your partially laced shoes and see how it feels. Make sure you\'re comfortable and can walk around easily with a loose laced shoe. This is a popular lacing style, giving your shoes the informal, grungy look. Loose lacing works best with Converse High-Tops.</p></li>\n<li><p><b>The Bottom Tie.</b> Not as common as the first two lacing methods, the bottom tie method nevertheless has its fans. To lace the shoe in this way you have to be wearing it. Start by pulling the lace through the top two holes nearest your ankle, and loosely weave them all the way down to the bottom two holes closest to your toes. Make sure you loosely weave the laces doing this. Once you reach the bottom of the shoe, tie the two lace ends in a classic bow, the same way you would in the cross lace. You now have a reverse cross lace, with the bow at your toes instead of near your ankles.  </p></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p></br></p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(118,1,117,2,'Converse knee high socks is neccessity for your shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6175318060/\" title=\"converse knee high socks by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6178/6175318060_a4bb63f58f.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"500\" alt=\"converse knee high socks\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse knee high socks are avaliable in wide range of colors and designs.It is made from either cotton or nylon.Cotton socks absorbs sweating easily but are costly and needs regular washing.Nylon socks are cheaper option but their absorbing ability is limited.High end socks are <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/dr-seuss-converse-shoes-for-kids-and-adults\">decorated with your favourite characters</a>.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/BtMchWveDJM\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/john-varvatos-converse-slip-on-shoes\">John varvatos converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">Kurt Cobain converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-ox-shoes-are-trendy-yet-variant-and-comfortable\">Converse Ox shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Why we need to wear socks with knee high shoes</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li> It absorbs sweat during warm seasons.It is must when you are wearing shoe in warmer season. </li>\n<li> A sock of appropriate thickness can give perfect fitting with your shoe </li>\n<li> It stops irritation and covers marks on your legs </li>\n<li> Decorated socks <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">adds to your style</a>. </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/mBJ27VzINBw\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br></p>\n\n<p>Just make sure that your socks are soft and gives you <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/orange-converse-shoes-for-kids-are-real-fun\">desired comfort level</a>.It will help your boot to slide on while wearing.Take good care of your socks.Wash them regularly to get rid of smell.After wash go for air dry method.Fold them carefully.Always choose socks that go with your dress while going out.So go and buy one.     </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(119,1,118,3,'Jack Purcell the badminton star on converse',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/