or a regular practice. Navy Men from Jack Purcell is another shoe that has a nice, clean look. <b>Preferred by badminton as well as tennis players</b>, this shoe has a timeless popularity. The premium laces running through the Metal eyelets add a classy effect to the embroidered tongue. The tender lining of fabric, cushioned inner-sole and the bumper Toe-cap of rubber are the rudimentary features oh this shoe.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>The OTR Leather-Mid of the Jack Purcell variety is elegant footwear, which complements the athlete look.</b> The upper part is made from rich, full-grain leather which enhances the elegancy as well as the comfort level of this sleek style-icon shoe. The eyelets are steel cramped and the dark brown lacing gives a sophisticated touch. The cushioned insole, rubber toe-capping and rubber outsole makes this footwear comfy yet stout.  <b>Jack Purcell® class has a trendy sneaker called LP II from Converse® that fulfills the Urban appeal to those who sport it.</b> The metallic eyelets has got ethnic eye lace-ups that make the shoe more appealing. The outsole made of rubber has got the signature mark embalmed on it. A removable padded foot bed lines the canvas for making the shoe wearing experience a very much comfortable one.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>A sophisticated shoe of the Jack Purcell is the Vintage OX Sneaker.</b> This Beige-Khaki-Tan, men’s footwear brings forth a soft, tender look. The upper portion is made of fabric like linen or cotton and lower portion includes manmade outsole. The Boat Slip-on is yet another variety of the Jack Purcell collection. There are metallic eyelets but no lacings are there; it refers to the archetypal Moc-toe design. The shoe has detachable foot bed along with the textile lined, rugged uppers. <b>LTT Ox is a globally famous, old- school style of the Converse shoes.</b> The upper portion is boldly styled by Disco-ready, flashy sequins. The outsole is rubber crafted to give a good tensile strength to the shoe. <b>Certain other momentous Jack Purcell footwear are Evo Tennis shoes, Black Canvas sneakers for women, Helen sneakers for Women, JP Saltwash-Leather.  </b>                               </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(120,1,119,2,'Buy Converse Knee High Only',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6174790935/\" title=\"converse knee high by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6157/6174790935_bb1ea76185.jpg\" width=\"493\" height=\"500\" alt=\"converse knee high\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>converse knee high brands available on amazon</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" width=\"640\" height=\"390\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/siema5KmHaE\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/john-varvatos-converse-slip-on-shoes\">John varvatos converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">Kurt Cobain converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-ox-shoes-are-trendy-yet-variant-and-comfortable\">Converse Ox shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Converse Chuck Taylor All Star Knee Hi</li>\n<li> Canvas Knee Boot Sneaker </li>\n<li> White Knee Sneaker Lace-up Boots Canvas  </li>\n<li> Plaid Black White Knee Sneaker Boots Canvas 20i Women  </li>\n<li> CONVERSE CT Tweed XXHI Boots Shoes  </li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-in-movies\">Converse Chuck Taylor</a> Swirl XX HI Unisex Boots   </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></b