/object></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4102/4903738809_71eac17a6a.jpg\" width=\"343\" height=\"500\" alt=\"converse-knee-high-shoes-4\" /></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>I am unable to find converse knee high size 4 </h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You should look in kids section or check for custom order if you are not finding right size.Its difficult to find size 4.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h2>You can design your own converse knee high shoes</h2>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.converse.com/?bhcp=1#/shoes\"> Design converse shoes online</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4135/4904328294_362eb7c3ba.jpg\" width=\"426\" height=\"500\" alt=\"converse-knee-hi-shoes-5\" /></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>How to Convince my parents to buy me high knee shoes</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Try to help your mom with house work and show her the pics of other girls wearing it.If it does not work,find a part time job any buy it from your earned money.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>zip up vs lace up</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Zip up is more convenient than lace up as it is quicker than tying it.You can easily slip in your shoes and zip it up.You can step up on loose laces and shoe will get dirty.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4095/4903738701_8bf17a686b.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"273\" alt=\"converse-knee-high-shoe-3\" /></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h2>How to lace my high knee converse shoes</h2>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Put the lace in top hole (near knee).Now move the lace from one hole to another till bottom.Go to below link to learn 33 methods of lacing your shoes:</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fieggen.com/shoelace/lacingmethods.htm\">How to lace your shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>How to buy knee high converse shoes if I live outside usa</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You can go to your country specific converse website :</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse Australia</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.converse.net.au/\">Converse australia</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse UK </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.converse.co.uk/\">Converse UK</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>What to wear with with knee high converse shoe :</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>skinny jeans</li>\n<li>black leggings </li>\n<li>red pink skirt </li>\n<li>white collared shirt</li>\n<li>v neck shirt</li>\n<li>Hoodie</li>\n<li>Tank tops</li>\n<li>casual skirt </li>\n<li>denim skirt</li>\n<li>plain shorts</li>\n<li>blaack booty shorts</li>\n<li>knee high jeans </li>\n<li>calf length jeans</li>\n<li>skirt with fringes</li>\n<li>Sweater</li>\n<li>Denim jacket</li>\n<li>sunglasses</li>\n<li>fitted tee</li>\n<li>necklace</li>\n<li>Black tights</li>\n<li>cartoon t-shirts</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Check the below link to see items that look good with your high knee converse boots</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.polyvore.com/cgi/set?id=1106514\">Item that look good on converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4093/4904327656_f646b90281.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"400\" alt=\"converse-knee-high-shoes-2\" /></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Avoid below points while wearing high knee shoes</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Do not wear leg warmers on top of them</li>\n<li>Do not wear revealling clothes</li>\n<li>Avoid wearing it with coloured skinny jeans as color will distract guys from looking at your shoes.</li>\n<li>Make sure that in summer you wear it on socks as it gets really sweaty.</li>\n<li>If your zipper broke or you lost your laces,Please dont throw your shoes.Go to store and buy an extra pair of laces or zipper.</li>\n<li>You can use brush to remove dirt and sticky items like tape to pull the hair.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h2>You can buy cheap knee high shoes at</h2>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Journeys</li>\n<li>Hot topic</li>\n<li>Alley</li>\n<li>Target</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Find cheap knee hi converse:</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Dont worry,If you do not have 70 dollar to pay for converse shoes.You can get exact look alike :</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You can search \"knee high shoes\" on google,ebay and amazon.After that select \"low to high\" from dropdown.You will be able to find a cheap converse shoes in 15 minutes.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You can try payless if you want to buy it under 35 dollars.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>These shoes almost look the same.No one will be able to tell the difference.   </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(123,1,122,3,'Slip on shoes looks cool on any feet',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6175219171/\" title=\"john varvatos by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6166/6175219171_e570e8d306.jpg\" width=\"334\" height=\"500\" alt=\"john varvatos\"></a>\n</br></p>\n\n<p>John Varvatos is yet another multinational company that has joined hands with Converse to venture into new ideas regarding footwear.<a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-low-tops-shoes-to-relax-your-feet\">Converse sneakers are quite popular</a> all around the world and John Varvatos is a renowned apparel manufacturer. These teams have merged to get the best out of their stock for the customers. <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/classic-yellow-converse-chuck-taylors-for-women-and-kids\">Several models fall under their new category of sneaker</a> production. </p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/BfeQo_VA-eE\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/john-varvatos-converse-slip-on-shoes\">John varvatos converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">Kurt Cobain converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-ox-shoes-are-trendy-yet-variant-and-comfortable\">Converse Ox shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br>\nWith the latest technologies and premium quality of manufacturing material, this brand promises to provide the best experience possible. John Varvatos Converse Star Player is a <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-high-heel-sneakers\">Men’s lace sneaker</a>, with a canvas upper wall and rubber outer sole to provide excellent grip.This model also has a lining made of fine texture. This shoe comes in two vibrant colors, dark brown and off white.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Similarly, the SAXX006, star tech high top, is a sneaker that will make our dreams come true.With the mesmerizing leather upper walls and the inner laces made of leather, chevron stripes and sole made of rubber, this footwear is versatile with its components. Another lovely model is the 122026, Chuck Taylor Oxford. This boot has the perfect combination of leather and rubber to provide excess comfort and grip simultaneously. The look and feel of the shoe is like being nostalgic and remembering the retro days. We can try this shoe in two colors, purple and white. <b>The 122132, Chuck Taylor Studded, is one of the best in the collection.</b> These high sewn hand made sneakers are limited edition material. Antique nickel studs flat studs make up the boot. A pinstripe lining, laces made from leather and red burnished outer design, gives this footwear a fascinating look.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>The 122522, studded Chuck Taylor, is available in two colors, black and off white.</b> These sneakers are embedded with flat studs made from nickel pyramid; laces made from leather, and have burnished gel on the outer parts of the shoe. <b>The perforated leather oxford, 121789,</b> usually incorporated the traditional low-top kind style, with perforated leather to create a feeling of distress and revamped nostalgic effects. This is another perfect retro shoe. This footwear is available in two colors only, black and white. <b>The 121790, oxford, has the same build as the previous shoe.</b> The only difference is that, this shoe has a sporty look along with the build of retro footwear. This shoe is also made from perforated leather and is available in two colors, green and black.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>The star canvas oxford, 121776, is a sporty as well as casual wear supporting footwear.</b> This is a low-top shoe with the upper wall canvassed with wax. A chevron logo, lining in pinstripe and a burnished outer look, gives the feel like this shoe is a complete package. Colors are also available for the shoe in dark blue and white. <b>The perforated leather footwear featuring a high-top facility, also known by 121768, is a traditional type shoe with high-top characteristics.</b> The footwear is decorated at places with perforated leather; a detailed work has been implemented at the upper region of the shoe with leather again. This upper layer leather is light in weight to support extra movement capabilities of the feet. This shoe is available in two colors, black and white.              </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(124,1,123,2,'How to clean knee high converse shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6174790399/\" title=\"clean converse shoes by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6159/6174790399_07be6c9188.jpg\" width=\"342\" height=\"500\" alt=\"clean converse shoes\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>It is very important to wash your chucks carefully.Wasing them in machines can lead to fading,wearing or even the loss of rubber soles.Please read below to learn how to wash your chucks in a better way.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/m_mZ5TbnXnc\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/john-varvatos-converse-slip-on-shoes\">John varvatos converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">Kurt Cobain converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-ox-shoes-are-trendy-yet-variant-and-comfortable\">Converse Ox shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>Prepare the cleaning mixture using white vinegar,hot water and baking soda.Mix them in equal amount to prepare the paste.</li>\n<li>Make sure that you dampen your shoes before cleaing.Easiest way is to removes laces and run them under tap water.</li>\n<li>Apply the paste on canvas in circular motion.Try to cover the maximum area in minimum strokes.</li>\n<li>Put your <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/knee-high-converse-shoes\">converse shoes</a> in a bucket full of lukewarm water.Rinse it properly till all the soda and vinegar are removed.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Tips</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Add bleach for white sneaker</li>\n<li>You can use tooth brush for proper cleaning.</li>\n<li>Always dry it in sun w/o the laces.Add laces only when the chucks are dried completely.</li>\n<li>You can repeat rinsing on the areas where stains are not removed.</li> \n</ul>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(125,1,124,3,'Converse sneakers based on comics characters',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6175747426/\" title=\"dr seuss converse by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6168/6175747426_06746859d1.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"348\" alt=\"dr seuss converse\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse has been <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/red-knee-high-converse\">manufacturing classy sneakers</a> for a long time now. They have excelled in this field and now they are prowling for more! A new taste of literature seems to have been added to their collection of shoes. Dr. Seuss, the famous book writer is lending his characters to be portrayed on the canvas of the converse sneakers.These two mind-boggling captains have teamed to produce the best from their collection. It is now cool and fun to be wearing such a pair of shoes which are <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/pink-knee-high-converse\">available for both kids and adults</a>.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/0IkmwM8CgPE\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/john-varvatos-converse-slip-on-shoes\">John varvatos converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">Kurt Cobain converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-ox-shoes-are-trendy-yet-variant-and-comfortable\">Converse Ox shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The latest advent from Converse, is trying this unique idea.Dr. Seuss has been specific about his jolly characters in his famous books and so are the show manufacturers.There are about 13 <a href=\"www.kneehighconverse.info/white-knee-high-converse\">different design available in all sizes</a>, from babies to the grown ups. One fish, low tops with two fish and high tops in a playful mood have given unique appearances to this new approach.There are the Bob, builder and also the Dora, explorer shoes available with converse now.These do not look shabby; in fact, they give quite an impressive look to the person wearing it. The shoes will be available in both the classic high and also the customary sneaker version.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Thing 1 will be accompanied by Thing 2 in some of the shoes, while other converse sneakers might picture the Cat in Hat characters. These sneakers pose a deep reference to Seuss at times. Some of the shoes might contain only <b>Seussian stripes</b> while others may refer to characters deeply. We do not need to get saturated while making our choice. The company has already inhabited a lot of the characters into their products. One fish, Red Fish, the Two Fish and Blue Fish, are some of the common themes that customers are comfortable with. The sneakers are available with special Velcro designs to suit the need of infants.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Like we all know, converse has the special technology to give us that extra comfort zone for our feet. The uppers of the sneakers are made from canvas and low tops are characterized with a unique three panel construction. Other exciting features include exciting colors of the shoelaces. These colors contrast the body of the shoe strongly. This gives a striking dazzle to the shoe. Moreover, every sole is made up of literary material. <b>Dr. Seuss’s work on comic and books are imprinted on the inner soles of these sneakers.</b> This shows how the manufacturers focus on the implementation of the theme.The most striking feature is that Converse themselves have got indulged into idea so much that they feel like renewing the designs everyday. With more than 60 books from Mr. Seuss, the company is free to depict a new design every now and then. If we have an idea about customizing our shoe from Converse, we can avail that option too. <b>Converse allows a full customization facility, where we can imprint our selection of Dr Seuss characters at our selected place. </b>            </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(126,1,125,2,'Converse features kurt cobain on shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6175220271/\" title=\"kurt cobain converse by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6154/6175220271_a17622dc91.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"288\" alt=\"kurt cobain converse\"></a>\n</br></p>\n\n<p>A number of collections are available from the Converse house that have taken a toll over the footwear market; <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/john-varvatos-converse-slip-on-shoes\">some of the premium modules</a> are John Varvatos shoes, Kurt Cobain shoes, Jack Purcell shoes, Dr Seuss shoes and Chuck Taylor shoes, One Star Shoes.All the above mentioned varieties have their unique feature. Kurt Cobain shoes are an elite range created by the Converse Firm.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/uuOtM4B5KCM\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/john-varvatos-converse-slip-on-shoes\">John varvatos converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">Kurt Cobain converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-ox-shoes-are-trendy-yet-variant-and-comfortable\">Converse Ox shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Kurt Cobain is a highly discussed variety of all the shoe-crafts under the Converse Marque. The assortment of Kurt Cobain Shoes can be classified into two slots. One of them is the “Vintagized” form of the <a href=\"\">Jack Purcell </a> lot as well as the <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/knee-high-converse-shoes\">Chuck-Taylor-High-Ankles</a>, along with the One Star swarm, while the other one is the Chuck Taylor varieties, sculpted with the writings as well as sketches that Cobain drafted in his journal, published in 2002. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse shoes have been a very important aspect of Cobain’s life; be it the early, rugged days of his life or the concert days, Cobain sported Converse all his life. Converse House is still working on, to craft more and more shoes from its collection into the <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">Kurt Cobain</a> Variety.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The latest upcoming variety of the Cobain model is the Kurt-Cobain-Custom-Chucks.The detachable cushioned foot bed, adds comfort to the textile “uppered” Custom model of Chucks Taylor. The Vintage model of the Chuck Taylor lot has been stitched with contrast colors to form the Kurt-Cobain-Converse-Chuck-Taylor-Vintage. These “vintagized”, ankle-high heels sport, denim uppers with steel eyelets. <b>Other Vintage models are Kurt-Cobain-Converse-One-Star-Vintage, Jack-Purcell-Vintage.</b> Next comes, the shoes that are littered with sketches as well as writings of Cobain. These shoes are generally the Ankle High Boots of the previously mentioned varieties. <b>Converse shoes have launched Kurt-Cobain-All-Star boots.</b> These shoes are carved with the writings of Cobain. The black writings on the white shoes bring the correct appeal in the shoes.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Some Kurt-Cobain-All-Star boots are sculpted with the paintings from the journals.</b> These boots have rubber outsole so that they can provide a proper traction. The fabric uppers offer a good breathing capability of the shoes. These shoes can be worn with Denim- Three-quarters teamed with a nice funky T-shirt. <b>The signature emblem of the Converse house remains attached to the shoe with a separate piece.</b> The Chuck Taylor lot of the Kurt Cobain Variety is formed from the black fabric, ankle length, and lacy boots of the All Star lot. The white sketches contrast the basic color of the shoes and make it eligible to give a rugged look. <b>Chuck-Taylor-low of the Kurt Cobain class is designed in the similar manner that is by sculpting the Cobain sketches on the Low shoes.</b> These shoes are good in spite of their price because they combine both comfort with quality as well as durability.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse is a global brand that specializes in engineering athlete wear. This is quite untrue that the shoes marketed by Converse are only for sportspersons; many youngsters love to sport these shoes for a funky hangout or for a cool look.Statistical studies have revealed that bikers prefer these Converse boots a lot.           </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(127,1,126,2,'Black knee high converse is versatile',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6175317142/\" title=\"black converse by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6154/6175317142_7fc394ca20.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"340\" alt=\"black converse\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Black matches with any clothes.Basically you dont have to worry about matching clothes if you are wearing black shoes.You can wear it everywhere.Black makes you <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-ox-shoes-are-trendy-yet-variant-and-comfortable\">appear slimmer and give you regal touch</a>.Try to repeat black somewhere in your clothing.Black shoe matches with any color like white,red,pink,blue,etc.</p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/vmeHZvAegRs\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/john-varvatos-converse-slip-on-shoes\">John varvatos converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">Kurt Cobain converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-ox-shoes-are-trendy-yet-variant-and-comfortable\">Converse Ox shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<h3>Don\'t with Black converse</h3></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li> Make sure that <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/john-varvatos-converse-slip-on-shoes\">your shoe is matching</a> belt and purse </li>\n<li> Avoid pastels </li>\n<li>Avoid going all black else you will look like will smith</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Black converse high knee -- video</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/0mx67zA5Ir0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(128,1,127,2,'Converse Shoes in Hollywood Movies',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<img src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4102/4903738809_71eac17a6a.jpg\" width=\"343\" height=\"500\" alt=\"converse-knee-high-shoes-4\" />\n</br></p>\n\n<p>Converse shoes have appeared in over 1000 hollywood movies.They have appeared in harry potter series,james bond movies and even in oscar winning rocky.Below i have compiled a list of most famous movies in which <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/dr-seuss-converse-shoes-for-kids-and-adults\">converse shoe</a> appears prominently.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h2> Mysterious Man With Red Shoes in Amelie (2001) Movie </h2>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/3HpIZrOH4zc\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/john-varvatos-converse-slip-on-shoes\">John varvatos converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">Kurt Cobain converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-ox-shoes-are-trendy-yet-variant-and-comfortable\">Converse Ox shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<div class=\"right-menu\">\n<h2> Hollywood Movie Names </h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Amelie</li>\n<li>American Pie</li>\n<li>Anaconda</li>\n<li>Back to the future</li>\n<li></li>\n<li>Deep rising</li>\n<li>Commando</li>\n<li>Fast and the furious</li>\n<li>Flubber</li>\n<li></li>\n<li>The girl next door</li>\n<li>Grease</li>\n<li>I robot</li>\n<li>Harry potter and the order of phoenix</li>\n<li></li>\n<li>Harry potter and half blood prince</li>\n<li>National Treasure</li>\n<li>National treasure book of secrets</li>\n<li>Quantum of solace</li>\n<li></li>\n<li>Rush hour</li>\n<li>Rocky</li>\n<li>Pulp fiction</li>\n<li>The Pursuit of Happiness</li>\n<li>Robo cop 3</li>\n<li></li>\n<li>The shining</li>\n<li>Spy kids</li>\n<li>Twins</li>\n<li>Stuart little</li>\n<li>Stuart little 2</li>\n</ul>\n</div></p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(129,1,128,2,'High heel shoes for men and women',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6175747208/\" title=\"converse high heel by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6171/6175747208_5306c4a5f7.jpg\" width=\"414\" height=\"500\" alt=\"converse high heel\"></a>\n</br></p>\n\n<p>Converse creations specially include Chuck Taylor shoes, The Weapon and some special editions like Nirvana, Sailor Jerry, Metallica and so many more. Another significant yet comfy creation of this corporation is Sneakers with High Heel.The High-Heel boots are <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/knee-high-converse-shoes\">available for both men as well as women</a>.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/uVW7SUj551Y\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/john-varvatos-converse-slip-on-shoes\">John varvatos converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">Kurt Cobain converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-ox-shoes-are-trendy-yet-variant-and-comfortable\">Converse Ox shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The Chuck Taylor amalgamation of retro high sneakers with boots of ankle height brings forth a classy panache. The wicked 6” heels along with the pointed toe zone make this shoe a <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/white-knee-high-converse\">trendy yet stylish one</a>. This Stiletto Sneaker looks absolutely impressive. The ankle length shaft as well as the pencil heel makes these shoes look erotic. An interesting collection of high-heel Sneaker is the Lea High, belonging to the <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-in-movies\">Chuck Taylor</a> class.These Sneakers are fashioned it of Black leathers with the laces being white. The Signature logo is embalmed at the tongue as well as the heel. The outsole is made of Rubber and bears a brown tint on it.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>PLAY-COMME-DES-GARÇONS is a modish Converse High Sneakers of the Red Heart variety. These Off-white sneakers sport a canvas, which is a bit high in the top. The toe region has a rubber Cap; white laces are used for tying the shoe. The shoe features’ eyelets of the Silver Tone. The heel region has a canvas panel that has black lining. The Tonal top-stitching along with the rubber outsole makes this Heart Signed work and making this 100% cotton shoe, a favorite one.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Triangle-Print-Marimekko is a High-top Sneaker that flaunts the geometric iteration print on the shoe body.</b>  The definitive design of this rubber heel shoe has a lace-up front apart from a toe-cap of rubber. This masterpiece has been skilled using Finnish craft art. These sneakers are comfortable for a day-long work due to the cushioned insole. <b>Comme-des-Garçons-Play is an exclusive lot of belonging to the Canvas Sneaker of the High-Top type.</b> This sneaker is a unisex one with the laced canvas. The outsole id made of Treaded rubber.   <b>The All-Star-Light is suede crafted</b>, leather high sneaker that comes from the Chuck Taylor class. The rubber-cap sneaker has a vivid textile lining along with Rubber Outsoles; these high-tops are obtainable is teo vibrant shades like Gray as well as the Metallic one.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>The XX High class of the All Star has been exclusively launched under the Chuck Taylor category.</b> These Knee-length shafts bearing Silhouette has got a canvas upper portion along with the rear, zipper closure that runs along the total length. The sidewalls of this toned, trim, Converse shoe has got a padded step-bed as well as a Toe-guard made of Rubber. Various other significant Converse Sneakers with high heels include <b>Converse Work 355, Composite Toe Work shoe, Converse Work 315, 391 Work Boots in green shade, athletic Hiker-Golden Tan, etc. </b>   </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse is a reputed rubber shoe firm in Massachusetts.Initially, converse specialized in making rubber shoes but later it advanced to the era tennis shoes. After a certain period, converse house moved on again with its new management to the epoch, where they started crafting basketball shoes. Slowly they emerged as one of the leading creators of shoes for athletes.       </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(130,1,129,2,'Get ready for combat',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6175747508/\" title=\"converse studded by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6179/6175747508_6e3dec1a29.jpg\" width=\"332\" height=\"500\" alt=\"converse studded\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Combat boots are mainly designed for the defense personnel.Combat boots are specialized in firm grip, ankle stability and for foot protection. With the change in fashion and style these boots are now designed and decorated with stones to give it a <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">fashionable look</a>. Studded combat boots are designed with innovative thoughts to make you look outstanding. With western outfits combat boots match the best.These boots are all time <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/knee-high-converse-shoes\">favorite for both men and women</a>.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/SJL4L7Fr6x0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/john-varvatos-converse-slip-on-shoes\">John varvatos converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">Kurt Cobain converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-ox-shoes-are-trendy-yet-variant-and-comfortable\">Converse Ox shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The studded combat boots give you a <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/\">bold and beautiful look</a>. It makes you look confident, aristocratic, smart and stylish. Online shopping has made it easier to purchase the combat boots at an affordable price. You can choose from the wide range and make the best deal. You can see the designs, colors and brand before bagging one for yourself. Some of the studded combat boots are:Army style studded combat boots give you a professional look. It has a flap studded that makes you more stylish.<a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/studded-converse-boots\">Bess Studded Converse boots</a> designed to let ventilation happens with the bullet design in it.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Pyramid studded straps, black in color with lace up with buckles, with external stitch and it is silver studded.Studded muffin combat boots comes in two colors. They have flips and the flips are studded with silver and golden effects.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>The studded converse boots give you a vibrant look.</b> Your entire personality changes when you wear a pair of combat boots. The boots are elegant and it suits the person who knows how to carry them. To break the monotony of shoes and slippers and sneakers you must shop for combat boots. They change your boring outfits into stunning looks. The converse boots were invented initially for the defense personnel and the security officers; however, <b>in today’s world combat boots have become a fashion.</b> With strap less dress, denims, trousers, leather jackets studded combat boots are must. You can increase your confidence level and can become the eye catcher even in the crowd. You can get them online with discounts and offers. Make the best deal by buying a pair today itself. <b>Studded converse boots are fashion for the rock stars and the models.</b> For their extraordinary performance and glamorous looks studded combat boots are must. Converse boots have been designed to protect your feet from insects, mud, and water logging. The special design helps you to have strong grip and firm ankle balance.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>The studded converse boots are informal shoes that can be even worn in offices.</b> The boots do not come in vibrant colors however; the designs and the delicate work that is done are decent. Ideally black, brown, maroon are the common colors that most of the combat boots are made of. The combat boots are comfortable though heavy. Both men and women are attracted towards the studded combat boots and are fascinated with the exclusive designs that are done on them. <b>Combination of silver and gold studs in some of the boots with thick satin lace makes them out of the world.</b>            </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(131,1,130,1,'Contact us',1,'<p>Feel free to ask anything related to knee high converse shoes.You can either drop a comment or fill the form below.We will honestly try to give you information on converse shoes.We do not claim that our word is final but it will help you to buy the converse shoe that fits in your budget and suits all your needs.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(132,1,131,2,'Why converse is no 1 choice among shoe buyers',1,'<p><img src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4135/4904328294_362eb7c3ba.jpg\" width=\"426\" height=\"500\" alt=\"converse-knee-hi-shoes-5\" /></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Knee high chucks were First made in the USA For a time during the 1980\'s. They are an extra high-top shoe with twelve pairs of eyelets so you can lace all the way up to your knee. They also have a fold down position,and extra snaps are placed on the sides of the shoe to hold the canvas in <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/three-popular-lacing-styles-for-converse-shoes\">place when you lace</a> in the fold down position. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" width=\"640\" height=\"390\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/FE5Rd_uIdqw\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The traditional side patch is placed higher on the shoe, and there is a smaller interior patch in each shoe that is revealed when it is folded down.<a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/distinctive-varieties-of-converse-cvo-shoes-for-men\">Many of the models</a> feature a pattern alternate color interior. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Knee-high chucks were revived in 2003 by Converse, and have been made\nin both canvas and leather models, some based on the traditional knee-high, and others emulating the monochrome look. They are mostly made in small batches and usually quickly sell out. Knee-high chucks are very popular in Europe, and more models are made for thot market than lor the U.S. market. A few models are made just to be worn in the knee-high position. Canvas models of the knee-high have been made in black white,blue denim, black monochrome, black-\nneon pink, b|ack-orange, camouflage,khaki, green with multicolored pattern,gray-pink,light-blue-yellow,orage-yellow,parch ment-olive, red bandana,\nroyal blue with multicolored pattern, and white with a multicolored pattern.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Variety of materials</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Over the years seasonal chucks have come out in a variety af alternate upper malerials besides canvas. These have included uppers made from gold or\nsilver metallic Fabric; a fur-like leopard pattern; embossed silk; corduroy; black blue, and natural white denim; black and navy blue hemp; and a variety of woven plaid models. Chucks made from leather uppers are also made occasionally, with the recent black and white high-top worn by Will\nSmith in the science fiction movie I Robot being the most prominent. These days most leather models are issued in black, brown or white and have a monochromatic look. One unusualline of leather chuck high-tops was the \"jewel,\" These high-tops came in black or white glove leather and actually had the ankle patches on the outside at each upper instead at the inside.The patches weren’t the usual glued on rubber patches either. They were three dimensional\nplastic patches with white plastic stars inside.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Chucks represent freedom from the mundane world</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>It there is such a thing as a \"philosophy of footwear,” you soon discover that wearing a pair of chucks represents Freedom: freedom from the world of work (although these days many people are fortunate enough to be able to wear them at work), freedom ofexpression (with many colors and styles to choose from to express your individuality), freedom from heavy boots and shoes that weigh\nyour feet down, and the freedom associated with summers and vacations. Wearing chucks can make a difference in your life. Many people have commented on what a pleasurable moment it was when they laced up a pair of chucks for the very first time. That special feeling is one of the reasons that people continue to wear chucks throught their lives.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Chucks are great for special activities</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>While most people think of their chucks as a funcasual or athletic shoe, some people like\nto wear chucks for special activities. Onedevoted wearer of black high-tops states that he prefers to drive his hig performance car wearing chucks. \"My chucksmold perfectly to the shape of the gas,brake, and clutch pedals. The rubber soleis iust thick and firm enough to prevent puncturing, yet thin enough to bend to the shape of whatever |\'m stepping on. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Chucks epitomize retro appeal</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>An interesting development in recent years has been the growth of the \"retro\" footwear market. Turned off by the\nincreasing high techno|ogy and expensive prices of high performance sneakers, people are choosing to wear classic models ofshoes made by Converse, adidas, and Puma instead. Retro shoes are popular becausethey have the look and sty|e that people love.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Chucks can go with just about any style of clothing</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Although chucks are no longer confined to the basketball court, they  still look great with basketball ierseys and shorts, and other athletic sportswear. The classic casual outfit for chucks is with a pair of ieans and a T-shirt or sweatshirt. This \"look\" has been officially recognized by LeviStrauss &amp; Co  and chucks are often shown in ads for Levis. ln warmer weather chucks look good with shorts, worn these days with or without socks. Chucks are practical for outdoor water activities, on rocks and in streams and rivers, because they are flexible, protect your\nfeet, and dry out quickly. Chucks look great with more dressy outfits for men, like sport shirts and Dockers or even with dress shirts, slacks, and ties. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Chucks have great variety</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>No other shoe comes in so many colors,patterns, and styles as the Chuck Taylor All Star. Chucks fall into two cat-\negories: the core models of classic high-top and low-cut black, red, navy blue, and white canvas, which are always available, and seasonal models,\nusually only made once, which come in bright and unusual colors and a variety of canvas patterns. Seasonal chucks come in high-top, low cut, knee high, and slip-on moclels.Seasonal chucks can be made with special fabric or even leather uppers. Seasonal chucks often have special features like multicolored canvas uppers, unique drawings or pictures,double tongues (in double colors), a wom or distressed look,or a Foldover (roll-down) design. It is now even possible to\ndesign your own special pair. Whatever it is that attracts you to chucks, you would have to agree that they make a statement. That is why you always notice someone wearing chucks in a crowd.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Article republished from </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://books.google.com/books?id=ko_a_Ij3TRMC&pg=PA79&dq=knee+high+converse&hl=en&ei=AGCcTNjXOYTfcaeW5dMJ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=book-thumbnail&resnum=1&ved=0CC0Q6wEwAA#v=onepage&q=knee%20high%20converse&f=false\">The Phenomenon of Converse Chuck Taylor All Stars By Hal Peterson</a>   </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(133,1,132,3,'Kids simply love orange color shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6175219305/\" title=\"orange converse shoes by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6167/6175219305_0d64e84779.jpg\" width=\"441\" height=\"500\" alt=\"orange converse shoes\"></a>\n</br></p>\n\n<p>Converse shoe are both suitable as men’s wear and women’s wear. But they look best on a toddler’s feet. The converse shoes for kids are made with such colors and designs that suit the innocence of the kids well. The orange converse shoes for kids are one such <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">variety of converse shoes</a>. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/O9Xx3jQ3Ilw\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/john-varvatos-converse-slip-on-shoes\">John varvatos converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">Kurt Cobain converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-ox-shoes-are-trendy-yet-variant-and-comfortable\">Converse Ox shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>This orange shoe is made of canvas on the upper part and is allied with a flexible rubber sole.The orange <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/knee-high-converse-shoes\">converse shoes</a> are high end and thus have superior extended ankle support. The shoes are <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/dr-seuss-converse-shoes-for-kids-and-adults\">fun to wear</a> and can be teamed with any outfit no matter whatever its color is.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You can choose from Converse All Star Chuck Taylor Gel Hi that comes in fluorescent orange color. The shoes are so attractive that with its solid liquid structure, the kids will not want to depart from their cherished converse shoes. The making is done in special regard to children’s taste and fancy. The stitching in the shoe is done with a contrast colored thread and the logo is textured in gel. The high top construction of the converse sneaker gives extra ankle protection. For extra comfort, textile lining is provided. The snug fitting of the shoe is provided by closure built of a lace. The top cap is made up of rubber and the midsole of vulcanized rubber. They all render greater durability.The shoes’ outsole has been prepared with hard wearing rubber. The hard hitting rubber is used to resist damage.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Another assorted variety of converse shoe in orange color, a favorite among children is the Chuk Taylor All Star Yarn Dye Plaid Ox.</b> The shoe is not a classy orange version but is designed with checked orange patterns. Thus, orange and white both the colors are found in the shoes. The shoe has been dyed with yard colors. The shoe features full lacing in the front and also has metallic eyelets. The converse shoe has a cushioned foot bed and has been lined with canvas that provides extra comfort. <b>A rubber toe box similar to signature Chuk Taylor shoes are also used for both the toe guard and toe box.</b> The sidewall is trimmed and is provided with side air vent at the medial side using vent holes. A heel patch of All Stars is also used. The outsole used is of vulcanized rubber.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>All the converse shoes excel in its superior durability support and comfort.</b> Supported by all the features is its warm refreshing looks. The shoes are best made for children of all sex and all age group. There are plenty of sizes to choose from as kid’s feet keeps on changing rapidly. The Converse shoes are a brand that is trustworthy and reliable for its superior quality. They excel in giving the best products. The shoes although are best suited for athlete’s feet and practice but is also acceptable by the commoners. <b>The shoe of kids from Converse carries the heritage of American sports during the times of the 20s.</b> They are easy to be maintained and can be bought online and shipped for free!            </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(134,1,133,2,'White knee high converse gives you a casual look',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6174790173/\" title=\"white converse by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6158/6174790173_3a37432df4.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"323\" alt=\"white converse\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>People generally wear it during summer.It is most suited for parties and informal events.White color symbolises purity,innocence and virginity.White shoes looks best with <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/black-knee-high-converse\">darker colors</a>.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/0BbHdFp_jfo\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/john-varvatos-converse-slip-on-shoes\">John varvatos converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">Kurt Cobain converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-ox-shoes-are-trendy-yet-variant-and-comfortable\">Converse Ox shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<h3>Do\'s with white converse</h3></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li> Its good for people of dark complexion  </li>\n<li> Wear white belt with white shoes </li>\n<li> Choose purse and jewllery that compliments white color </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Don\'t with white converse</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Never wear white shoe for a wedding and funeral </li>\n<li> Avoid white shoes if you have large leg </li>\n<li>Avoid going all white</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(135,1,134,2,'Low top sneakers from converse',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6175219977/\" title=\"converse low tops by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6174/6175219977_cd7f032e2c.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" alt=\"converse low tops\"></a>\n</br></p>\n\n<p>Converse low tops shoes make you feel relaxed and comfortable when they are worn.To give yourself a stylish look and make yourself feel comfortable you must have a <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/\">pair of converse shoes</a>. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/CP1LdF903rM\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/john-varvatos-converse-slip-on-shoes\">John varvatos converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">Kurt Cobain converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-ox-shoes-are-trendy-yet-variant-and-comfortable\">Converse Ox shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br>\nThe shoes sole are made of rubber. There are two types of converse shoes available in the market, namely the <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-jack-purcell-shoes\">low top shoes and the high top shoes</a>. Apart from players, people who love to travel in the hills can use these shoes since they are the most comfortable shoes you can look for. For a sports person converse is all time favorite. The grip and texture makes it <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/pink-knee-high-converse\">unique from others</a>.The importance of converse low top shoes is that they are comfortable, convenient, and help you stay away from foot pain or swells.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>They are designed in such a manner that even if you wear them for hours your feet do not feel pressurized. Some of the shoes are so well designed with colorful laces that you can wear them in informal parties also. Converse low top shoes are one of the best brands of sneakers that you must have in your collections. They can be purchased online and at discounts. Various offers are also available on converse.To grab one, you must visit their official website and look at the huge range of collections.Each pair of shoes is unique, eye catching, and exclusively designed.  Be aware while buying converse shoes when you shop online.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The latest technologies have made it possible to shop online. Converse shoes are easily available at online stores at an affordable price. <b>The official website of converse shoes offers you huge range of converse, along with minute information on their appearance and features.</b> The unique design and the soothing bright colors make them attractive and stylish. Some of the best shoes that you can purchase for your collection are:<b>A pro Star Converse shoe reveals the classic look.</b> The shoes are surrounded with elastic edge fold and are flexible to wear. The unique star sign gives it a classy look.<b>Converse Chuck Taylor All-star fun laces shoes</b> are designed with colorful satin laces, and rubber toe.<b>Converse Jack Purcell Low top shoes</b> are laced shoes with rubber toe cap and low heel. In front it has a silver tone eye lid.<b>Converse Chucks Lace less black low cut sneakers are perfect for daily usage.</b> Designed in a trendy manner giving complete comfort to your feet.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse shoes are popular among both men and women. The brightness and exclusive designs have made them popular in the market. With your denim or sports dress, jogging suit or leather jacket a pair of converse is a must. <b>For the youth of today converse has designed their shoes with vibrant colors like red, green, yellow, pink, blue and combinations.</b> When you go for an online purchase your shopping cart must have the range of some of the best designed converse shoes. Made out of rubber; special care is given to the ankle and toe areas making the converse the hottest brand. To relax your feet is what converse shoes aim at.              </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(136,1,135,2,'How to Wear Knee High Converse with Skinny Jeans',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6175318162/\" title=\"converse knee high skinny jeans by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6176/6175318162_073454586a.jpg\" width=\"333\" height=\"500\" alt=\"converse knee high skinny jeans\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse high-tops today are worn more as a fashion statement than a state of the art basketball shoe due to their excellent reputation with the haute couture crowd; websites like thechicfashionista.com declare that Converse high-tops are  a very good investment because they\'ll never go out of style.A new trend in women’s fashions is the pairing of the venerable Converse high-tops with skinny jeans; a look favored by everyone from <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-in-movies\">high-school teenage girls to Hollywood starlets</a>.               </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/YYUm4o1aDmY\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/john-varvatos-converse-slip-on-shoes\">John varvatos converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">Kurt Cobain converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-ox-shoes-are-trendy-yet-variant-and-comfortable\">Converse Ox shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br>\nThis should be done with care, however, as there is a specific way of wearing Converse high-tops with skinny jeans Since their introduction all the way back in 1917, Converse high-tops have remained in the public consciousness to this day. <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">Initially marketed as a basketball shoe, Converse</a> high-tops have never gone out of style and are still one of the Converse Corporation\'s best selling models. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ol>\n<li><p>The key to achieving the right look is to <b>lace your Converse high-tops correctly</b>. Start with the tip of the shoelace inserted through the top left hole, and continue in the same manner from top to bottom. Repeat this process with a second shoelace in the top right hole.</p></li>\n<li><p><b>Firmly holding each shoelace tip, pull both toward you.</b> This has the effect of creating a lateral shoelace band across the top holes of your high-tops. Pay extra attention to the lengths of the shoelaces; make sure both right and left ends are equal. Now hold the left shoelace at its tip and pull diagonally across the right-side hole second from the top. Insert the left end shoelace tip into this hole and continue the process all the way down.</p></li>\n<li><p><b>Pull the right end of the shoelace diagonally across the left hole that is second from the top.</b> Slip it into the hole and continue in the same way going down. Keep going until four holes on both sides are laced, making a grand total of eight holes laced and eight holes left unlaced.</p></li>\n<li><p><b>Put on a pair of socks, it\'s time to wear your shoes!</b> Start by putting on one shoe and pulling its laces towards you, tightening them. If you feel the shoe hugging against your foot you\'re on the right track. Move the shoe\'s tongue away from you.</p></li>\n<li><p><b>Now for the finishing touches! </b>Tie the shoelaces in a bow underneath the shoe\'s tongue - the bow\'s knot should be snug but not tight. Pull the tongue back towards you - depending on your preference the shoe\'s tongue may lie flat against your foot or sticks straight up. Some even like to have their shoe\'s tongue sit askew.</p></li>\n<li><p>Pull down the bottoms of your skinny jeans so they conceal your socks - you\'re all done! You are now in the cutting edge of fashion with <b>your Converse High-Tops and skinny jeans combo. </b> </p></li>\n</ol>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(137,1,136,2,'Classic Yellow Converse Chuck Taylors for Women and Kids',1,'<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6174791325/\" title=\"yellow converse by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6152/6174791325_b2bd84286a.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"312\" alt=\"yellow converse\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br>\nAlthough it is never good to spoil their kids, most parents will want to give their children the best, even when it comes to things like trendy shoes or clothes. The Kid\'s Yellow Converse Shoes are a particular favorite of trendy tykes, as are the ever-popular Chuck Taylor All Stars.Yellow <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/dr-seuss-converse-shoes-for-kids-and-adults\">Kid\'s Converse shoes</a> are something of enduring classic in kid\'s fashions. The appeal of these shoes weathers the test of time, remaining popular from generation to generation. There is a very high probability that the parents buying these yellow <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/orange-converse-shoes-for-kids-are-real-fun\">Converse sneakers for their kids</a> themselves had a pair when they were growing up. Not only are these shoes at the pinnacle of adolescent fashion sensibilities, they also have the added benefits of being extremely comfortable and durable.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/srMiZkVRBDM\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/john-varvatos-converse-slip-on-shoes\">John varvatos converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">Kurt Cobain converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-ox-shoes-are-trendy-yet-variant-and-comfortable\">Converse Ox shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Little kids are increasingly fashion conscious in today\'s media saturated world.Kids know what\'s in and what\'s out, and will always be aware of the <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-low-tops-shoes-to-relax-your-feet\">latest designer fashions</a> in clothes, sunglasses, or shoes.    Shoes are always important for kids, as they are something of a status symbol at school or on the playground - the feeling of disappointment when a child is rejected by the \'cool crowd\' at school because of their clothes or shoes is immediate and severe.      </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Kid\'s Yellow Converse Shoe give your children\'s feet a dash of color, making them stand out in a crowd - the primary bright yellow color of the shoe appeals to kid\'s youthful sensibilities. Any child wearing a pair of Kid\'s Yellow Converse Shoes is instantly hip - not to mention absolutely adorable.Features of the Kids Yellow Chuck Taylor All Stars include a lace up closure for a tight fit; the classic Converse Chuck Taylor design; enhance traction from the tick vulcanized rubber outsole; and a supremely durable canvas. If you want your little one to be a part of the \'in-crowd\' then you should definitely consider getting him or her the yellow Converse Chuck Taylor All-Stars. These bold yellow shoes will imbue you child with a sense of self-confidence and encourage him or her to stand out of the crowd.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h2>Yellow Converse Chuck Taylor All Stars for Women </h2>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>It is no secret that women are the primary drivers in the fashion world. Most women have an inherent knack for knowing what looks good and what is trendy. Women who are into looking good and dressing well always pay extra attention to their choice of clothes, shoes, bags and even car. <b>One way for women on the cutting edge of fashion to make a strong fashion statement is by wearing Women\'s Yellow Converse sneakers.</b>\nEver since they started making rubber soled basketball shoes nearly a century ago, Converse has diversified into women\'s sneakers. Today you can buy Converse shoes in different styles, colors and patterns - all of which have been designed specifically for women. <b>One such popular model is the Yellow Women\'s Converse Shoe.</b> While not the most subtle accessory, a bright yellow pair of Converse sneakers makes a bold statement. <b>They also match well with many different styles of shorts, skirts and jeans.</b></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Out of all the yellow Converse shoes designed for women, the classic Chuck Taylor All Stars remain the most popular.</b> These classic sneakers have been around for ages, and never go out of style. Their simplistic design and classic looks means that they go well with a variety of fashion styles. No matter what look you\'re aiming for, the ladies Yellow Chuck Taylors will complement and enhance it.Women wearing Yellow Converse shoes will definitely stand out of the crowd. <b>A bright yellow pair of classic Converse sneakers speaks volumes about your fashion sensibilities and advanced sense of style.</b> Why follow the crowd when you can stand out and be noticed?   </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(138,1,137,2,'Knee High Converse is Always in Fashion',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<img src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4102/4903738809_71eac17a6a.jpg\" width=\"343\" height=\"500\" alt=\"converse-knee-high-shoes-4\" /></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Knee high converse are Shoes that cover upto your knee or the shoe that stops where your knee begins.It was launched in 1970\'s.It was launched by american shoe company converse.It is also known as <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/reasons-to-wear-converse-shoes\">knee hi chucks</a>.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><object width=\"640\" height=\"510\"><param name=\"movie\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/ZPeS-hndAIE?fs=1&hl=en_US&rel=0\"></param><param name=\"allowFullScreen\" value=\"true\"></param><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\"></param><embed src=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/ZPeS-hndAIE?fs=1&hl=en_US&rel=0\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"640\" height=\"510\"></embed></object></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/john-varvatos-converse-slip-on-shoes\">John varvatos converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">Kurt Cobain converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-ox-shoes-are-trendy-yet-variant-and-comfortable\">Converse Ox shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>It helps you to make style statements.It is trendy and classy.It is one of evergreen fashion trends and is always in demand.It gives you <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/black-knee-high-converse\">super sexy look</a>.If you are wearing high converse knee boots,people will notice and you will get lots of compliments.Your Calves will appear <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/knee-high-converse-shoes\">slimmer in these boots</a>.Any marks on your legs will be covered.It keeps your feet warm in summer.It gives you casual look with jeans and sexy look with skirts. </p>\n\n<p><br> </p>\n\n<h2> What is common between a teenager, supermodel, celebrity and working women? </h2> \n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>They all have atleast one pair of converse hi knee in their wardrobe.Because You can wear your pair on any occasion.It matches with all kind of outfits.It is avaliable in pointed, round or square toes.It comes in wide range of colors (red,black,white,chocolate,brown,etc).It is generally available in 6.5 B to 10 B sizes.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Converse types</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>see through</li>\n<li>lace up</li>\n<li>zip up</li>\n<li>Buckled</li>\n<li>Pull on</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Tips on wearing high knee chuck taylors </h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>If you are wearing tight converse shoe on jeans ,make sure that your jeans is skinny.</li>\n<li>In summer you can wear it without stockings but Avoid mini skirts when you are barelegged.</li>\n<li>If it is loose,wear it with thick stockings.</li>\n<li>Make sure that your ankles are clean if you are going Barelegged </li>\n<li>Always check how the knee high boot fits on your calves before buying.</li>\n<li>Walk around in your house with new pair for one week.It will help your boot to adjust to your feet.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>All the girls must have at least one pair of converse high knee shoes in their wardrobe.<b>High Knee converse is boon for plus size women.Its wide calf option fits women of any size as circumference at the top is more.</b>It is available in both pointed and round toes.You should choose its material based on on your budget and need.Leather is water proof but costly.Women who are looking for cheaper options can go with fake leather.Just keep in mind that it is not water proof.Cloth knee high is cheap but worns out easily and needs regular washing.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Just keep in mind that <b>knee high converse</b> looks good on any cloth and women.You can wear it for your company presentation,morning walk or in your school.It is also top choice for atheletes.<b>Tall women can go for flat footed option.</b>Short women can wear them with heels to add to their height.\nIt is stylish and comfortable.It keeps your feet warm and gives you sexy look and feel.Irrespective of fashion changes,knee high converse is always in demand.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Types of converse hi knee boots :</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li> Motorcycle boots </li>\n<li> Riding boots </li>\n<li> Kinky boots </li>\n</ul>                       \n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(139,1,138,2,'knee high converse videos',1,'<h3>Learn how to make knee high converse </h3>\n\n<p></br>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><object width=\"480\" height=\"385\"><param name=\"movie\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/MVC1NfTWjVs?fs=1&hl=en_GB\"></param><param name=\"allowFullScreen\" value=\"true\"></param><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\"></param><embed src=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/MVC1NfTWjVs?fs=1&hl=en_GB\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"480\" height=\"385\"></embed></object></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Knee high vs over the knee</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><object width=\"480\" height=\"385\"><param name=\"movie\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/MkDpnjZZcu4?fs=1&hl=en_GB\"></param><param name=\"allowFullScreen\" value=\"true\"></param><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\"></param><embed src=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/MkDpnjZZcu4?fs=1&hl=en_GB\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"480\" height=\"385\"></embed></object></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n  <h3>How to wear knee high boots</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><object width=\"480\" height=\"385\"><param name=\"movie\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/9m7uuU69-yg?fs=1&hl=en_GB\"></param><param name=\"allowFullScreen\" value=\"true\"></param><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\"></param><embed src=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/9m7uuU69-yg?fs=1&hl=en_GB\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"480\" height=\"385\"></embed></object></p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(140,1,139,2,'How to create converse shoes for kids',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6174790317/\" title=\"converse-kids by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6155/6174790317_5e052b1fc2.jpg\" width=\"334\" height=\"500\" alt=\"converse-kids\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You can design shoes for your kids on the converse website easily.Please see the bottom of page for exact link to start the design of your <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/orange-converse-shoes-for-kids-are-real-fun\">kid\'s converse shoe</a>.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Steps to create converse shoe for your kid</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>You will see four dropdown menus (collection,gender,material style) ,once you land on converse design link.</li>\n<li>Please choose \"kids\" under \"gender\".</li>\n<li>You will see approximately 7 shoes.Ak your kid what he likes the most.Please click on the <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/pink-knee-high-converse\">shoe your kid likes the most</a>.</li>\n<li>Now you will see the large image of the shoe.Plese click on it to start.</li>\n<li>First thing is to select the size.It will be on right hand side.Click on \"size\" and choose one of USA or UK sizes.After that select the size of your kid.It is better to have a shoe of 1/2 size down.</li>\n<li>On the top one bar will show the progress of your design.For example Click on \"outside body\".You will see two options on left hand side : color and print.First choose the color and after that a matching print for that color.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>You can repeat the above process for :</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>tongue</li>\n<li>lace</li>\n<li>toe cap</li>\n<li>toe bumper</li>\n<li>medial eyelet</li>\n<li>outside body</li>\n<li>Racing stripe</li>\n<li>Lining</li>\n<li>stich</li>\n<li>rubber sidewall</li>\n<li>Heel stripe</li>\n<li>inside body</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Once you are satisfied with your design,please click on save button.</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Notes:</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Rotate the shoe and make sure that it is looking perfect from all the angles.</li>\n<li>Zoom on the shoe to make sure you are creating a perfect converse for your kid.</li>\n<li>Make sure that your kid is sitting with you during the whole process.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Exact link</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>http://www.converse.com/#/products/shoes/converseOne/scratch/all</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(141,1,140,2,'Ox Shoes are really nice',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6175746944/\" title=\"converse ox by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6151/6175746944_a1a3e3b285.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"354\" alt=\"converse ox\"></a>\n</br></p>\n\n<p>Ox shoes are the trends of the season.So when you want to shop for ox shoes rely on reputable brands that use the finest material, sole or canvas to prepare ox shoes. There are <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-jack-purcell-shoes\">multiple varieties of converse</a> ox shoes to select from.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/wON-cXri5cI\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/john-varvatos-converse-slip-on-shoes\">John varvatos converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">Kurt Cobain converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-ox-shoes-are-trendy-yet-variant-and-comfortable\">Converse Ox shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You can shop for Converse Ox shoes with star print.As the name suggests, the shoes are laden with colorful stars. <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">Chuck Taylor</a>, a great basket ball player is the inspiration behind such ox shoes. The shoe can also be renamed as Chux. Insole of the <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/white-knee-high-converse\">sneaker is comfortable enough</a> for a basket player to practice matches. But with its glamorous patterns it easily became a craze as casual footwear. The Canvas used in the shoe is durable and easy to maintain. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The toe box is made of carbon and it renders protection to upper foot.The outsole of the shoe is made up of vulcanized rubber. The heel and the forefront have diamond shaped lungs, while the toe region is extricated with grooves and lungs in horizontal order. The periphery however, has slanting grooves. The shoe is comfortable to wear because of its canvas tongue that is much longer than normal sneakers. The shoe has a foam insole and a foot bed that is padded. The reinforced guard protects the shoe’s forefoot. All these qualities make it a comfortable yet trendy footgear.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>For a daring yet girly look one can try Converse Ox shoes with a floral print.</b> This shoe is designed in the same pattern as the previous printed patter converse ox shoe. The creation of the midsole, outsole, upper canvas all is similar in all the chief canvas ox shoes. The converse ox shoes comes in such variety that you will fail to make an easy choice as every shoe is remarkable. <b>You can have a look of the Converse white shoes that are designed as a unisex variety.</b> The shoe has a rugged look and the latter side has a patch work of star appliqué. The high ankle design provides extra support to the foot extending to the anklet. Converse specialty ox shoes have a unique variety. They come in glamorous colors like rusty orange or leafy green.  <b>The Converse Green Ox shoe has an arty design.</b> The canvas has intricate check patterns and is a classic version of sneaker shoes.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>The ox shoes are generally an emerging trend. It is mostly a specialty among girls to wear it as a style statement. </b>Sport shoes are prepared for providing comfort at times of sport practice. The converse ox shoes however should be taken good care of. To take care of them first take one tablespoon each of baking soda, vinegar and hot water. Now rub the paste obtained in your converse shoes before treating them to lukewarm water for washing. <b>Converse ox shoes are available in different sizes and you can choose the one that fits you perfectly.</b> Free shipping of the shoes is also available. Cash on delivery option can also be availed in case the buyer does not have a credit or debit card or is hesitant about making transaction online.           </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(142,1,141,3,'A man always looks good in CVO sneakers',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* knee high converse shoes-rect */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2433556184\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/67732675@N06/6175746372/\" title=\"converse cvo by mycollectionofsho, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6179/6175746372_da93d30c06.jpg\" width=\"354\" height=\"500\" alt=\"converse cvo\"></a>\n</br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>A CVO shoe from Converse has minimal styling. They bring back the basic or <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/classic-yellow-converse-chuck-taylors-for-women-and-kids\">conventional converse sneakers</a> devoid of any intricacy or specification, kept much simple and represent contemporary trends. The upper part of the converse shoes is made up of suede. The tongue and collar of the shoe also do not have heavily padded soles. <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/three-popular-lacing-styles-for-converse-shoes\">Easy lacing can be provided to these shoes</a> using metal eyelets. The outsole of the shoe is vulcanized where rubber is converted using sulphur in to more durable material. </p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/F0Mw8DRoBko\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/john-varvatos-converse-slip-on-shoes\">John varvatos converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/kurt-cobain-converse-shoes\">Kurt Cobain converse</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/converse-ox-shoes-are-trendy-yet-variant-and-comfortable\">Converse Ox shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The skateboard CVO shoes from converse have insole that are of higher density than <a href=\"http://www.kneehighconverse.info/white-knee-high-converse\">other converse shoes</a>.Such shoes add superior protection and comfort to an athlete’s foot. The shoes are of slightly narrow width and have normal length. The fitting of the shoes are snug fitting in type and they loosen with repeated wear.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The converse Ka-One shoes comes both in black and white variety. But in both the types both the colors are used in distinct proportion, to give it a classy finish. The shoe is designed after an inspiration from classic silhouette from Converse.  Kelly Anderson’s signature sneakers were also a theme for these shoes. The toecap and the Ollie area have been stitched heavily and are constructed as a cup sole. There are laces sported in a wavy pattern. A buyer can find the logo of the converse in leather in one side and the tongue of the shoe with a tag. <b>The converse logo is printed also at the heel of the converse CVO shoe.</b></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>There is another tempting converse CVO shoe that has known as Shitake or Cinnabar.</b> The shoe has a fine partition of rusty red color and dusky wooden brown color with the edges brown and upper part red. The look is so attractive that it will catch attention at a single glance. The tongue and the collar of the shoe however, are thin. With its outsole vulcanized, it is not only durable but also helps to land easily and smoothly on ground after a jump. The mix and match canvas or red and brown colors are made using leather. Thus, it is leather borne CVO shoe from canvas. <b>Another similar type of canvas shoe yet with a varying color texture is Cloisonné converse CVO shoes.</b> Blue and black are the colors generally used in this shoe in the similar way as the earlier Cinnabar shoes. A CVO shoe with a blue-white variety can also be expected. The upper part of the shoe is prepared from three materials- suede, leather and ordinary canvas. To make the collar of the cloisonné shoe leather is used. <b>The support of the Ollie is outstanding in this CVO variety. </b>The Ollie area has been stitched twice but the toecap is left without stitches. The converse logo and tag are present both at the rear heel and tongue. The shoe is super durable and indeed very comfortable.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>All the converse CVO shoes are specially designed for men.</b> They are all unique in one feature or another. The shoes with its basic styling yet comfy build and wear is creating a craze as a hot casual foot wear.            </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(143,1,142,1,'Some controversial launches of converse',1,'<p><b>2010: Converse INC launched \"Memory of Hnedrix\" shoes</b> that depicted guitar legend Jimi Hendrix as Hindu God.Its launch offended Hindus all over the world.One hindu leader Beth Kulkarni wrote the complaint letter to converse customer service and soon these shoes were taken off from the converse website.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>2003 :Converse shoe launched the Loaded Weapon shoes in 2003.</b>According to them it was the next generation of their Weapon shoes (launched in 1981) loaded with latest cushion systems and hence the name : \"Loaded weapons\".The launch was met with controversy as people thought it was a bad message for kids and many agreed that it was a bad tactic to use violence to increase the sales.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>1995 : Converse recalled its Raw Energy basketball shoes</b> after receiving complaints from atheletes who reported leakage of fluids from the soles.RAW Shoes had two silver fluid windows in the sole for extra cushioning.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>1993 : Converse changed the name of its <b>Run N Gun shoes to Run N Slam</b> after it received complaints from many social organisations which said the name will increase the violence among youth.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>1992 : Magic Johnson ended his 12 year old association with converse.</b>Johnson said,\"Converse is still living in the 60\'s and 70\'s.They have not arrived in the 80\'s and 90\'s where advertising and marketing are the keys.Magic wanted to leave the converse in 1987 only but a lawsuit filed by Converse prevented his departure.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Use of dead celebrities</b> like kurt cobain (who died from a gunshot wound to the head in 1994),journalist Hunter S Thompson and Joy Division singer Ian Curtis(both commited suicide),Sex Pistols bassist Sid Vicious(died of a heroin overdose) to promote the converse brands is under severe criticism.Crtics said,\"it is impossible to know which shoe brand they actually want their fans to buy and wear as they are dead\".</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(144,1,143,1,'A to Z of converse hi top shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5925647134/\" title=\"converse-hi-top by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6027/5925647134_837ca415cc.jpg\" width=\"470\" height=\"417\" alt=\"converse-hi-top\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Pink hi-top</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse changed its status from seasonal to core model Due to its pupularity among women.Black piping adds to the beauty.<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/rainbow-converse-shoes\">Some of the popular variations are  </a> :</p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/PnyAFfY3n18\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n\n<p></br>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li> Neon pink </li>\n<li> Medium pink </li>\n<li> Peach </li>\n<li> Light pink </li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Red hi-top</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The sexiest among <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info\">all the hi-top models  </a>.Red hi-top is very popular among women and comes with black piping (just as pink hi-tops).It looks different and stylish.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Optical white hi-top</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>It was first used by the  <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">american basketball team in 1936 olympics  </a>.</p>\n\n<p>It was also used for millitary training during the second world war.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Piping is available in red and blue colors</li>\n<li>Ankle patchs were availale in blue,white and red colors.</li>\n<li>White Canvas</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Navy blue white top</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>It was launched in 1960\'s.It looks good on all types of clothing.It comes with blue piping and toe-caps.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Monochrome black hi-top</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>It is one of the oldest selling models of con