 href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Green Lantern Converse shoe</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Green Lantern is a superhero comics series published by dc comics.He has a ring and lantern that him the superpowers.It is also a superhit movie of 2011 starring Ryan Reynolds as Green Lantern.You can <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> wear these shoes with skinny jeans  </a> (even straight ones look good) and t-shirts.You can buy this shoe by clicking at below link :</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.journeys.com/product.aspx?id=189961\">Buy converse green lantern shoes at Journeys</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Superman Converse shoe</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Superman is the most recognised comics character.It has appeared in number of tv shows and movies.He is man of steel and protects earth.Converse is selling its shoes with the print of superman on canvas.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You can buy superman converse shoes at below places :</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.journeys.com/product.aspx?id=170250\">Buy superman converse at Journeys</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Journeys does not have shoes with S shied of superman.Fortunately i found a place where the guys sale hand painted superman converse shoes.Please check below </p>\n\n<p>link :</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://punkyourchucks.com/supermanmain.html\">Custom superman converse with S shield</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Batman Converse shoes</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Batman is only superhero with no superpowers.He relies on his wits,martial arts and technological weapons to fight.This makes him more lovable and realistic than other superheroes.He has appeared in a number of comics,tv serials and movies.You can buy batman shoes at discount from yebhi.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.yebhi.com/SH~0~0~1~-1~true~Batman%20Shoes~-1~op~/\">Buy batman converse shoes from yebhi</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Joker converse shoes</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Batman fights many villains like poison ivy,riddler,penguin,two face,etc but one villain that even batman is afraid of is \"Joker\".This character is popularied by heath ledger in the movie Dark Knight.It is not wrong to say that his popularity rivals that of our superheroes.You can buy Joker shoes from Journeys.Aavailable colors are Black,white and gray.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.journeys.com/product.aspx?id=176695\">Buy joker shoes from Journeys</a>      </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(150,1,149,1,'Buy cool double upper shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5936713994/\" title=\"Converse-All-Star-Double-Upper by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6142/5936713994_4841f661d7.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"356\" alt=\"Converse-All-Star-Double-Upper\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse shoes were always criticized by people because of lack of colors in their designs.The converse double upper collection is <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/yellow-converse-high-tops-for-kids\">launched in great number of color combinations   </a> to address this issue and it succeeds.It is available in every color that you can think of.It has an additional flap and two pair of eyelets for doble laces (brown and white).It has extra air holes for <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/what-to-wear-with-yellow-converse\">keeping the inside cool during summer  </a>.</p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/j2bPaCCdgg0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You will fall in love with these shoes at first sight.It <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/what-to-wear-with-gray-converse-high-tops\"> looks cool and sylist </a> due to rich color combos.Its great buy for students because of its durability and color choices.This is an example of changing design to keep it updated with time while retaining the core of <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/what-to-wear-with-green-converse-high-tops\">converse classic shoes  </a>.All star logo is on inner tongue.It is covered by outer tongue.</p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"349\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/aROOaTNvucg\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br></p>\n\n<h3>Lacing tips for double upper shoes</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>Some people wear it without laces and believe me that it looks cool</li>\n\n<li>Lace only the inner eyelets.This is best for lazy guys like me.</li>\n\n<li>Lace the inner layer using ladder stich and use normal lacing on outer layer.This is the best solution if you are not a pro at lacing.</li>\n\n<li>Some people are reading lacing tips at this site : http://www.fieggen.com/shoelace/lacingmethods.htm .It is very good site to learn lacing for your shoes.</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You can design your own double upper shoes at converse website.Below i have listed the most popular shoes waiting to be designed as per your taste :</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>All star double upper</li>\n\n<li>All star double tongue neon</li>\n\n<li>All star layer up</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3> Double upper is available in below colors </h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n\n<li>Blue</li>\n\n<li>Green</li>\n\n<li>Yellow and gold</li>\n\n<li>Purple and pink</li>\n\n<li>white and silver</li>\n\n<li>black and gray</li>\n\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><h4>Dresses to wear with Double upper </h3></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>Wear with Tux on Prom Night.</li>\n\n<li>Girls can try it with light brown denim shorts.</li>\n\n<li>It Adds flare to your skinny jeans.Open the flap to cover jeans.</li>\n\n<li>Small girls can wear it with polka skirt</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(151,1,150,1,'Wear converse for your next golf match',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5980629681/\" title=\"converse-golf-shoes by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6015/5980629681_4b29e63f2f.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"328\" alt=\"converse-golf-shoes\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>If you want to play golf like top pros (tiger woods) than you need to buy golf <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/thigh-high-converse-sneakers\">shoes from converse  </a>.These shoes fit well and help your game.Just buy them and see it yourself.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/vBYazGFBXOc\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>In earlier times,golf shoes were not designed specifically.Not now.These days converse designs its golf shoes keeping the sports in mind and use the <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">technology of athletic shoes  </a>.These shoes are light,comfortable,flexible and will feel like the part of feet.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Tips while buying golf shoes</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Meaure both the width and length of your feet while ordering online.</li>\n<li>Consult a doctor if you feel pain while playing the golf.</li>\n<li>Keep in mind that shoes are an essential gear of your game.So always choose them with care.</li>\n<li>Make sure that you have plenty of space to move your feet comfortably.One easy way to check is to move the toe area once inside the shoe.</li>\n<li>Proper lacing keeps every area of your feet at the proper place and help in releasing the pressure efficiently.</li>\n<li>Make sure that you are comfortable with the height of the heel.</li>\n<li>Around 10 mm space must be available between your longest toe and shoe.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Advantages of converse golf shoes</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>A widw heel base to give you better support and stability.</li>\n<li>No one creates better shock absorbing soles than converse.It has plenty of cushion to absorb any kind of shock.</li>\n<li>You have plenty of heel height options to choose from.</li>\n<li>Good amount of thumb space clearence to avoid any kind of nail problems.</li>\n<li>Extra air holes for ability to breathe and to keep the temprature low inside the shoe.</li>\n<li>Small twisting motion for the better balance.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Make sure that you try the shoe before buying it and it should meet all the requirements stated above.Never buy a tight shoe or high heels as it can lead to blisters and less stability.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(152,1,151,1,'Converse Boots are best for hiking',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5981188140/\" title=\"converse-hiking-boots by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6125/5981188140_3d3c8fb20e.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" alt=\"converse-hiking-boots\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse manufactures its hiking boots with less seams to make it water resistant.There is plenty of room at toe area for movement.Heels are designed <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">keeping biomechanics in mind  </a> to provide support to your ankles.It has extra air holes for better air flow during the summer. <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/buy-converse-shoes-part-one\">Always buy converse  </a> for your hiking as it is cheap,durable and comfortable.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/3CMqhQDGd3k\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Features of converse hiking boots</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>A perfect shock absorbing sole made od softer materials to protect your feet against the Jarring.</li>\n\n<li>Large toe area is provided for <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-stretch-converse-shoes\"> free movement of feet inside the shoes </a> and it help counter the blister problems.</li>\n\n<li>Heels are desiged keeping human body in mind.It allows for a very small amount of twisting motion.</li>\n\n<li>Heel base is broad to increase the contact area between your feet and ground and in turn increases your stability.</li>\n\n<li>Boots bend near the toe area (instead of arch).</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Because of the above features,<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-lace-up-boots-for-girls\"> converse boots </a> provide better support to your body during the hiking time.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Tips on buying hiking boots</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>You must lace your shoes perfectly(either too tight nor too loose).This will keep feet in proper lace and reduce the pressure on toe areas.</li>\n\n<li>Always look for low heel as it reduces the load placed on forefoot and keep your centre of gravity at right place.</li>\n\n<li>Try your hiking boots with socks that you will wear on hiking.Make sure that your feel comfortable once inside the shoe.</li>\n\n<li>The best time to try shoes is in afternoon(your feet is slightly larger at that time).</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse manufacturers its hiking boots in different designs and colors.It is available in all price ranges.Just go to any store and buy converse hiking boots that is perfect fit and suits your budget.      </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(153,1,152,1,'Converse Knee High Boots For Girls',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5925135127/\" title=\"converse-shoes-2 by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6126/5925135127_7d194a09bc.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" alt=\"converse-shoes-2\"></a>\n</br></p>\n\n<p>Converse knee high boots for girls is a product line dedicated to young adults and teens who love to wear <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/buy-superman-batman-green-lantern-and-joker-converse-shoes\"> sporty and chic footwear </a>, and don’t like to get caught up in the web of old, bland designs and patterns of shoes. These shoes are loved by those girls who want to break shackles and stop playing the plain Jane, but want to feel free and wear what they like, and sometimes even design what they wear. <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/knee-high-converse-for-girls\"> Converse knee high boots </a> is manufactured under all models, particularly Chuck Taylor and All Star. </p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/pvMq2RrGObk\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The best selling boots for girls are All Star Shower Boot and All Star outsider. They are amazingly attractive models and apt for parties and outdoor functions. They are very comfortable inside and the lining is very soft, which cushions your feet and doesn’t strain you while walking. Converse knee high boots for girls come in various forms, such as, <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/knee-high-converse-for-kids\">with and without laces, with buckles, zipped, and straps  </a>. Some of the shoe types have laces in front and zipper from the side giving them the contemporary look. They come in retro as well as modern styles and designs. Mostly they have canvas material with rubber soles, but some of them are in suede or vinyl, adding diversity to their collection. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Be it the Chucks or the All Star, Converse has got a huge collection of knee high footwear that will make you look gorgeous, whether you wear it on bare legs, which will let you flaunt your sexy legs with a splash of style and appeal, or whether you wear it on jeans that will give you a smart look. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The bottom line is that if you want to break the stereotype, when it comes to shoes, you should certainly have at least a pair of Converse knee high boots for girls to adorn your wardrobe with something exquisite and contrast.     </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse is one of the biggest names in shoe industry, manufacturing high quality footwear since 1910. It has always been a trendsetter, having a wide variety of shoes for kids, men and women.  Because of its dynamic nature and perpetual innovative methods, Converse has become a very well known name in many parts of the world. The sporty shoes are eye-catching and you will be spoilt for choice by going through their collection. Special edition collections like The Ramones, Metallica, Grateful Dead, Nirvana, DC Comics and Ozzy Osbourne are also available for you to get hold of, before someone else does.    </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(154,1,153,1,'Converse Knee High Sneakers For Kids',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5925492266/\" title=\"knee-high-converse by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6013/5925492266_4fee76d645.jpg\" width=\"493\" height=\"500\" alt=\"knee-high-converse\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse knee high sneakers for kids is a product line entirely dedicated to those kids who don’t like to go with the flow, but like to <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">create their own fashion statement  </a>\n and  set their own standards.</p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/J4vjLJjt9ec\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Call it offbeat or call it uncanny, but the truth is that whenever the new model of Converse comes out, it takes the market by a storm and sets new benchmarks and reaches new heights. <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-knee-high-socks\">Converse knee high  </a> sneakers for kids come in a wide variety of designs, patterns, colors and styles.  The conventional colors include <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/a-to-z-of-converse-hi-top-shoes\"> black top  </a> with white rubber soles, but they have come up with so many eye-catching and bright colors that you will certainly be spoilt for choice when deciding to buy the one that will suit you best.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The designs are also admirable and appealing.  Apart from their traditional lace up design, they have sneakers with buckles, zipped and Velcro straps. Some of the shoes have the combination of straps and lace, or buckles and straps, giving the sneakers a fashionable look. One of the strong points of Converse is that in the product line of Converse knee high sneakers for kids, the shoes can be designed themselves by the kids; all they have to do is to order the design they want to be made on the shoes and just wait while the customized sneakers get ready. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Other advantage of Converse sneakers is that you can fold the sneaker at the knee if you want to, and their inner lining is designed in such a visually appealing manner, so that when you fold the top of the shoes from knee down, it looks nice and cool. Converse high top All Star Kids is an example of trendy sports sneakers that can be worn by kids who love sports and regularly go outdoors for fun activities. Converse knee high sneakers for kids are an amazing option if you want your kids to look stylish and cool.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse is one of the best shoe manufacturing companies that have been in shoe manufacturing business from 1910. Currently, it is a subsidiary of Nike, and has brought various style and designs into the market by its innovative methods and plans. It is the market leader in the production and sales of canvas shoes with rubber soles, the pattern and design now imitated by other leading shoe manufacturers. Apart from canvas, Converse has got a huge variety in other shoes like suede, vinyl and hemp.         </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(155,1,154,1,'Converse Knee High Socks',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5925085833/\" title=\"converse-knee-high-socks by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6140/5925085833_41106fcf3b.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" alt=\"converse-knee-high-socks\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>They sure are growing in their popularity; women love them particularly teenage girls and young women. Men love them because <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/thigh-high-converse-sneakers\"> women look sexy in them </a> and hot too and the socks give them a flirty vibe, hence the <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-double-upper-shoe\">raging trend these days  </a>.</p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/rCPMLwz7T3E\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse knee-high socks are in vogue these days due to stylish and trendy look. The female folk love them particularly teenage girls and young women.  <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/knee-high-converse-shoes\">Converse Knee High  </a> socks present themselves in a wide variety of shapes and sizes with some of the finest patterns you can ever imagine. These patterns are purely meant to give your legs something to bargain on. They come in every color combination possible and really make your legs look like dancing on the streets while you walk. One can also put a <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/what-to-wear-with-silver-converse-high-tops\">matching shoe   </a> which will make it completely fantastic.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>There is a “tall sports sock” which is fast catching up the trend these days. They look awesome on skirts, shorts or any outfit which gets you legs exposed up to knee level. There are “ruffle tops” which gives a lace like appearance. By having them on your legs, you are not only making them look beautiful and sexy but you are changing the whole perception of how people were taking them.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>These Converse Knee high socks, in fact, enhance your leg shape by bringing out those really hot and also makes your outfit look really good. There is a Converse stirrup socks which is also a knee length sock which acts as a warmer without being so thick. It comes with a wide strap that makes your foot look nice. Use them with your favorite sandals to make sure that your legs look slimmer and nicer.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Young women like them, because they can pair them up with any kind of shoes and dresses and enhance their personality by putting on these socks. These women love to wear them for parties where they will be admired by one and all for their beautiful looking legs. When women put them on they generally stay on means that they become irresistibly irresistible. These socks can be used also as stockings and at the same time make your legs look slim and trim with a lot of beauty and sex appeal to them. The fabric of these socks is smooth and does not cause any rashes or itching.        </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(156,1,155,1,'Converse Lace Up Boots For Girls',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5925085833/\" title=\"converse-knee-high-socks by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6140/5925085833_41106fcf3b.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" alt=\"converse-knee-high-socks\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The new brand of laced shoes for girls from converse has a style of their own. They have come into the market with impunity and are here to stay for a long time.<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-tennis-shoes\">These shoes come up with different styles  </a> and different sizes to accommodate every customer. They have good color combinations that make them very attractive. They have <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-lace-converse-high-tops\"> different lace styles </a> too, which adds to their beauty and uniqueness. The material used in them is always good and meant to make your feet comfortable in them.</p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/LuoRzj92eEM\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse is known for its style and durability which it has never compromised till date. Converse offers shoes for children men and women. Their <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">designers work </a> day in and day out, doing research all the time and always come up with the styles that are meant to stay. Their special girls segment which covers all the styles and designs of different laced boots girls usually wear. These boots are perfectly made to fit into any size of feet. These laced boots are selling like hot chocolates because of their <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-padded-collar\">never before seen colors and style  </a>. The colored laces add to their beauty and make them bit different.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The option and the range in the colors of these boots are so huge that girls can choose a particular color that will suit their outfits. They can even buy the same color socks to make things bit interesting. These shoes are specially designed so that you can wear them on anything like skirts jeans or shorts. They don’t strain your feet or legs. The canvas they use in these shoes is special and very durable and at the same time it is very soft so that even if you wear them on naked feet there won’t be any kind of rashes on your skin.  These Converse lace up boots are very famous with girls of all ages. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Back in the year 1908 a man named Marquis M. opened Converse Rubber Shoe Company in Maldon, Massachusetts. It was also known by the name Boston Rubber Shoe Company. The company has been in the shoe making business since the early part of the twentieth century.  It was primarily into providing rubber soled footwear generally for winter seasons. It is in 1915 that the converse went into manufacturing tennis shoes. After that in 1917 converse introduced All Star basketball shoes into the market.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(157,1,156,1,'converse padded collar shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5936589374/\" title=\"converse-padded-collar by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6018/5936589374_756efeb8cc.jpg\" width=\"283\" height=\"500\" alt=\"converse-padded-collar\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>It was released in 2009 as a part of \"Always On \" <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/best-of-chuck-commercials\">Campaign by converse  </a>.A better outsole and padded collar seperates it from the classic shoes.</p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/n5nI25-oX9c\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Its the most comfortable and stylish shoes from the converse.It looks much better than <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info\"> classic converse </a> as Paaded collar adds style and extra support to your foot.Its perfect for every occasion.<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-golf-shoes\"> You can even play golf </a> and tennis in these shoes.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>I was able to find only one matching shoe on converse website:  Men\'s All Star Dual Collar.It is available in black and charcoal colrs and is priced at 39 USD.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>If you are looking for more options ,you can order it from footlocker website.It seems that it was made exculusively for footlocker.Footlocker has a nice collection of these shoes in various sizes,colors and materials for both men and women.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>These shoes are available in below colors :</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>ATHLETIC NAVY</li>\n<li>BLACK</li>\n<li>CHARCOAL</li>\n<li>CHOCOLATE</li>\n<li>DENIM STUDS</li>\n<li>DENIM TECHNO FLORAL</li>\n<li>GREY</li>\n<li>PHAETON GREY</li>\n<li>WHITE DENIM</li>\n<li>WHITE STUDS</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The Racing stripe is of black color and it adds to the beauty of white Rubber sidewall.White laces looks pretty nice on black outside body.It is not wrong to say that this shoe has killer looks and a perfect addition to your collection of shoes.In my view it is much better than their classic collection and a smart buy.The converse logo shines around the heel area and it gives you the feeling of a proud converse owner.Its a much needed improvement on classic shoes made by converse.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Girls should buy a pair of chocolate brown or denim studs and wear it with red skirt while going to parties.Boys can go for leather for their bike trips.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>So go and buy a pair of these shoes to add style to your clothes and comfort to your feets.In short,The best shoes ever made by any shoe company.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(158,1,157,1,'Converse promo code 2011',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p>You can save money on the purchase of converse shoes by using these carefully collected Promo codes for <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info\"> converse shoes </a>.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"610\" height=\"540\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/yJasNo0An28\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>At Yebhi, you will get 20 to 30 percent discount on converse shoes.Please check the below link for more details :</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.yebhi.com/SH~0~0~1~-1~true~Converse~-1~op~/\">Converse sale on Yebhi</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>At footlocker you will get 20 percent discount if you purchase items worth more than 75 dollars.The promo code is IPFLV726.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You can check the sale section of converse shoes at footlockers for better bargains.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.footlocker.com/se