></p>\n\n<p>Another good place to try is Work Boots USA</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://workbootsusa.ecomm-search.com/search?catalog=yhst-48446621305942&x=0&y=0&query=converse+shoes\">Converse sale at work boot usa</a></p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(159,1,158,1,'converse shoes in movies',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5925164299/\" title=\"converse-i-robot by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6149/5925164299_76752367c6.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"285\" alt=\"converse-i-robot\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>A list of 35 hit movies in which at least one major character wears <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info\"> the converse shoe </a>.The list includes movies of big box office stars like daniel craig,arnold schwarzenegger,pierce brosnan,johny depp,will smith,bruce willis,tom cruise,nicolas cage,etc.</p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/3HpIZrOH4zc\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>Amelie</li>\n<li>American pie</li>\n<li>Anaconda</li>\n<li>Charlie and the Chocolate Factory</li>\n<li>Commando</li>\n<li>The girl next door</li>\n<li>Gran torino</li>\n<li>Grease</li>\n<li>Halloween 4</li>\n<li>Harry Potter and the Half Blood Prince</li>\n<li>Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix</li>\n<li>Honey i shrunk the kids</li>\n<li>Juno</li>\n<li>The money pit</li>\n<li>Percy Jackson and The Lightning Thief</li>\n<li>Pulp fiction</li>\n<li>The Pursuit of Happyness</li>\n<li>Saw 2</li>\n<li>Sin city</li>\n<li>Spy kids</li>\n<li>Stuart Little</li>\n<li>Wrong turn</li>\n<li>Twister</li>\n<li>Twins</li>\n<li>Three Ninjas</li>\n<li>Rush hour</li>\n<li>Rocky</li>\n<li>Run lola run</li>\n<li>Robocop 3</li>\n<li>Rain man</li>\n<li>Quantum of solace</li>\n<li>National Treasure</li>\n<li>National Treasure: Book of Secrets</li>\n<li>I robot</li>\n<li>Fast and the furious</li>\n</ul>        \n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(160,1,159,1,'converse size chart',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p>Converse does not manufacture its shoes as per US Sizing guidelines.This leads to some confusion about your converse sizes.But you dont have to worry about this as <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-buy-converse-shoes-if-you-live-outside-usa\">Converse website  </a> automatically converts the shoe from US size to <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/books-for-converse-fans\"> converse </a> size.For example:</p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"610\" height=\"540\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/kAESAzy4mjQ\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<ul>\n<li>Step 1 : Find your regular US foot size.</li>\n<li>Step 2 : While ordering enter this size (USA),converse will automatically tell you your converse size.I will show this by below example.Just go to below link</li> \n<li>http://www.converse.com/#/products/Shoes/ChuckTaylor/125644F</li>\n<li>Enter your regular size as 11.5 (US Mens) and converse website automatically converts and show the converse size as 11.Try it yourself with different sizes.</li>\n</ul></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<H3>Some points about converse size chart</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>The size written on inside of <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-stretch-converse-shoes\">converse shoe  </a> (or shoe box) is converse size.It has nothing to do with your regular sizing.For example if 11.5 is written on it than it means 12 in US size.</li>\n<li>Converse makes shoes in half sizes also.</li>\n<li>Try Nordstroms,if you are looking for shoes in kids sizes 2 or 3.</li>\n<li>All types of converse (lo tops,high tops,etc) follow the same sizing convention.</li>\n<li>The websites like amazon and ebay show the regular us size of converse shoes.Keep that in mind while ordering from these places.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>My converse size is 12,what size should i order in Vans or Puma?</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse shoes are generally bigger.Everyone that i know ,wears half size less in converse.So my suggestion is to add 1/2 to your converse size for vans or Puma.It means you should order shoes of 12.5 size.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>I am a women ,what is my converse size?</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse manufactures its shoes as per mens sizes only.Dont worry they have wonderful women styles and you just have to subtract 2 from your size.A women size of six means MENS 4.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>All the information about sizing chart is fine.But in my view you should go to store and see it for yourself before ordering it online.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(161,1,160,1,'Converse Tennis Shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5938985831/\" title=\"converse-tennis-1 by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6015/5938985831_7eb53f83ea.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" alt=\"converse-tennis-1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Tennis involves a lot of running and chasing the ball.It puts a lot of stress on your ankle and heels.Converse Tennis Shoes are answer to all of your problems as it is lightweight and protects your heels and ankles against all kind of motions by adjusting biomechanically to your every movement and by providing <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-repair-converse-shoes\"> extra padding and support to your heels and ankles </a>.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/w4AmyZPXBSI\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse tennis shoes are available in Jack Purcell <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-padded-collar\">Collection in many colors and sizes  </a>.Jack Purcell was a great player and champion.These shoes will give you advantage on court just like they did to jack purcell.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Some points about Jack Purcell Tennis Shoes</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>These are <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-lace-up-boots-for-girls\"> lightweight shoes </a> with lots of support and cushion for every movement on court.</li>\n<li>It is available for men,women and kids in both lo-top and slip-on.</li>\n<li>It has lightweight top,arch suport and thick sole.</li>\n<li>It uses flywire technology to protect your feet.</li>\n<li>Lightweight and easy to clean.</li>\n<li>These shoes are available in price range between 35 USD to 110 USD.You can not find a better tennis shoe in this price range.</li>\n<li>These shoes are also perfect for morning walk and for a trip to market.They give you retro look.You can even dance and go to gym in them.</li>\n<li>These shoes look good on every dress (cargo,jeans,skirts,etc).It even looks good with sundresses.</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"349\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/YPNLMBhuDS8\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Jack Purcell shoes in Movies</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>Peyton reed (director of teen commedy bring it on) loves converse tennis shoes.  </li>\n<li> Converse tennis shoes are placed in one scene of Marie Antoinette to show marie as normal teenage girl.  </li>\n\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Below i have listed the four tennis shoes on converse website Customize option:</h4>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>Red Jack Purcell</li>\n\n<li>Red Jack Purcell (Leather)</li>\n\n<li>Jack Purcell</li>\n\n<li>Jack Purcell Leather</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>My personal favorite is jack purcell plaid because of its unique textile upper.Believe me that coverse has one of best collection of tennis shoes.So go and buy a pair of tennis shoes and walk on to the court with confidence.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(162,1,161,1,'Top 21 Moments in the history of converse shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5925135011/\" title=\"converse-shoes-1 by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6024/5925135011_46123b1eb4.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"419\" alt=\"converse-shoes-1\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse is the <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info\"> most famous shoe company </a> in the world.The top 21 moments in its history from 1908 to 2008 are listed below :</p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/w_zyqUivDJE\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<ul></p>\n\n<p><li>1908 Marquis converse started the converse shoe company</li></p>\n\n<p><li>1917 Birth of <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/a-to-z-of-converse-hi-top-shoes\"> converse all star </a> (the first basketball shoe)</li></p>\n\n<p><li>1921 Famous basketball player chuck taylor joined the converse company.</li></p>\n\n<p><li>1930 converse all star was renamed as <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">converse chuck taylor all star  </a></li></p>\n\n<p><li>1935 Launch of Converse Jack Purcell (jack purcell was famous badminton player)</li></p>\n\n<p><li>1936 USA basketall team weared \"Converse white hi top all stars\" in 1936 olympics.They continued using it in next 8 olympics.</li></p>\n\n<p><li>1942 Converse desings A6 flying boot for usa army</li></p>\n\n<p><li>1945 The words on ankle patch were changed to \"converse all star\" from \"converse atheletic shoes,chuck taylor model\"</li></p>\n\n<p><li>1957 Launch of low cut All Star </li></p>\n\n<p><li>1962 Converse launches its very famous model oxford</li></p>\n\n<p><li>1966 Converse shoes are launched in 7 more colors keeping the younger generation in mind.Before 1966,it was available in only black and white.</li></p>\n\n<p><li>1967 earl llyod and bunny levitt joined the converse company</li></p>\n\n<p><li>1974 Launch of converse one star</li></p>\n\n<p><li>1981 First biometrics lab was created inside the company</li></p>\n\n<p><li>1984 converse company was the official sponsor of the olympic games</li></p>\n\n<p><li>1986 Weapon ad campaign is launched</li></p>\n\n<p><li>1991 Grandma ad campaign is launched</li></p>\n\n<p><li>2001 converse company files for bankruptcy</li></p>\n\n<p><li>2003 Nike purches the converse company</li></p>\n\n<p><li>2004 Converse i robot (inspired by will smith movie of the same name ) became one of best selling converse shoes </li></p>\n\n<p><li>2008 Converse completes its 100 years journey</li></p>\n\n<p></ul>        </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(163,1,162,2,'Why People love Converse Shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5925647134/\" title=\"converse-hi-top by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6027/5925647134_837ca415cc.jpg\" width=\"470\" height=\"417\" alt=\"converse-hi-top\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\">\nPeople are wearing converse shoes for around 100 years. It has been  worn  by kids, teenagers,women,celebrities,adults,etc. Its appeal cuts across <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/a-to-z-of-converse-hi-top-shoes\">generations, genders and all sections of society  </a>. Almost half the america has at least one pair of converse. It is the first choice of basketball players,rock musicians,film and television stars and the common man.The top seven reasons for the <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-shoes-in-movies\">amazing popularity of converse  </a> are discussed below:\n</div></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/ZPeS-hndAIE\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Inexpensive</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>They are the coolest thing available in 40 US dollar price range.Chucks rival the  <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-hiking-boots\">high end athletic shoes </a> in performance at one fourth of their price.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Durability</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>They offer the great value for your money as they last very long time.Some people are wearing same pair for more than 5-6 years.They have the <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">100 years of manufacturing experience  </a>.You can increase the life even more by alternating pairs and drying them completely before wearing.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Great comfort</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>No other shoe can fit like converse.People wearing them have claimed that they experience barefoot feeling.The \"arch insole\" supports your feet better than any other shoe.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Customization</h4>\n\n<p></br>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\">\nThey let you customize every part of your shoe( toe bumper,medial eyelet,outside body,Racing stripe,Lining,stich,etc). Combine it with amazing number of choices available in laces. You can create a unique shoe on converse website in 5 minutes that will be the envy of your friends and neighbours.\n</div></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Always in fashion</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse shoes always remain in fashion and help you adjust to different looks.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li> Retro look : Faded jeans and fold overs </li>\n<li>Classic look : Nothing beats the black hi-tops  </li>\n<li> Political : Try democracy or american flag models</li>\n<li> Sexy : Try knee high converse with skinny jeans</li>\n<li> Cute : Try pink or red converse </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4> Good customer support </h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse has the lowest failure rate in the market.Still if you find any fault with your shoe,just return the shoe with original reciept in 30 days.Your money will be refunded without any questions.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Seasonal designs</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse always launch its seasonal designs keeping the changing time and current taste in mind,apart from its core designs(classics).These seasonal designs are available for around one year.            </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(164,1,163,1,'How to buy converse shoes if you live outside USA',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5925135127/\" title=\"converse-shoes-2 by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6126/5925135127_7d194a09bc.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" alt=\"converse-shoes-2\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse company does not ship its shoes outside USA.If you live outside USA,you have two options for <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info\">buying converse shoes  </a> :</p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/x9lCTpbcVn4\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>You can buy it from country specific <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/books-for-converse-fans\">converse  websites </a> in the below 14 countries :</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>Mexico: www.converse.com.mx</li>\n<li>Argentina: www.converseargentina.com.ar</li>\n<li>South Korea: www.conversekorea.com</li>\n<li>Singapore: www.converse.com.sg</li>\n<li>Australia: www.converse.net.au</li>\n<li>Germany: www.converse.de</li>\n<li>Hungary: www.converse.hu</li>\n<li>Benelux: www.converse.be</li>\n<li>Spain: www.converse.es</li>\n<li>Czech Republic: www.conversecz.com</li>\n<li>South Africa: www.converse-sa.co.za</li>\n<li>United Kingdom: www.converse.co.uk</li>\n<li>Greater Balkans: www.converse.rs</li>\n<li>France: www.converse.fr</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>If you dont live in above 14 mentioned countries,you can try the Below URL to locate converse store in your country </h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Go to the URL https://www.converse.com/Help/RetailLocator.aspx</li>\n<li>Scroll down to the bottom</li>\n<li>Select your country ,Under the \"international\" field.For example ,i select \"Hong kong\" as country.</li>\n<li>Now the store results for the Hong Kong will be shown :Yue Ming International HONG KONG (852 2302 0213)</li>\n<li>You can repeat the above for any country.</li>\n\n</ul>        \n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(165,1,164,1,'Clean your converse in 5 minutes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5925164335/\" title=\"how-to-clean-converse by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6135/5925164335_1771b19cd3.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"300\" alt=\"how-to-clean-converse\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Use this 8 step tutorial to clean your <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-repair-converse-shoes\"> converse shoes </a>.These cleaning tips will help your shoes looking new forever.Some people prefer to hand wash instead of machine washing.In my view,both are equally efficient (machine washing saves time,even though it does not provide the same cleaing quality as hand).</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/m_mZ5TbnXnc\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<ul></p>\n\n<p><li>Remove the <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-lace-converse-high-tops\"> laces of the shoe </a> to provide easier access.</li></p>\n\n<p><li>Remove all the mud (dirt) using a dry brush.</li></p>\n\n<p><li>Place them under tap (lukewarm) water.It will moist <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-stretch-converse-shoes\"> the shoes </a> and make cleaning easier.Squeeze to remove the extra water.</li></p>\n\n<p><li>Create a paste mixture using 1 tablespoon each of vinegar,soda and hot water.</li></p>\n\n<p><li>Apply mixture on strains using toothbrush.Apply more strokes on deep stains.Try to clean stains part by part (like toes,sole,canvas,etc).</li></p>\n\n<p><li>Stains on canvas are difficult to remove.Use some detergent and wet soft towel.Try soaking instead of scrubbing,else the stain will spread to other parts</li></p>\n\n<p><li>Run your shoes under tap water until all the traces of paste are removed.</li></p>\n\n<p><li>Place them in the shadow and wait till they are dried completely.</li></p>\n\n<p></ul></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Tips on cleaning</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n\n\n<li>Add some drops of bleach if you are trying to clean white converse.</li>\n\n<li>Avoid bleach on rubber parts of shoe.</li>\n\n<li>Air dry is preffered method to sun drying.Sun light can cause color fading.</li>\n\n<li>Try handwashing for the first time if you have colored converse.They bleed a little color on first time washing.</li>\n\n<li>Use cold water and gentle mode if you are using washer.</li>\n\n<li>To remove any smell,mix the borax,detergent and soda in washer.</li>\n\n<li>Use rag or soft towel to remove the mud from glitters.</li>\n\n<li>Wash the laces seperately.</li>\n\n<li>You can try eraser to clean the white parts of shoe.</li>\n\n</ul>         \n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(166,1,165,1,'How to create unique converse shoe for women ,kids and man',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5925135247/\" title=\"converse-3 by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6020/5925135247_45dd0159e4.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" alt=\"converse-3\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>First Read the tutorial to customarize the converse shoes.After that open the URL given at the bottom of the tutorial.This tutorial will help you in designing your own <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">converse shoes for women,kids and man  </a>.</p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"610\" height=\"540\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/_Nrw39accK4\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Once you open the URL in your browser,You will see a list of 46 <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/best-of-chuck-commercials\">converse shoes  </a>.These are the shoes that you can customarize as per your taste.You will see 4 dropdowns on the top (collections,gender,material and style).</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Simple example to design canvas chuck taylor hi-top for women</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Select \"<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info\"> chuck taylor </a>\" from \"collections\" dropdown\".After that select \"female\" in \"gender\" dropdown.Now choose \"canvas\" in \"material\" and \"hi-top\" in \"style\" dropdown.</li>\n<li>You will see 7 converse shoes.These are the 7 canvas chuck taylor hi-top shoes available for women that can be customarized. Click on any of shoe to customarize as per your needs</li>\n<li>Once you select the shoe,you will see a bar (on top of bar 0/14 completed will be written)</li>\n<li>First click On \"outside body\" (first box in the top bar)</li>\n<li>You will see two options :color and print.Choose what you like.</li>\n<li>Once you have selected the color and print,you will see 1/14 on top of bar.</li>\n<li>You can use \"zoom\" and \"rotate\" buttons just below the shoe to reconfirm your selection.</li>\n<li>You need to repeat the process for rest 13 boxes in the bar.These other options are tongue,lace,toe cap,toe bumper,medial eyelet,outside body,Racing stripe,Lining,stich,rubber sidewall,Heel stripe and inside body. </li>\n<li>Just click on \"your size\" tab ,once you finish the design.You will have two international sizing options (usa,uk).After that select gender(women),size and qty.</li>\n<li>Last step is to click on the \"save\" button</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>In similar way you can design converse shoes for kids and man.You just need to change the values in the \"gender\" dropdown to \"kids\" or \"man\".</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Notes :</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>The url is http://www.converse.com/#/products/shoes/converseOne/scratch/all.Just copy and paste in your browser.</li>\n<li>Please create your account on converse website before starting the custom design.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Collections availble for customarization are  :</h4>\n\n<p></br>\n<ul>\n<li>Chuck taylor</li></p>\n\n<p><li>Jack purcell</li></p>\n\n<p><li>One star suede</li></p>\n\n<p><li>Basketball</li></p>\n\n<p><li>Skateboarding</li></p>\n\n<p><li>Sport authentics</li></p>\n\n<p><li>Converse(product) red</li>\n</ul></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Materials available for customarization are </h4>\n\n<p></br>\n<ul></p>\n\n<p><li>Canvas</li>\n<li>leather</li>\n<li>suede</li>\n</ul></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4> styles available for customarization are </h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>lo-top</li>\n<li>hi-top</li>\n<li>X-hi</li>\n<li>slip-on</li>\n\n</ul>        \n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(167,1,166,1,'How To Lace Converse High Tops',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5925725890/\" title=\"lace-converse by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6022/5925725890_dba2291961.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"370\" alt=\"lace-converse\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Usually converse high tops come with short laces, which make it difficult to tie them trendily and conveniently. But with long laces you will be able to <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/popular-lacing-styles-for-converse-shoes\"> lace your converse in a stylish manner </a>. Everybody has his own style of lacing a converse. But some instructions below can help you in designing the lacing of converse in a much better way.\nYou should always count the number of eyelets of your converse sneakers.  Usually the <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/a-to-z-of-converse-hi-top-shoes\">high tops  </a> have up to twelve eyelet pairs.</p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/g_5LhDRUG6Q\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Depending on the number of eyelet pairs you can lace your sneakers in different ways. If your <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/a-to-z-of-converse-hi-top-shoes\"> high tops </a> have twelve pairs then you should go with seventy two inch lace, and for nine eyelet pairs you require sixty three inch and for eight eyelet pairs, fifty four inch <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-lace-converse-high-tops\">shoe lace  </a> is needed.  In order to avoid dirt on your shoe laces, white color should be avoided and darker color shoe laces should be chosen.  Flat athletic laces should be given preference over round ones.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You should start with putting unlaced shoe in one of your foot, and in order to avoid discomfort at later stages, you should flatten out any creases. You should start with putting on laces through your shoes from top most eyelets and it should be tangent to the shoe. Then you should tighten the laces and make equal length of laces on both sides.  Right side lace should be crossed over the first eyelet on the left side. Thread the lace into the eyelets. Then do the same process with the left shoe and make it to cross over to right side. You can simply lace the whole shoe by following these steps with all the eyelets which are left over.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Another method which you can follow to lace your converse high tops is firstly put the laces at the top of the shoe, making sure that the lace should not go outside the shoe. And tie a knot which is loose which will make it very convenient afterwards in pulling out the strings. Some people prefer to have converse with short laces as it will consume less time in lacing and cleaning the eyelets afterwards.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>There are some general points which need due consideration, such as:</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Each eyelet should have ace only one time passed through them.\nLaces should be very easy to loosen or tighten.       </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(168,1,167,1,'how to repair converse shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5939305293/\" title=\"converse-shoe_repair by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6129/5939305293_a6e9a5086d.jpg\" width=\"451\" height=\"500\" alt=\"converse-shoe_repair\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You can easily repair your <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/\"> converse shoes</a>  in home by investing as little as 5 to 10 US Dollars.Below i have listed the most common issues faced by converse owners and their solutions.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/pjg379TX0h4\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Rubber sidewall and racing stripe is coming out</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You need to go to store and buy Shoe-Goo.It is an adhesive designed for fixing shoes.Just apply it in area that is coming out and hold it together for some time using your both hands.Make sure that you don\'t apply too much.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Scratches on Shoe</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Buy a marker of the same color as <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-promo-code-2011\"> your shoe </a> .</li>\n<li>Apply it on scratches .</li>\n<li>Immediately rub it off using a cloth (back and forth).</li>\n<li>Aply polish in circular motion.</li>\n<li>After that rub it using cloth (round and round).</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"425\" height=\"349\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/_Nrw39accK4\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>How to prevent fading of shoes ?</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Buy a sharpie of same color as your shoe and apply it on faded areas.</li>\n<li>Another option is to place duct tape on wearing areas.You need to repalce them from time to time.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Hole in sole</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Buy napkin or tissues.</li>\n<li>Apply shoe goo around the hole.</li>\n<li>Now place the napkin above the hole and press it using both your hands for around 90 seconds.It will increase the life of your shoe by some weeks.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Damaged Heel</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Take a cloth of medium thickness and high durability(denim) or you can buy backlinings from store.</li>\n<li>Apply shoe goo on affected area.</li>\n<li>Place cloth over applied shoe goo and apply pressure for some time.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Try below tips on your converse shoes to increase its life:</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Always wash your shoes and make sure that its dried properly.</li>\n<li>In case of leather shoes,you need to polish them regularly.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>In my view, The converse looks much better when its ragged.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(169,1,168,1,'Tips to  stretch your converse',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5925725934/\" title=\"Shoe-Stretch-converse by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6029/5925725934_38341b3e25.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"500\" alt=\"Shoe-Stretch-converse\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You need to stretch your converse,if you find them tight when you wear them for first time.It is preffered to check your size and <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> buy the right size </a>.But the feet of some persons fall between two sizes like 8 or 8.5 causing discomfort.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/qf5mJ7aR2t8\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<h4>Use ice to stretch the converse using the expanding property of water when it freezes</h4></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Buy ziploc bag</li>\n<li>Put a glass of water inside the bag</li>\n<li>Take the air out and seal the bag</li>\n<li>Insert bag in <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-hiking-boots\"> the boot </a> and tap it down to problem area</li>\n<li>Put the boot in freezer for 6 hours</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-tell-if-converse-shoes-are-fake\"> Try the shoes </a></li>\n<li>Repeat the process if the problem persists.</li>\n<li>Make sure that your bag does not leaks.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Tips to stretch converse</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Loosen the laces all the way.It will provide some extra space for your feet.</li>\n<li>Just go to shoe store and for shoe stretcher.Decide on length or width wide stretching.</li>\n<li>Buy the shoe tree from walmart and place it inside converse when you are not wearing them.</li>\n<li>Wear them for a week till they adjust to your feet.Converse shoes take some time to adjust to your feet shape. Use band aids to avoid blisters.</li>\n<li>Wash them 2 or 3 times in first week.It will loosen them up.</li>\n<li>Go for thinner sock,it will provide some extra space between your feet and shoe.</li>\n<li>Buy shoe stretch solution.Put some drops inside the shoe and walk in the shoes for aroud 30 minutes</li>\n<li>Use alcohol: Either use a shoe tree or wear them.</li>\n</ul>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(170,1,169,1,'how to tell if converse shoes are fake',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5925164521/\" title=\"Spot-Fake-Converse-3 by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6015/5925164521_b1fe9e7726.jpg\" width=\"280\" height=\"390\" alt=\"Spot-Fake-Converse-3\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>This is an tutorial to help you seerate the fake converse from the genuine ones.We will see it using an example.Lets say that you have brought a <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/a-to-z-of-converse-hi-top-shoes\"> Converse chuck taylor all star shoe (hi-top shoe) </a> for your husband.Lets assume that the shoe is of black color ,made of canvas and size is 8.5</p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/x9_OVLD9G28\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br>\n<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br>\nGo to converse website.In the search box,type \"<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/books-for-converse-fans\">All Star  </a> \"</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Now you need to select :</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<Li>select \"Black and grays\" in \"color\" dropdown</li>\n<Li>select \"chuck taylor\" in \"collection\" dropdown</li>\n<Li>Select \"men\" in \"gender\" dropdown</li>\n<Li>select \"canvas\" in \"material\" dropdown</li>\n<Li>select \"hi-top\" in \"style\" dropdown</li>\n<Li>select \"8.5\" in \"size\" dropdown</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"425\" height=\"349\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/XBiAwvhKdZE\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br></p>\n\n<p>Now you will see a list of some shoes.Select the one that you have brought.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Look at the price of the shoe.Your converse is fake If you brought it at less price.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Just look at the image of the selected shoe.Compare it with the shoe in your hand.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You will see three small shoe images,just below your selected converse.These small images show your converse from different angles.Select them one by one and compare the shoes from every angle.Everything should look exactly the same.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>You will see the logo in side view.Its a circle with \"Converse\" written on top and \"all star\" at the bottom.\n</li>\n<li>A star sign will be between the above words</li>\n<li>Check for chuck taylor signature.\"Chuck\" will be on left hand side of star and \"taylor\" will be on right hand side of star.</li>\n<li>You will see a small circled r ,just above the words \"all star\" and below the star sign.</li>\n<li>In the behind view (click on third small image),you will see \"All star\" written on the heel that are seperated by star sign.A small circled star will be just below the star.</li>\n<li>Look at the color of the words.</li>\n<li>Check the number of holes,stich,lining,toe cap,lace,tongue,etc.</li>\n<li>Your shoes are genuine If everything matches exactly.</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h4>Notes</h4>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n<Li>Either order online from converse website or buy from a converse showroom.</li>\n<li>Converse sell shoes in half sizes also</li>\n<li>Never buy converse at very low price like 20 USD </li>\n</ul>         \n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(171,1,170,1,'How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5925725776/\" title=\"converse-skinny-jeans by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6024/5925725776_c9368177d5.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" alt=\"converse-skinny-jeans\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>With the advent of summer, women start thinking about getting themselves into something that is cool and comfortable and looks attractive as well.  <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/knee-high-converse-shoes\"> Wearing knee high Converse </a> with skinny jeans is a new trend taken up by women to look attractive and to make waves around.  These women pair it up with skinny jeans that makes them look like fashion divas.<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\"> They were introduced back in 1917 </a>\n and since then they had withstood the never ending competition and ever increasing fashion trends. </p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/YYUm4o1aDmY\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>At first they were brought into market as <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/\">Basketball shoes</a>\n. They have retained their style and design throughout their product life cycle and even after so long they are going great. They are probably converse companies most stylish and fast selling models. There is a particular way of wearing these <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/a-to-z-of-converse-hi-top-shoes\"> converse high-tops </a> with skinny jeans.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The main thing here is to lace up your converse high-tops in a near to perfect manner. Starting with the tip of the shoelace then insert it through the top hole at the left, then repeat the whole process till you reach the bottom of it. Do the same thing with the second one too.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Tightly holding each shoelace tip, pull both the shoelaces towards you. Keep it in mind that both the right and the left ends are same. Get hold of the left shoelace by its tip and pull it diagonally across towards the right-side hole second from the top. Put the left end shoelace tip into this hole and repeat the process till it reaches the bottom.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Now take the right end of the shoelace and pull it diagonally across the left hole that is second from the top and slid it into the hole and continue in the same manner going down. Make sure four out of eight holes are laced on both the sides.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>It’s time to get your socks and wear them. Now is the time to get your shoes. Well, begin by taking a shoe and putting it on and then pull its laces towards you tightly while keeping its tongue away. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Now get the shoelaces tied up in a bow underneath its tongue. Get the tongue back to you and that largely depends on your preference weather you like it straight up or lie flat on your feet.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Now get down the bottom of your skinny jeans and make sure it covers your socks. Now you are ready to go and rock the fashion streets.       </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(172,1,171,1,'Important converse links',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5925696964/\" title=\"converse-4 by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6140/5925696964_29c6146c29.jpg\" width=\"332\" height=\"500\" alt=\"converse-4\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The collection of seven links from <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/important-converse-links\">converse websites</a> like sizing information,gift cards,track order status,reuse shoe ,store locator,etc.</p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/90fRlMQTdSs\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Just go to below link and enter your order number and email id to track the status of the shoes <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info\">ordered from the converse</a> .</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.converse.com/Help/OrdersShippingAndReturns/Index.aspx\"> Track converse order status</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You can easily find the shoe size of your kid.Just go to below url and print the image.lace your kids feet on the print out and measure the size.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.converse.com/pdf/kids_sizing_chart.pdf\"> Print the Kid sizing chart</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You can reuse your converse shoe easily.Converse has partnered with nike to reuse the shoes.Nike uses old converse shoes to build turf fields and sports tracks.Please support this program to preserve your environment.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://play.converse.com/?p=3196\">Reuse your converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You can locate the converse stores in any country by going to below URL</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.converse.com/Help/RetailLocator.aspx\">Converse store locator</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>If you love creative touch and want your converse shoe to be unique.Just go to below url and design your own shoe.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.converse.com/#/landing/create\">Design your own converse shoe</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Check the top converse cut and paste designs at this url </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://play.converse.com/?p=7497\">Converse cut and paste designs</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You can register for converse open gym and start playing basketball with the converse stars.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.converse.com/experiences/opengym/Register.aspx\">Converse open gym</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse gift card is perfect for your friends,family or girlfriend.Just order from below url.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.converse.com/#/products/giftcard/giftcardPhysical\">Order converse gift card online</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.converse.com/#/products/giftcard/giftcardLanding\">Check your gift card balance</a>        </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(173,1,172,1,'Knee High Converse For Girls',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5925492266/\" title=\"knee-high-converse by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6013/5925492266_4fee76d645.jpg\" width=\"493\" height=\"500\" alt=\"knee-high-converse\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>In this day and age, everyone wants to look stylish and trendy, especially women. Women are more concerned about fashion as compared to men. They want to look younger and gorgeous. In addition to stylish dresses, women can look appealing and elegant by <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-knee-high-boots-for-girls\">wearing fashionable, knee high, converse shoes  </a>.  </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/dOHozy4jgjo\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>These shoes are not only available for young and slim girls, but also for plus sized women.They can wear it easily due to its broad width at the top. Knee high converse shoes go up to your knees, and they are also called as <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-knee-high-sneakers-for-kids\">knee high chucks  </a>.Girls can make fashion statements by wearing it, as it is stylish and trendy.  It gives you a sexy look and whenever you wear it you are sure to get a lot of compliments. The best feature of <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-knee-high-socks\"> knee high converse </a> is that it keeps your feet warm in winters.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You can wear it with many outfits and it will enhance your personality if you wear it with a pair of jeans. It can be worn to various occasions and goes well with all kinds of outfits. It is available in various exquisite shapes like round, pointed or square toes. It comes in wide range of colors. All the girls must have at least one pair of knee high converse shoes in their wardrobe. The main reason for girls to have the knee high converse is that it is affordable and you could easily transform it into various styles and creative looks, as a result you may get many stylish appearances, which is definitely an additional benefit for young girls. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You can fold over the top section of the knee high converse to form a cuff; moreover you will discover that the interior of the knee highs’ is lined with multi-colored material, which gives it a classy look. To make your knee high converse look even more fashionable, you could lace them to the half way position and leave the rest of the portion open to create yet another extraordinary look.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>If you are among those who like to remain ahead of the latest fashion, wear knee high converse shoes and become a trend setter.         </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(174,1,173,1,'Knee High Converse For Kids',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5924930615/\" title=\"knee-high-converse-kids by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6133/5924930615_eb0698a28c.jpg\" width=\"343\" height=\"500\" alt=\"knee-high-converse-kids\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Knee high Converse for kids has been relatively latest addition to their list of <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-promo-code-2011\"> matchless collection of shoes </a>\n. Converse has also manufactured shoes designed and dedicated to celebrities. Many young celebrities also endorse and wear knee high converse shoes. Converse holds the benchmark in the shoe industry for being highly innovative and manufacturing <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/knee-high-converse-shoes\"> fashionable and sturdy shoes </a>\n.</p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/z5NbqZHa2jA\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The designs that Converse offers are unparallel. Most of them have a canvas upper with a sole made from rubber. <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info\"> Converse Chuck Taylor </a> for kids is a well known brand having variety of shoes made of canvas, suede and vinyl with stylish linings so that when the shoes are folded at knees the design of lining shows and makes it more attractive. Knee high Converse for kids comes with laces or without laces, <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-lace-up-boots-for-girls\"> buckled, zipped or strapped </a>.</p>\n\n<p></br>\nKnee high Converse for kids has a wide range of models to suit the particular style and taste of kids. They range from fancy to sports, elegant to funky; there is an array of models to fit the versatility of kids.  They come in different types like suede, canvas, vinyl etc. and also with and without laces. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>One of the most famous knee high Converse for kids is the Chuck Taylor All Star Easy Slip Flag Sneaker that has got flag printed on it , which gives a colorful look to it. Kids can also design their own Converse before buying a -Design Your Own- by Dr. Seuss. Many Converse models have been dedicated to big celebrities and youth icons. Converse high knee shoes for kids have become a rage, the world over.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>They are very trendy and comfortable and kids love to have something different from the same old sports sneakers in their wardrobe. Besides giving options of designing your own shoes, Converse offers heavy discounts on online purchases. By keeping in mind that kids shoes’ may undergo lot of wear and tear, knee high Converse for kids have been made with great quality material to make them long-lasting in addition to being comfortable and modish. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>From 1900s when it was manufactured as sports sneakers for the basketball players to the 21st century when it has become an iconic image in the world of shoe industry, Converse has come a long way. From its all-time popular Converse All-stars to the latest and hip Converse -The Weapon 86 and The Weapon EVO, it has reached out to the worldwide market and pleased millions of customers with its quality and comfort.      </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(175,1,174,1,'Knee High Converse Shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5925492534/\" title=\"knee-high-converse-shoes by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6009/5925492534_054845a392.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"400\" alt=\"knee-high-converse-shoes\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Give your old school look a break. Give your image a makeover and double it up with knee high Converse shoes. <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-knee-high-boots-for-girls\">Converse high knee shoes  </a> have transformed the way people look at shoes. They are the new generation shoes worn by teenagers and young adults to <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-knee-high-sneakers-for-kids\">give their looks a boost  </a>. </p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/xSJBEZw2dJc\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>They come in many forms and can be worn on bare legs as well as with jeans and other dresses that <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-knee-high-socks\"> cover your legs </a>. You can never go unnoticed while wearing it and will always be the center of attention, as they go well with any attire, from party-wear to sports-wear. Knee high Converse shoes come in a range of colors and designs, and you can choose the one that perfectly fits your personality and taste. They can be with or without laces, in canvas and in rubber, <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/thigh-high-converse-sneakers\"> covering knees or just ending before knees start </a>. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>They can be modified and made into sporty and funky looking shoes, for instance, you can fold them at the top and fasten with cuffs or velcro straps or buttons, which will enhance the appearance of the shoes. You can lace it up differently or inadequately to make it look a bit different. The interior of the shoes is lined with material having attractive design to make sure that it looks nice if and when you fold it at the knees. Knee high Converse shoes comes in different patterns; you can opt for a simple pattern with laces that can be used as sports or casual shoes, or you can buy designer shoes that have different models that are suited for versatile people. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Another plus is that knee high Converse shoes are affordable and can be bought by anyone who wants to look fashionable and chic. The quality of material used is tested under many quality control methods to ensure that the end product is highly durable and has longevity on top of being sporty. The comfort provided by them is matchless, and it won’t pinch or sore your feet, rather you will feel like you are gliding effortlessly. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Knee high Converse shoes are easily washable, which means that you don’t have to worry about getting it dirty, and every time you wash it, you can make it as good as new. So, all said and done, Knee high Converse shoes are the way forward, and if you are looking for shoes that can complement your personality and accentuate your sexy legs you should surely have one of these in your wardrobe.        </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(176,1,175,1,'Popular Lacing Styles For Converse Shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5925492612/\" title=\"converse-lacing-styles by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6140/5925492612_9142a39bf3.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" alt=\"converse-lacing-styles\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse is America’s most popular sneaker till date, starting its operations in 1900s. These sneakers have a demand which is timeless and that’s why it’s heavy on consumers’ minds. <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-golf-shoes\">Converse sneakers  </a> are liked mostly by musicians, kids, artists, women and teenagers. Most of you must be in love with the sneakers and have developed various <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-lace-converse-high-tops\">methods of lacing your favorite converse shoes  </a>. The most popular methods of lacing your sneakers are </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/A53xy88md-g\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Bottom tie method:</b>  This is the rare lacing method. But it also has a huge number of fans who follow this way of lacing. <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-lace-converse-high-tops\">To start lacing your sneaker  </a> by this method, you should first wear it. Starting with the two holes, which are nearest to your ankle, and then intertwine them loosely till you reach to the bottom eyelets of the shoe.  You should always intertwine loosely while following the process.  When you will reach at the shoe’s bottom then make a <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/what-to-wear-with-green-converse-high-tops\"> Classic </a> bow of two lace ends, as you would also do in case of cross lace. The pattern will result in the reverse cross lace and you will not have to bow at ankles, but at toes.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Classic cross lace:</b> Initiating with putting the lace through the bottom eyelets of the sneakers and then start pulling the laces.  Then you have to pull the right lace through the hole which is nearer. Then continue the same on the opposite side for the lace on the left side. Follow the same pattern and go on with lacing the whole shoe in the same fashion by stretching both the laces through holes on opposite sides.  By doing this properly you will surely see your shoe laces in x pattern and it will provide a classy look. Most of the people, who believe that things should be kept free from adulteration and otherwise they lost their essence, prefer this classy pattern of lacing. Many people like their sneaker lacing pattern in the same way as their grandparents or parents used to do it.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><b>Loose Laced Look:</b>  It’s started in the same way as in cross lacing; begin by pulling the lace through the two holes at the bottom of the shoe near to the toe. Go upwards repeating the same procedure as followed in cross lace. Now when you will reach at ¾ , immediately stop and the process is finished.  Now move around and check out how you feel in partially laced sneakers. Well one thing should be ensured that partially laced sneakers fit in your comfort zone. This is the trendiest style of lacing; providing your shoes with casual, scruffy look. Converse high tops usually look perfect with loose lacing.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(177,1,176,1,'Rainbow Converse Shoes',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5936954276/\" title=\"rainbow converse by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6131/5936954276_ee3db132f2.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"286\" alt=\"rainbow converse\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Rainbow converse shoes are for the people who want multicolored unique shoes.After all,every one wants to add little bit of color in their life. <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/knee-high-converse-for-girls\"> These shoes are cute </a> and goes with almost all the outfits of your wardrobe. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/Xt5Ni6RaOgA\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Converse is selling all star rainbows for kids in the age group 4 to 12 years.The outer body has the rainbow graphics and it <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-tennis-shoes\">looks cool with the white colored Rubber  </a> sidewall,toe cap and toe bumper.I was unable to find much options on converse website.I will suggest to look in walmart,target,macys and Journeys.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Unfortunately the converse website does not have any rainbow <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">shoes waiting for customization  </a>.You can look for some local artist who can handpaint shoes for your kids.This is perfect for people who are looking for unique shoes to impress their friends.If you do not want to invest that much money than you can buy a clean pair of converse shoes and try to color it with hair spray or spray paint.Please avoid varnish as it leaves permanent color on your shoes.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"425\" height=\"349\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/5PU_1FzRGMU\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>If you dont want to go for rainbow shoes because of its queer nature but need a unique look than the best option is to buy Youth hi-top rainbow laces(36 inches) at just 3 dollars from the converse website.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Best rainbow converse shoes</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>CONVERSE Kids\' CT Stretch Lace Ox  </li>\n<li> Converse Ct Rainbow Ox Grey Womens Trainers </li>\n<li> CONVERSE Kids\' A S Stretch Lace Tod </li>\n<li> Converse Kids Rainbow Leopard Print Low Top Sneaker </li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Go and buy rainbow shoes for sweet and cute looks.My personal favorite is leopard print on upper canvas.These shoes are best for kids and women.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(178,1,177,1,'Thigh High Converse Sneakers',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5924930323/\" title=\"thigh-high-converse by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6141/5924930323_14cbf69b44.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"300\" alt=\"thigh-high-converse\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Thigh high <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/a-list-of-top-5-controversies-of-converse-shoes\"> Converse sneakers </a>  have been around from a very long time.These converse thigh high sneakers come in different colors and in good combinations as well.  <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\"> The converse designers </a>  work really hard to research what colors to come up with and when. </p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/OLrdIaVQw7U\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info\">These sneakers come in </a>  red, white and black colors. Sometimes it the combinations of these colors that make it look very different. There are some color combinations which can be used with any piece of clothing you have. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Given its comfort level everyone loves it, besides it gives you a very hot and sexy look. They are specially designed to mold in the shape of your leg and give it a perfect look. The material they use in them is very soft and it adjusts itself according to the shape of your legs and at the same time does not scratch your skin.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>These tall shoes can be used while dressing yourself in skirts at the same time they easily cover under part of your upper thighs. They come in the shape of sneakers that means you can participate in any event while having them on. They basically have this sporty nature. You can basically play any game while having them on.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The interiors of these sneakers come in color. You can fold them down on a particular occasion giving your dress a new added look. Everyone is very proud to own it. Because there are always compliments coming your way if you have them put on. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Everyone buys them not because they have to but because they love to be loved by the people around them. In these Converse thigh high sneakers girls always look beautiful and naughty while going around and everyone falls in love with them the way they look.  It is a style you should have and you should own. They surely have become one of the hottest choices for women in the 21st century. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>They have the much needed expertise to make shoes that will make a mark and that can get you to the top of the fashion world. They know what type of shoe and when to come up with it in the market. They make shoes which generally under normal conditions can last long. You will find these in everyone’s shopping lists these days. The thing is that they can suit with any type of outfit you wear.  </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(179,1,178,1,'What to wear with gray converse high tops',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5950685456/\" title=\"gray-converse-high-tops by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6002/5950685456_16a98fb868.jpg\" width=\"333\" height=\"500\" alt=\"gray-converse-high-tops\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Some cloth suggestions for your gray converse</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/CNfV_ri87us\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<ul></p>\n\n<p><li>Dark colored <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\"> skinny jeans looks too good  </a> with gray.Avoid too tight jeans as it is uncomfortable.</li></p>\n\n<p><li>Girls can try matching tote bags and silver Earrings</li></p>\n\n<p><li>Remember that you need  <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info\"> So try black </a>  to compliment grey.So try black shirt or sweater OR yellow tee or cardigan.</li></p>\n\n<p><li>Denim skirts and shorts look good on slim legs.Leggings are another top choice.</li></p>\n\n<p><li><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/knee-high-converse-shoes\"> Experiment with  </a> pink and black shoe laces</li></p>\n\n<p><li>Never try to match gray with gray.</li></p>\n\n<p></ul></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Grey is one color that matches with everything.Gray is Similar to black and it matching with every color of clothes.It is a neutral color and cool with almost everything.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Some tips on your gray converse high tops</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>You can use bleach to add whiteness to your grey shoes.Believe me ,it looks really cool.</li>\n\n<li>If you dont want to buy a complete grey shoe than the best option for you is is to buy grey striped converse shoes.</li>\n\n<li>Roxy Mitchell (played by Rita Simons) wears grey converse shoes in one episode of popular tv serial Eastenders.</li>\n\n<li>Four colors that really compliments grey are  navy blue ,pink ,yellow and purple.</li>\n\n<li>Pink,blue and black laces goes well with grey shoes.You should buy a pair of each of these laces and rotate for fun.</li>\n\n<li>For fun purposes you can use sharpie to color the white parts of your grey converse.You can add some doodles or anything that looks cool and unique.</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Gray converse high tops are perfect addition to your growing converse collection.It is one of the best colors to have in your wardrobe.      </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(180,1,179,1,'What to wear with green converse high tops',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5954151748/\" title=\"green-converse-high-tops by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6022/5954151748_dcda46502e.jpg\" width=\"333\" height=\"500\" alt=\"green-converse-high-tops\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Nothing is more cute and vintage than Green <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/a-to-z-of-converse-hi-top-shoes\">converse high tops  </a> . Below i have listed the dressing options that really look good with green chucks.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/OGpklkstpww\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>Pair of forest green bangles,Green pearl necklace,Black <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\">skinny jeans  </a> ,Dark green emma tank top,black waistcoat.Add a metal shiny belt.</li>\n\n<li>Wear Satin tube top with blue bleached skinny jeans.</li>\n\n<li><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/what-to-wear-with-gray-converse-high-tops\">Wear Casual   </a> white tank top with navy blue skinny jeans.</li>\n\n<li>My favorite is Black Button Front Half-Sleeved Top with white denim shorts.</li>\n\n<li>Try Black jeans with Black shirt (with green stripes)</li>\n\n<li>Dark denim and white shirts looks cool and are good for daily activities.</li>\n\n<li>Another favorite look is white short with light pink t shirt.</li>\n\n<li>Wear red skirt and  neon green shirt for halloween and prom nights.</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Some more suggestions for your green converse high tops</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>Buy matching earring,nailpolish and hair bands.Always remember that Red,black,yellow and orange colors compliment the green.</li>\n\n<li>Never bleach your green chucks else they will loose their original color.</li>\n\n<li>Buy dark sholelaces to give the glowing effect.White shoelaces also look good with green.</li>\n\n<li>Black knee high socks will look cool with your green chucks.</li>\n\n<li>Always avoid pants with patterns and stripes.</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>If you dont want to buy pure green then you should take a look at shoes in below colors :</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>Neon green </li>\n<li>lime green </li>\n<li>celtic green </li>\n<li>Bamboo green</li>\n<li>Pine green </li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You can buy Green converse high tops from converse website.Converse site lets you design your own shoes.If you prefer shopping in stores,then you can try below stores :</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>Journey</li>\n<li>JC Penny</li>\n<li>Sears</li>\n<li>Nordstroms</li>\n<li>Walmart</li>\n<li>Footlockers</li>\n<li>Eastbay</li>\n<li>Gap</li>\n</ul>      \n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(181,1,180,1,'What to wear with silver converse high tops',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5950126653/\" title=\"silver-converse-high-tops by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6147/5950126653_546d194e5b.jpg\" width=\"333\" height=\"500\" alt=\"silver-converse-high-tops\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Are you looking for some funky shoes for prom night or your date or for halloween party ? If the answer to the question is yes than look no further than the Funky silver <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info\"> converse high tops </a>.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/ouZ1sUiJt5Y\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/important-converse-links\"> Always remember that</a> Silver is a color that shows your intelligence and maturity and It has a calming effect on others.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>What colors to avoid with silver converse high tops</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Silver is a neutral color like black and <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info\">grey</a> and so it looks good with almost any color in this world.But i will suggest you to avoid yellow and orange with silver as other colors look much better.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Some cloth suggestions for your silver converse</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>Wear a matching headband(pink looks coolest).</li>\n\n<li>Try silver or daimond earrings to add x factor to your converse shoes.It is better if earrings are large and sparkle from a distance.</li>\n\n<li>Tr purple cotton leggings for halloween party.You will love it.</li>\n\n<li>You can wear pencil skirt with Red T-shirt.Another favorite of mine is dark jeans (navy blue) with striped shirts.</li>\n\n<li>If you are in hurry,you can try Any t-shirt with skinny jeans(go for extra tight ones).\n\n<li>You can try hoodies also</li>\n\n<li>Add a denim jacket or sweater (red) in the winter season</li>\n\n<li>Keep in mind that the Black ,purple l,ime green and aqua colors goes well with silver.My personal favorite is blue.</li>\n\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>You can add some silver patterns on your black converse using a silver sharpie If you dont have a silver converse.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Always keep in mind that nothing expresses your feminine side better than silver converse.So go and buy a silver converse high tops to express yourself.</p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(182,1,181,1,'what to wear with yellow converse',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5953655355/\" title=\"yellow-converse by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6012/5953655355_f7679ea05f.jpg\" width=\"385\" height=\"500\" alt=\"yellow-converse\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>Yellow converse shoes are attention drawing as it is the easiest color to spot.Yellow high tops helps you to gain attention in parties and work places.Below i have carefully prepared dresses that will match with your yellow <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info\"> converse high tops </a>.Try these dresses and look in mirror to find out the best one for you.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/M-9wjbgWgJM\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n\n<li>Wear with Denim short and <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/a-to-z-of-converse-hi-top-shoes\"> white </a> t shirt with some funky design on grid hat and matching tote bag for even better look.</li>\n<li>Black t shirt ,dark green leather jacket and blue skinny jeans.</li>\n<li>Wear it with White t shirt (with black stripes) and polka skirt(the best is pink polka dots on black ).</li>\n<li>Black high waisted skirt with Yellow black checkered shirt.</li>\n<li>Red hairband,drak sunglasses and purple ring adds to the magic.</li>\n<li>Black opaque tight,purple denim skirt and white t-shirt (with v neck).</li>\n<li>Black t-shirt,black hat,silver colored elephant necklace and dot jeans(its better if you find one with Blue,red and yellow dots on white).</li>\n<li>You can try studded acid washed jeans for unique looks.</li>\n<li>Red and green striped shirts with navy blue jeans.</li>\n<li>Always remeber that the yellow looks best with the purple.It also matches well ith brown,black and purple.\n</ul>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<h3>Take care of these points while buying yellow converse shoes :</h3>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<ul>\n\n<li>Buy purple or brown shoes laces for your yellow shoes.Always experiemnt with laces to find the perfect ones.</li>\n<li>Try matching hats,earrings,bags,hair clips,rings,necklaces and socks to add to the beauty of yellow color.</li>\n<li>You can buy these shoes from stores or you can design your own at converse website.</li>\n\n</ul>      \n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(183,1,182,1,'Yellow Converse High Tops For Kids',1,'<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"pub-8530669473842162\";\n/* Converse Shoes rect ad */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"0783133816\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 336;\ngoogle_ad_height = 280;\n//-->\n</script>\n\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/redagni/5925492108/\" title=\"yellow-converse-hi-tops by redagni, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6146/5925492108_e362af4198.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"302\" alt=\"yellow-converse-hi-tops\"></a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The yellow color of these Converse shoes is popular among the general masses. The yellow colors make these shoes very different and attractive.  These colors are <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/\">available for kids, women and men  </a>. Many prefer yellow color over all other colors because of its attractive looks and being very different than the rest. </p>\n\n<p></br>\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"510\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/FsQvBqZ6308\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n\n<p></br>\n<a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-create-unique-converse-shoe-for-women-kids-and-man\">Design Unique Converse shoes in 5 minutes</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/how-to-wear-knee-high-converse-with-skinny-jeans\"> How To Wear Knee High Converse With Skinny Jeans</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-size-chart\"> Converse Size Chart</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">History of converse shoes</a></p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>There is a wide variety of yellow colored shoes in converse with one thing in common and that is quality and the style converse is meant to be.There is a particular type known as <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/history-of-converse-shoes\">Chuck Taylor shoes  </a> in the category of High tops which is classic in nature and has been around for a long time. They are simple made from rubber and canvas and have made a mark in the world because of their simplicity. Their popularity has never decreased since they came into market.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>There is another type known as yellow <a href=\"http://www.theconverseshoes.info/converse-double-upper-shoe\">converse all stars  </a>. They are very hot among the crowd. They are different yet very stylish. They are very comfortable and they are very affordable too. The yellow color makes them get easily noticed in the crowd. The yellow color has bright properties yet it is very soothing to eyes.</p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>These yellow Converse shoes come in various styles and sizes and they look very cute and trendy. Children usually love them.  Children look smart in them. Due to its bright property children who have them on easily get observed among the rest and are always admired by the on lookers as they look cute in them. This yellow color suits children as it signifies life full of happiness and playful mood. It goes well with the general character of the children and their nature. Yellow has this capability of matching with any outfit you put your children into. </p>\n\n<p></br></p>\n\n<p>The Converse name has been around for over 100 years now. All these years they have come up with so many varieties of shoes and all of them have made their mark in the market. There are some shoes that have cemented their place in the market and they are going great even these days. They simply have no competitor who can challenge their essence. The color combinations of these shoes are great and amazing. They are specialists in making sports shoes or casual shoes also. These shoes become very hot when they enter the market because of the great research these designers of the Converse do for making them.         </p>\n',NULL,'2013-03-04 10:58:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00');
